\id JDG - Mbula 
\h Akas 
\toc3 Akas 
\toc2 Akas 
\toc1 Akasǝla 
\mt1 Akasǝla 
\imt1 MƏNCAU 
\im Malǝmce mala \bk Akasǝla\bk* ka lumsǝ nǝ akǝɓicau mala a nza ɓara-ɓara mala do ɗwanyi nggurcau mala amǝ'Isǝrayila, a nre kutio malea a nzali Kan'ana andǝ kum murǝm malea. Aman yi akǝɓicau ka à nda amur ɓwaburaɓwa mala akanggǝrang aɓwana mala nzali mǝnana à tunǝki ama akasǝla ka; bangulea ka amǝgulo soje na, amǝ'ɓashi na kǝla mana aɓwana kǝ twali ka ɗàng. Mwashat atea mana à súrǝì kǝ̀rkǝ́r ka nda Samsǝn, mǝnana atúró male ka à gilǝia aɓa kùré lum-nong-tàrú aban ká lum-bwamdǝ-tongno-nong-mwashat (13-16) ka. Girkani mǝgule aɓa malǝmcenî ka nda mana ama, do-yilǝmu mala Isǝrayila ka do amúr nyesǝɓamuru malea aban Ɓakuli, sǝ ɗwanyi nyesǝɓamuru ka kǝ wanǝ ban a kiɗiki pwari-pwari. Sǝ gìr nakam mǝnana karmur mǝnia ka: ko ɓǝ̀ à na ama, nzalinì ɗwanyi oaki Ɓakuli, sǝ tanni yiu ka, Ɓakuli na amur kúndǝô koya pwari ɓǝ̀ amsǝ aɓwana male, yi mana ɓǝ̀ à pwanzali sǝ à nyar a baní ɗǝm ngga. 
\iot Agir mǝnana a ɓalǝi ka 
\io1 Tsaɗi mala agir mǝnana à kumban ba lú mala Jesǝwa ka \ior 1:1; 2:10\ior* 
\io1 Akasǝla mala Isǝrayila \ior 2:11; 16:31\ior* 
\io1 Agir ɗàngɗáng mǝnana à kumban ngga \ior 17:1; 21:25\ior* 
\c 1  
\s1 Tàu mala Yahuda akdǝmba ká nǝ munǝo arǝ amǝ'Kan'ana 
\p  
\v 1 Anzǝm lú mala Jesǝwa ka, amǝ Isǝrayila ɗì Yahweh ama, <<Ya tàu nani nǝ̀ tita kánǝ munǝo arǝ amǝ'Kan'ana?>>  
\v 2 Yahweh earia wia ama, <<Tàu mala Yahuda na nǝ̀ tita ká ka. Wu sǝni, Ən pàna nzalinì a ɓabuia.>>  
\v 3 Amǝ'tàu mala Yahuda ne amǝ'eambia, amǝ'tàu mala Shimiyon ama, <<Wu yiu atà sǝm, wu bwala sǝm munǝo arǝ amǝ'Kan'ana ace ak nzali mǝnana à kasǝa sǝm ngga. Sǝ sǝm gbal ka, sǝm nǝ̀ ká atà wun ace ak nzali mǝnana à kasǝa wun ngga.>> Pǝlǝa amǝ'tàu mala Shimiyon wari ateà.  
\v 4 Amǝ'tàu mala Yahuda warinǝ munǝo, sǝ Yahweh túr amǝ'Kan'ana andǝ amǝ'Periz a ɓabù amǝ'tàu mala Yahuda; sǝ à gandǝ aburana malea á-lum a Bezek.  
\v 5 À yi kum Adoni-bezek a Bezek, sǝ à warinǝ munǝo arǝì. À gandǝ amǝ'Kan'ana andǝ amǝ'Periz.  
\v 6 Adoni-bezek ɓangŋa, à pǝrte sǝ à kya bwali. À kasǝki amunabuì-mǝbure andǝ amunakusǝi-mǝbure.  
\v 7 Pǝlǝa Adoni-bezek bang ama, <<Amurǝma lumi-tongno-nong-ɓari nakam mǝnana à kasǝki amunabuia-mǝbure andǝ amunakusǝia-mǝbure ka, à kǝ tarki ɓwangina girlina aɓata kpamgbang-lǐ mem; Ɓakuli mbwenam a kúnì gìr mǝnana ǝn pakkia wia ka.>> À yinǝi a Urǝshalima, sǝ kya wú abanì. 
\p  
\v 8 Amǝ'tàu mala Yahuda soa munǝo arǝ amǝ Urǝshalima, sǝ à ak nggea-lê. À gandǝia nǝ kún nggeabyau, sǝ à soaki nggea-lê bǝsa. 
\p  
\v 9 Anzǝm mǝno ka, amǝ'tàu mala Yahuda wario à kya soa munǝo arǝ amǝ'Kan'ana mǝnana à ndanǝdo aɓa nzali múr-ankono, andǝ Negev, andǝ nzali kusǝ-ankono ka.  
\v 10 Amǝ'tàu mala Yahuda warinǝ lwa arǝ amǝ'Kan'ana mana nǝdo a Hebǝron ngga (lullǝ Hebǝron ɗiɗyal ka nda Kiriat-Arba.) À gandǝ \f + \fr 1:10 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Ɓal 13:22; Jes 15:14\ft .\f*Sheshai andǝ Ahiman andǝ Talmai. 
\p  
\v 11 Anzǝm mǝno ka, à warinǝ lwa arǝ aɓwana mǝnana nǝdo a Debir ka (lullǝ Debir ɗiɗyal ka nda Kiriat-Sefer.)  
\v 12 Pǝlǝa Kalip bang ama, <<Ɓwa mǝnana kat lì Kiriat-Sefer nǝ lwa ka, mǝ nǝ pè wi ɓoarnsarilem Aksa ɓǝ̀ duk māmí.>>  
\v 13 Nda Otǝniyel, muna-ɓwabura mala Kenaz, mǝ'kyauwa Kalip lì ka, sǝ Kalip pè wi ɓoarnsarile Aksa duk māmí.  
\v 14 Lang Aksa yina ka, nacau nǝ Otǝniyel ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ zǝmbi wi tárrí Kalip, ɓǝ̀ pè wi nzali a liro. Pǝlǝa Aksa sulǝî nzǝm mǝdambǝriso male, sǝ Kalip ɗì ama, <<Mana a earkice?>>  
\v 15 Pǝlǝa eari wi ama, <<Ida, ɓwamuram. Nzali mǝnana a pam ngga, nda a Negev,\f + \fr 1:15 \fq Negev \ft ka pǝɗanban na.\f* ado ka pam ban mǝnana ndanǝ amgbeɗe mùr ka gbal.>> Nda Kalip pè wi amgbeɗe mùr mana a mgbang-ban andǝ amgbeɗe mùr mana a tūliban ngga.  
\v 16 Amǝ'kà nkil Musa mǝɓwabure, ɓwa Ken, puro andǝ amǝ'tàu mala Yahuda, a nggea-là mala anggun nkangga\f + \fr 1:16 \fq Nggea-là mala anggun nkangga \ft ka nda Jeriko. \f* sǝ à oa Arat aɓa pǝɗanban mala Yahuda, mǝnana nda a Negev ka. À wario à kya do andǝ amǝ'Amalek.\f + \fr 1:16 \fq andǝ amǝ'Amalek. \ft Aɓea mbu-malǝmce mana à gilǝia ɗiɗyal nǝ bù ka à gilǝa ama, <<andǝ amǝ'tàu mala Yahuda.>>\f* 
\v 17 Amǝ'tàu mala Yahuda wari andǝ amǝ'eambia amǝ'tàu mala Shimiyon, sǝ à gandǝ amǝ'Kan'ana mǝnana à ndanǝdo a Zefat ka, sǝ à kiɗikì nggea-lê kat-kat. Adyan ngga aɓwana kǝ tunǝ nggea-lê ama Horma.\f + \fr 1:17 \fq Horma \ft ka ɓalǝi nda kiɗikì kat-kat. \f* 
\v 18 Ɗǝm ngga, amǝ'tàu mala Yahuda ak Gaza andǝ Ashkelon andǝ Ekǝron, andǝ alá mǝnana à kària ka.  
\v 19 Yahweh ka nda atà amǝ'tàu mala Yahuda, sǝ à ak nzali múr-ankono duk malea, sǝama à gandǝ pǝr aɓwana mǝnana à ndanǝdo a ɓawanban ngga ɗàng, acemǝnana à ndanǝ awaru-pǝr mala bolo-candǝa.  
\v 20 À pè Kalip Hebǝron, kǝla mǝnana Musa bang ngga. Pǝlǝa Kalip pǝr amǝ'kà Anak mǝno tàrú ka à purî banì.  
\v 21 Sǝama amǝ'tàu mala Benjami pǝr amǝ'Jebus mǝnana à ndanǝdo a Urǝshalima ka ɗàng, acemani ka amǝ'Jebus do andǝ amǝ'tàu mala Benjami a Urǝshalima bà yalung. 
\s1 Anggurkwar mala Ifǝrem andǝ Manasa ak Betel 
\p  
\v 22 Nggurkwar mala Yisǝfu warinǝ munǝo arǝ Betel, sǝ Yahweh ka nda ateà.  
\v 23 Nggurkwar mala Yisǝfu túr amǝ'shenzǝ-nzali a Betel (lullǝ nggea-lê ɗiɗyal ka nda Luz).  
\v 24 Lang amǝ'shenzǝ-nzalinì sǝn ɓè ɓwabura aban purì ɓá nggea-lê ka, à banggi wi ama, <<Lǝmdǝa sǝm bankutio aɓa nggea-lê pě, sǝ sǝm nǝ̀ pàkkô mǝɓoarne.>>  
\v 25 Pǝlǝa ɓwabure lǝmdǝia wia bankutio aɓa nggea-lê, sǝ à wal-lú koya ɓwa aɓa nggea-lê nǝ kún nggeabyau, sǝ ɓwabure andǝ amǝ'ɓala male ka, à nyia ɓǝà o.  
\v 26 Sǝ ɓwabure wari a nzali mala amǝ'Hitti kya ɓak nggea-là kàm, sǝ tunǝi ama Luz. Anggo sǝ à kǝ tunǝ nggea-lê bà yalung. 
\s1 Acili abân mǝnana amǝ'Isǝrayila lia raka 
\p  
\v 27 Nggurkwar mala Manasa pǝr aɓwana mana nǝdo a Bet-shan andǝ amuna-là male ka ɗàng, sǝ à pǝr aɓwana mana nǝdo a Ta'anak, andǝ Dor, andǝ Ibǝlem, andǝ Megido, andǝ amuna-là malea mana à kària ka ɗàng, acemǝnana amǝ'Kan'ana dàrrì arǝ do aɓa nzali mǝno.  
\v 28 Lang amǝ Isǝrayila yi kumǝna rǝcandǝa kpǝm ngga, à tsǝk amǝ'Kan'ana púp aɓa túró mǝcandǝe, sǝama à pǝria kat-kat ɗàng.  
\v 29 Nggurkwar mala Ifǝrem pǝr amǝ'Kan'ana mana nǝdo a Geza ka ɗàng, nda amǝ'Kan'ana lidǝmba nǝ do aɓalǝia a Geza ka. 
\p  
\v 30 Amǝ'tàu mala Zebulu pǝr aɓwana mana nǝdo a Kitǝron, ko aɓwana mana nǝdo a Nahalol ka ɗàng. Nda amǝ'Kan'ana do aɓalǝia ka, sǝama à tsǝk amǝ'Kan'ana púp aɓa túró mǝcandǝe.  
\v 31 Amǝ'tàu mala Asha pǝr aɓwana mǝnana nǝdo a Akko, ko aɓwana mana nǝdo a Sidon, ko mala Alap, ko mala Akzip, ko mala Helba, ko mala Afek, ko mala Rehop ka ɗàng.  
\v 32 Nda amǝ'tàu mala Asha do aɓalǝ amǝ'Kan'ana, aɓwana mala nzalinì, acemǝnana à pǝr amǝ'Kan'ana ɗàng. 
\p  
\v 33 Amǝ'tàu mala Naftali pǝr aɓwana mǝnana nǝdo a Bet-Shemesh, ko aɓwana mǝnana nǝdo a Bet-Anat ka ɗàng. Nda à do aɓalǝ amǝ'Kan'ana, aɓwana mala nzalinì. Kat andǝ mǝno ka, amǝ'tàu mala Naftali par aɓwana mala Bet-Shemesh andǝ Bet-Anat aɓa túró mǝcandǝe. 
\p  
\v 34 Amǝ'Amor nggiki amǝ'tàu mala Dan, nda à nyar a nzali múr-ankono ka. À earî amǝ'tàu mala Dan ɓǝà sulǝ a dulum ɗàng. 
\p  
\v 35 Amǝ'Amor ka, à dàrrì arǝ do amúr Nkono Heres, a Aijalon, sǝ aɓa Sha'albin. Sǝama lang nggurkwar mala Yisǝfu yì kumǝna rǝcandǝa kpǝm ngga, à tsǝk amǝ'Amor púp aɓa túró mǝcandǝe.  
\v 36 Nzong-nzali mala amǝ'Amor tite a Eauwe Akrabbim, kya pur a Sela sǝ sárǝ́ aban ká dǝmba. 
\c 2  
\s1 Mgbikiru mala amǝ Isǝrayila 
\p  
\v 1 Mǝturonjar mala Yahweh lo a Gilgal, sǝ wari a Bokim a ɓekǝ pwari. Sǝ nacau ama, <<Ən pusǝ wun wu purî ɓá Masar, sǝ ǝn yinǝ wun a nzali mǝnana ǝn kángìr nǝma mǝ nǝ pè aká-wun ngga. Ən bang nǝma, \f + \fr 2:1 \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt Tite 17:7; Pur 6:4; Nggur 31:16\ft .\f*<Pà mǝ nǝ nggaɗi kunam arǝ kùrcau mem sǝnǝa wun ɗàng,  
\v 2 sǝ wun gbal ka, wu kǝa kúti aɓa ɓekǝ kùrcau wunǝ aɓwana mǝnana nǝdo aɓa nzali man ngga ɗàng; dumǝna púp wun nǝ̀ arki agyangŋan malea.> Sǝama wu okam ɗàng. Mana mǝnia wu pak ka?  
\v 3 Sǝ ado ka, mǝ ndarǝ na nǝma, pà mǝ nǝ pǝria ɓǝà upi ban wun ɗàng, a kún mani ka, à nǝ̀ dupa wun azwe arǝ ankanggari wun, sǝ aɓakuli malea nǝ̀ dupa wun gbǝli.>>  
\v 4 Lang mǝturonjar mala Yahweh bangŋǝna amǝnia yì acau aban amǝ Isǝrayila kat ka, aɓwe loasǝ già à ɓua.  
\v 5 Sǝ à tunǝ lullǝ banì ama Bokim.\f + \fr 2:5 \fq Bokim \ft ngga ɓalǝi nda <<amǝ'ɓua.>>\f* Sǝ à pà gìr'nkila aban Yahweh abanì. 
\s1 Lú mala Jesǝwa 
\p  
\v 6 Lang Jesǝwa mesǝna ɓwabundǝa ka, koyan atà amǝ Isǝrayila ka nyar a nzali liɓala male, ace ak nzalî ɓǝ̀ duk girkuma malea.  
\v 7 Sǝ amǝ Isǝrayila kpata Yahweh aɓa do-yilǝmu mala Jesǝwa kat, sǝ aɓa do-yilǝmu kat mala aɓwana-mǝgule mǝnana à ueo nǝyilǝmu anzǝm lú mala Jesǝwa, yià mǝnana à sǝlǝnace túró mǝgule mǝnana kat Yahweh pè ace Isǝrayila ka. 
\p  
\v 8 Sǝ Jesǝwa muna-ɓwabura mala Nun, guro mala Yahweh wǔ, ndanǝ apǝlǝa gbǝman-mwashat nǝ lum (110).  
\v 9 Sǝ à tsǝì a nzali liɓala male a Timnat-heres, mǝnana nda a nzali múr-ankono mala Ifǝrem ngga, nǝ njar-nza mala Nkono Gash.  
\v 10 Sǝ anzǝm mǝnana aɓwana mana a nza mǝno ka à umǝna atà akeâ ka, ɓè nza lo mǝnana à súrǝ̀ Yahweh, ko túró mǝnana pàkkî Isǝrayila raka. 
\s1 Amǝ Isǝrayila ɗeki kpata Yahweh 
\p  
\v 11 Amǝ Isǝrayila pàk gìr mǝɓane aɓadǝm Yahweh, sǝ à kpata aBa'al.  
\v 12 Sǝ à ɗekibuia arǝ Yahweh, Ɓakuli mala akeâ mǝnana pusǝia à purî ɓá nzali Masar ka. À o atà aɓea aɓakuli, aɓea aɓakuli mala aɓwana mǝnana à kària ka, sǝ à peri abania. Pǝlǝa à tsǝa bum Yahweh lúllô.  
\v 13 À nyingbuia arǝ Yahweh, sǝ à kpata aBa'al andǝ Ashtarot.  
\v 14 Nda bumlulla mala Yahweh earke arǝ amǝ Isǝrayila, sǝ tasǝia a ɓabu amǝ'tǝllìban mǝnana à pwan agirkuma malea kǝla pwan gǝna-lwa ka. Sǝ ɗǝm ngga, mea a ɓabu aɓia-mǝbura mǝnana à kària a koya buì, sǝ à gandǝ came a kúnià raka.  
\v 15 Koya ban sǝ à wari a lwa ka, bù Yahweh na mgbasho nǝia ace pàkkia wia mǝɓane, kǝla mǝnana Yahweh akdǝmba banggia wia, sǝ kánbia wia ka. Sǝ anggo ka, à kum ɓamúrià aɓa gir'murmwana mǝɓike. 
\s1 Yahweh loasǝ akasǝla 
\p  
\v 16 Pǝlǝa Yahweh loasǝ akasǝla, mǝnana à amsǝia a ɓabu aɓwana mǝnana à kǝ ɓǝmbǝria ka.  
\v 17 Kat andǝ mani ka, à okî akasǝla malea ɗàng; à gyatàrǝia aban ká kpata aɓea aɓakuli, sǝ à ɓun aɓadǝmbia. À kaurǝ pǝlǝ nzǝmia arǝ njar mǝnana akeâ ging kam ngga. Akeâ kpata anzongcau mala Yahweh, sǝ yià ka, à pàk anggo ɗàng.  
\v 18 A koya bàkú sǝ Yahweh loasǝì amǝ Isǝrayila akasǝla ka, Yahweh na atà mǝno yì kasǝla ka, sǝ kǝ amsǝia a ɓabu aɓia-mǝbura aɓa do-yilǝmu kat mala mǝno yì kasǝla ka. Mǝnia ka nda acemǝnana Yahweh sǝn mǝsǝswatǝr malea atàcau mala imge malea a ɓabu aɓwana mǝnana à kǝ pea wia tanni, sǝ à kǝ paria ka.  
\v 19 Sǝama a bàkú mǝnana mǝno yì kasǝla wuna ka, amǝ Isǝrayila nǝ̀ pǝlǝ nzǝmia, sǝ ɓealia nǝ̀ ɓike nǝ̀ kútì mala akeâ; à nǝ̀ kùti a kpata aɓea aɓakuli, andǝ peri abania, andǝ ɓunno aɓadǝmbia. À pà nǝ̀ vwakibuia arǝ pakkiagir malea ko kpata anjar mgbikiru malea ɗàng.  
\v 20 Pǝlǝa bumlulla mala Yahweh earke arǝ amǝ Isǝrayila, sǝ bang ama, <<Acemǝnana aɓwana mǝnia pak kpakpak arǝ kùrcau mem mǝnana ǝn tsǝki akeâ nzongcau arǝì, sǝ à ginǝna ok giem ngga,  
\v 21 anzali mala aɓwapǝndǝa mǝnana Jesǝwa ɗekia, liǎ ɗàng lang wù ka, pà mǝ nǝ pǝria ɗǝm a ɓadǝmbia ɗàng.  
\v 22 Mǝ nǝ pàktúró nǝia ace mwam Isǝrayila, ko à nǝ̀ tsǝkiria arǝ gya aɓa njar mem, Mim Yahweh, kǝla mana akeâ pàk ka, ko à pà nǝ̀ pàk ɗàng.>>  
\v 23 Nda Yahweh ɗeki aɓwapǝndǝa mǝno ɓǝà ueo, pǝria ɓǝà purî bania tù ɗang, sǝ tsǝa anzali mala aɓwapǝndǝa mǝno kpa a ɓabu Jesǝwa, ace mǝnana nǝ̀ liǎ ka ɗàng. 
\c 3  
\s1 Aɓwapǝndǝa mǝnana à nyia ɓǝà ueo a nzali Kan'ana ka 
\p  
\v 1 Amǝnia ka, à nda ka aɓwapǝndǝa mala anzali mǝnana Yahweh nyia ɓǝà ueo ace mwam Isǝrayila nǝia ka, yia amǝ Isǝrayila mana à lwa kǝ lwa aɓalǝ a'lwa kat mala nzali Kan'ana raka.  
\v 2 (Kǝ nda ace kanî anza mala amǝ Isǝrayila mǝnana à súrǝ̀ lwa ɗiɗyal raka, ɓǝà súrǝì.)  
\v 3 Amǝnia ka à nda ka aɓwapǝndǝa mala nzalinì: amǝ'yálmurû tongno mala amǝ'Filisti, andǝ amǝ'Kan'ana kat, andǝ amǝ'Sidon, andǝ amǝ'Hivi mana à ndanǝdo amur Nkono Lebano, twal a Nkono Ba'al-Hamon, kya bwal Lebo-Hamat ka.  
\v 4 À nying amǝnia yì aɓwana ka, ace mwam Isǝrayila, ace sǝlǝa ko Isǝrayila nǝ̀ kpata anzongcau mala Yahweh, mǝnana pè akeâ nǝ bu Musa ka. 
\p  
\v 5 Nda amǝ Isǝrayila do aɓalǝ amǝ'Kan'ana, andǝ amǝ'Hitti, andǝ amǝ'Amor, andǝ amǝ'Periz, andǝ amǝ'Hivi, andǝ amǝ'Jebus ka.  
\v 6 Sǝ à alki amuna-mamǝna mala amǝ'Kan'ana, sǝ à pà amuna-mamǝna malea aban amǝ'Kan'ana, à alia, sǝ à peri aban aɓakuli malea. 
\s1 Otǝniyel amsǝ amǝ Isǝrayila 
\p  
\v 7 Amǝ Isǝrayila pàk gìr mǝɓike aɓadǝm Yahweh. Ɓalǝia lorǝ Yahweh, yì Ɓakuli malea, sǝ à kùti a peri aban aBa'al andǝ Ashera.  
\v 8 Pǝlǝa bumlulla mala Yahweh, lo earki-bǝsa amur amǝ Isǝrayila, sǝ earî Kushan-Rishatayim,\f + \fr 3:8 \fq Kushan-Rishatayim \ft ko Kushan mǝ'ɓealɓikea kusǝ ɓari \f* murǝm mala Aram-Naharayim,\f + \fr 3:8 \fq Aram-Naharayim \ft ngga ɓalǝi nda <<Aram mala anggeasala ɓari>> aɓa nzali Mesopotamiya.\f* ɓǝ̀ gandǝ amǝ Isǝrayila sǝ paria aɓate, ba apǝlǝa tongno-nong-tàrú.  
\v 9 Sǝama, lang amǝ Isǝrayila ɓua aban Yahweh ka, Yahweh loasǝia wia ɓwa mǝnana nǝ̀ amsǝia ka. Lùllǝì ama Otǝniyel, muna-ɓwabura mala Kenaz, mǝ'kyauwa Kalip. 
\p  
\v 10 Bangŋo mala Yahweh yi sulǝ amurí, sǝ yi duk kasǝla mala Isǝrayila. Lang pur lwa ka, Yahweh tasǝ Kushan-Rishatayim, murǝm mala Aram, a ɓabuì, sǝ Otǝniyel limurǝm nǝ lwa amurí.  
\v 11 Nda nzalinì yi kum usǝlǝo mala apǝlǝa lumi-ine ka. Pǝlǝa Otǝniyel, muna-ɓwabura mala Kenaz yi paklú. 
\s1 Ehud amsǝ amǝ Isǝrayila a bù amǝ'Mowap 
\p  
\v 12 Amǝ Isǝrayila pàk gìr mǝɓike ɗǝm a mǝsǝ Yahweh. Pǝlǝa Yahweh pè Egǝlon, murǝm mala Mowap, rǝcandǝa amur Isǝrayila, acemǝnana Isǝrayila pàngŋǝ̀nà gìr mǝnana mǝɓike na a mǝsǝ Yahweh ka.  
\v 13 Egǝlon ramba amǝ'Amon andǝ amǝ'Amalek ɓǝà camatè, à kya gandǝ Isǝrayila a munǝo, sǝ à ak Nggea-là mala Anggun-Nkangga.\f + \fr 3:13 \fq Nggea-là mala Anggun-Nkangga \ft ka nda Jeriko.\f* 
\v 14 Sǝ amǝ Isǝrayila do aɓata Egǝlon, murǝm Mowap apǝlǝa lum-bwamdǝ-tongno-nong-tàrú (18). 
\p  
\v 15 Nyar ɗǝm ngga, amǝ Isǝrayila yinǝ ɓua malea aban Yahweh, pǝlǝa loasǝia wia ɓwa mǝnana nǝ̀ akmúria ka. Lullǝì nda Ehud, nggaro, muna-ɓwabura mala Gera, a tàu mala Benjami. Amǝ Isǝrayila tasǝì nǝ agir-cemi malea ɓǝ̀ kya mbwe aban Egǝlon, murǝm mala Mowap.  
\v 16 Ehud nǝ nggearǝì pàk nggeabyau mana kúni ɓari, sǝ sauwa male ka ɓakusǝu mwashat nǝ tsùrú na ka. Pǝlǝa kùrì a ɓunni nǝ tabuì mǝlì, aɓa nggea-daura male. 
\p  
\v 17 Yi pà agir-ceminî aban Egǝlon, murǝm Mowap, mǝnana nggea ɓwa mǝ'nyane na ka.  
\v 18 Anzǝm mana Ehud pana agir-ceminî ka, pǝlǝa tasǝ aɓwana mana à twal agir-ceminî ka ɓǝà o.  
\v 19 Sǝ yì ka, lang bingŋǝ́nà ban aɓǝ́nzál-tali mǝnana a Gilgal ka, wulio nyar aban Egǝlon, sǝ na ama, <<Murǝm, mǝ ndanǝ càu ɓa-sǝmbǝrǝa aceo.>> 
\p Pǝlǝa murǝm banggi amǝtè ama, <<Wu nying sǝm!>> Pǝlǝa yia kat ka, à puro, à nyì. 
\p  
\v 20 Ehud pǝlǝa kutio abani, lang ndaban do nǝmurǝì, a kurǝm-kuli male mǝpwale ka. Sǝ Ehud banggi wi ama, <<Mim ngga, mǝ ndanǝ cau mana Ɓakuli pam aceo ka.>> Pǝlǝa murǝm loapi buno male. 
\p  
\v 21 Sǝ Ehud warinǝ bui mǝnggare, kwetǝ nggeabyau mǝnana a ɓunni nǝ tabuì mǝlì ka, sǝ zuɓina murǝm nǝi a bumi.  
\v 22 Byau kutio sǝ kò andǝ garè, sǝ sak anzǝmi. Sǝ Ehud ka, pusǝ nggeabyaunì ɗàng, kara mùrú yi ta amur nggeabyau; sǝ ciu yi ar a nza.  
\v 23 Pǝlǝa Ehud, purî ɓá ndà, girki akún kurǝm-kuli, sǝ kumlǝkia. Pǝlǝa kutio o. 
\p  
\v 24 Anzǝm mana Ehud umǝna ka, amǝtúró mala murǝm yiu, sǝ à kum akún kurǝm-kuli agire. Sǝ à bang ama, <<Murǝm ngga ndarǝ usǝlǝo aɓa kurǝm ɓaɓalǝu mǝpwale aɓa palta.>>  
\v 25 Pǝlǝa à kúndǝô, ganda kya pakkia wia, sǝ lang à sǝni mǝn kún kurǝm-kuli raka, à twal kyî, sǝ à mǝngi akún-akurǝm. Kara à sǝni ka, murǝm kpana a nzali a ɓakurǝm, wuna. 
\p  
\v 26 Lang à dǝndi ka, Ehud auna umǝna. Yi kútì aɓǝ́nzál-tali, sǝ auwa o a Seyira.  
\v 27 Lang yi bingŋǝ́nà Seyira ka, twang njawe aɓa nzali múr-ankono mala Ifǝrem. Amǝ Isǝrayila sulǝî nzali múr-ankono andǝi, sǝ yì Ehud ka dupia wia a dǝmba.  
\v 28 Banggia wia ama, <<Wu yiu atam, acemǝnana Yahweh pana aɓiwun amǝbura, yì amǝ'Mowap, a ɓabu wun!>> Nda à sulǝ atè sǝ à kya ak abân yálì nkaring mùr mala Jodan, mana nda a nkāɓe nzali Mowap ka, sǝ à eare ɓǝ̀ kǝɓwa yàl aban ká a nkaring ɗàng.  
\v 29 A pwari mǝno ka à wal atà amǝ'Mowap kǝla ɓwa á-lum (10,000), yià kat ka aburana amǝ'rǝcandǝe andǝ amǝ ɓabumcandǝa na; ko ɓwa mwashat ateà au ɗàng. 
\p  
\v 30 A pwari mǝno ka, Isǝrayila ɓùn Mowap aɓatea, sǝ nzalinì kum usǝlǝo apǝlǝa lumi-tongno-nong-tàrú (80). 
\s1 Shamgar 
\p  
\v 31 Anzǝm Ehud ka, Shamgar muna-ɓwabura mala Anat, wal-lú ka amǝ'Filisti gbǝman-tongno-nong-mwashat (600) nǝ gara-pǝrta andá-rya. Yì gbal ka, amsǝ Isǝrayila. 
\c 4  
\s1 Debora andǝ Barak 
\p  
\v 1 Amǝ Isǝrayila ka à nyar ɗǝm à pàk gìr mǝnana mǝɓike na a mǝsǝ Yahweh ka, anzǝm lú mala Ehud. 
\p  
\v 2 Nda Yahweh túrmuria a ɓabu Jabin murǝm mala Kan'ana mana yálkiyi aɓwana a Hazo ka. Mǝ'sàrǝ̀ban mala amǝ'lwa male ka nda Sǝsera, mana ndanǝdo a Haroshet-Hagoyim ngga.  
\v 3 Acemǝnana Sǝsera ndanǝ awaru-pǝr gbǝman-tongno-nong-ine (900), mana à peǎ nǝ bolo-candǝa ka, par amǝ Isǝrayila, parban ɓana, arǝ apǝlǝa lumi-ɓari. Osso amǝ Isǝrayila ɓua aban Yahweh ɓǝ̀ bwalia-wia-kam. 
\p  
\v 4 A bàkú mǝno ka, Debora, māɓangnǝa, mālá Lapidot, nda mǝɓashi amúr Isǝrayila.  
\v 5 Pàk-ka nǝ̀ do a tǝ́r nggun-nkangga mala Debora anre Rama andǝ Betel a nzali múr-ankono mala Ifǝrem, sǝ amǝ Isǝrayila nǝ̀ yiu a baní ace ɓashi.  
\v 6 Ɓè fara ka, túrban atà Barak muna-ɓwabura mala Abinowam a Kedesh, aɓa bù-nzali Naftali, ne wi ama, <<Yahweh, Ɓakuli mala amǝ Isǝrayila, kǝ tsǝko mǝnia yì nzongcau ka ama: <Pwan amǝ'lwa á-lum (10,000) a tàu mala Naftali andǝ tàu mala Zebulu, sǝ wu kyan nǝia a Nkono Tabo.  
\v 7 Mǝ nǝ nun Sǝsera, mǝ'sàrǝ̀ban amúr amǝ'lwa mala Jabin, andǝ awaru-pǝr male, andǝ amǝ'lwa male, ɓǝà yiu ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu je-munǝo wunǝia a Nggeasala Kishon ngga, sǝ mǝ nǝ pò limurǝm amurí.> >> 
\p  
\v 8 Sǝ Barak ka nyesǝi wi ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ awu nǝ ká atàm ngga, mǝ nǝ ká, sǝ ɓǝ̀ a pa wu nǝ ká atàm raka, pà mǝ nǝ ká ɗàng.>> 
\p  
\v 9 Sǝ Debora eari wi ama, <<Mbak-kàngkàng, mǝ nǝ ká atò, sǝama njargula mǝnia a earce ká kàm ngga, pà nǝ̀ kánǝ we aɓa kum gusǝlǝban ɗang, acemǝnana Yahweh nǝ̀ túrmúr Sǝsera a ɓabu ɓwama.>> Pǝlǝa Debora lo sǝ à wari andǝ Barak a Kedesh.  
\v 10 Barak tunǝ tàu mala Zebulu andǝ tàu mala Naftali a Kedesh. Sǝ aburana á-lum (10,000) o atè, sǝ Debora o atè gbal. 
\p  
\v 11 (Adyan ngga Heba ɓwa'Ken, mǝ'kà Hobap, nkil Musa ka angŋa-dǝmba tùrna nyingŋǝna acili amǝ'Ken, sǝ tsǝ̀ngŋǝ̀nà gumli male zak, a ban nggun-mǝgule mǝnana a Zaananim, tù aban Kedesh ka.) 
\p  
\v 12 Lang à banggi Sǝsera ama Barak muna-ɓwabura mala Abinowam eauna amur Nkono Tabo ka,  
\v 13 kara ram awaru-pǝr male gbǝman-tongno-nong-ine (900) kat, mana à peǎ nǝ bolo-candǝa ka, andǝ aburana mǝnana kat à nda atè ka abanɓwáná, sǝ à lo a Haroshet-Hagoyim aban ká a Nggeasala Kishon. 
\p  
\v 14 Osso Debora ne Barak ama, <<Kyane! Pwari mǝnia yalung ngga, nda pwari mana Yahweh pana Sǝsera nǝi a ɓabuo ka. Yale Yahweh na aka wun dǝmba kǝ ká ka.>> Barak pǝlǝa sulǝî múr Nkono Tabo nǝ amǝ'lwa á-lum (10,000) male aban o atè.  
\v 15 Lang Barak andǝ amǝ'lwa male soa-munǝo nǝ kún nggeabyau ka, Yahweh túr Sǝsera andǝ awaru-pǝr male kat, andǝ amǝ'lwa male kat aɓa zurǝki, aɓadǝm Barak. Sǝsera sulǝî waru-pǝr male sǝ twal-mire nǝ kusǝi ace auwa.  
\v 16 Sǝ Barak pǝrta awaru-pǝr andǝ amǝ'lwa mala Sǝsera aban ká Haroshet-Hagoyim. À twalta amǝ'lwa mala Sǝsera kàng nǝ kún nggeabyau; kǝ ɓwa mwashat ue ɗang. 
\p  
\v 17 Sǝsera ɓang nǝ kusǝi wari a gumli mala Jayel, mālá Heba ɓwa'Ken, acemǝnana dotarǝu nakam anre Murǝm Jabin mala Hazo andǝ ɓala mala Heba ɓwa'Ken.  
\v 18 Jayel puro nǝ̀ kúllí Sǝsera, sǝ ne wi ama, <<Kàra yiu, ɓwamǝgule mem, kútiô aɓa gumli mem. Cè ɓangciu bwalo ɗang.>> Pǝlǝa kúti aɓa gumli mala Jayel, sǝ Jayel kumsǝi wi kungtung amurí.  
\v 19 Osso Sǝsera ne wi ama, <<Ida pam mur bǝtikulyak acemǝnana mǝsamur-kǝ-walam.>> Pǝlǝa Jayel mǝn du kiura, pe wi sǝ nu, pǝlǝa kumsǝi wi gìr amurí.  
\v 20 Sǝ banggi Jayel ama, <<Cam a kún gumli, ɓǝ̀ kǝɓwa yiu sǝ ɗio ama, <Kǝ ɓwa kani le ka?> Ne wi ama, <Awo.> >> 
\p  
\v 21 Sǝsera ka aulǝ kǝ̀rkǝ́r, nda kò a ntulo mǝlime ka. Pǝlǝa Jayel, mālá Heba twal nkpako gumli andǝ ndolo a buì, sǝ eamdǝki wari amurí sǝ gballî wi nkpakonî a ɓamuri, kya tǝm nzali. Nda wù ka.  
\v 22 Zuku ka, Barak yi tusǝo, ndarǝ pyangnǝ atà Sǝsera, sǝ Jayel pur atè kya kumi sǝ ne wi ama, <<Yiu! Mǝ nǝ lǝmdǝo ɓwa mǝnana a alkiyite ka.>> Nda kúti atè aɓa gumli, sǝ sǝni ka Sǝsera na nong ngga, lú na, nǝ nkpako a ɓamuri. 
\p  
\v 23 A pwari mǝno ka, Ɓakuli ɓungi Jabin murǝm Kan'ana aɓadǝm amǝ Isǝrayila.  
\v 24 Sǝ bù amǝ Isǝrayila lidǝmba nǝ candǝe amur Jabin murǝm mala Kan'ana, sǝ rǝcandǝa malea ɓākì, she lang à kiɗikini ka. 
\c 5  
\s1 Nggyal mala Debora andǝ Barak 
\p  
\v 1 A pwari mǝno ka, Debora andǝ Barak, muna-ɓwabura mala Abinowam, à tù nggyal mǝnia ka: 
\q1  
\v 2 Lang amǝgulo mala Isǝrayila akì aɓwana dǝmba aban ká ka, 
\q2 aɓwe eare à pà ɓamuria. 
\q2 Wu ɓwangsǝ Yahweh! 
\q1  
\v 3 Wu ǒ, wun amurǝma! 
\q2 Wu kwakikir wun, wun amǝgulo! 
\q1 Mǝ nǝ tùkî Yahweh nggyal. 
\q2 Mǝ nǝ tù nggyal ɓwangsǝban aban Yahweh, 
\q2 Ɓakuli mala Isǝrayila. 
\q1  
\v 4 Yahweh, lang a nying ɓá Seyir, 
\q1 lang a purì ɓá bù-nzali Edom ngga, 
\q2 nzali gǝggǝli, sǝ bumkuli nya mbulo. 
\q2 E, apǝrɓang rakki mǝsǝ mbulo. 
\q1  
\v 5 Ankono gǝggǝli aɓadǝm Yahweh, 
\q2 nggearǝ Saina aɓadǝm Yahweh, 
\q2 Ɓakuli mala Isǝrayila. 
\q1  
\v 6 Aɓalǝ apwari mala Shamgar, muna-ɓwabura mala Anat, 
\q1 sǝ ndya ɗǝm aɓalǝ apwari mala Jayel ka, 
\q2 aɓwana ɗeki kutio arǝ anjar-mǝgule, 
\q2 sǝ amǝgya kàr arǝ anjar-mǝkarke a nzǝm-la. 
\q1  
\v 7 Aɓwana mala amuna-là mala Isǝrayila yi malâ. 
\q1 À yi malâ she lang mim, Debora, ǝn lo; 
\q2 she lang ǝn lo kǝla nggeau a Isǝrayila ka. 
\q1  
\v 8 Lang Isǝrayila twal kpata bǝsa aɓakuli ka, 
\q2 munǝo kutio a kún nggea-là. 
\q1 À sǝn ntwangŋo ko nkongŋo kàm 
\q2 a bù aburana á-lumi-ine mala Isǝrayila le? 
\q1  
\v 9 Ɓabumam o arǝ amǝ'sàrǝ̀ban mala Isǝrayila, 
\q2 mǝnana à pà ɓamúrià nǝ eare malea aɓalǝ aɓwana ka. 
\q1 Ɓǝà ɓwangsǝ Yahweh. 
\q1  
\v 10 Wu bangce, wun mǝnana wu kǝ eau a nzǝm amǝdambǝriso-pwasǝa ka, 
\q1 wun mǝnana wu kǝ do amur agir-do nzǝm pǝr amǝɓǝlke, 
\q2 sǝ wu kǝ gya amur njargula ka. 
\q1  
\v 11 Wu kwakikir wun arǝ gi ka amǝ'nggyal arǝ abân to mùr; 
\q2 akano ka à kǝ zǝkice alimurǝm mala Yahweh, 
\q2 alimurǝm mala amǝ'lwa male a Isǝrayila. 
\q1 Pǝlǝa aɓwana mala Yahweh sulǝ aban ká arǝ akún nggea-là. 
\q1  
\v 12 Loapi-ntulo, Debora, loapi-ntulo! 
\q2 Loapi-ntulo, loapi-ntulo, loasǝ nggyal! 
\q1 Lo-came, Barak! 
\q2 Bwalki aguro-lwa mô, 
\q2 we muna-ɓwabura mala Abinowam! 
\q1  
\v 13 Pǝlǝa cili aɓwana-mǝgule mǝnana à ue ka, 
\q2 à sulǝo à yiu; 
\q1 aɓwana mala Yahweh sulǝo à yiu aceì, 
\q2 arǝ akanggǝrang amǝ'lwa. 
\q1  
\v 14 Aɓea aɓwana mala Ifǝrem, 
\q1 mana tǝrtea pur a Amalek ka, 
\q2 à yiu atò, we Benjami, 
\q2 wunǝ amǝ'lwa mô. 
\q1 Amǝ'sàrǝ̀ban mǝnana à pur a Makir ka, 
\q2 à sulǝo à yiu; 
\q1 sǝ amǝnana à kǝ ging nǝ gara mala mǝ'sàrǝ̀ban a buia ka, 
\q2 à pur a Zebulu sǝ à yiu. 
\q1  
\v 15 Amǝgulo mala Isaka ka, 
\q2 à nda atà Debora, 
\q1 kǝla mana Isaka pàk ka, anggo sǝ Barak pa; 
\q2 à giɓi aban ká aɓa ɓangŋaban a npurota kusǝi. 
\q1 Aɓalǝ anggǝsan mala Ruben ngga, ɓalkiɓabum na kam. 
\q1  
\v 16 Palang sǝ wu akrǝ wun atà adomwan mala anzur ma'wun, 
\q2 ace ok twanggi akarinka ace adomwan le? 
\q1 Aɓalǝ anggǝsan mala Ruben ngga, ɓalkiɓabum na kam. 
\q1  
\v 17 Aɓwana mala Gilǝyat ka à ueo a nkaring Jodan a takuli; 
\q1 sǝ tàu mala Dan ngga, palang sǝ akrǝi atà awaru-bǝsa? 
\q1 Tàu mala Asha ka, duk kano ɗǝong a kún nggeamùr, 
\q2 akrǝi a ban-kpasha mala awaru. 
\q1  
\v 18 Tàu mala Zebulu ka, à nda mǝnana à twal lú a kún buia ka; 
\q1 anggo gbal sǝ tàu mala Naftali pǎ a kun-munǝo. 
\q1  
\v 19 Amurǝma yiu sǝ à munǝo, 
\q1 pǝlǝa amurǝma mala amǝ'Kan'ana munǝ a Ta'anak, a kún myalmúr Megido, 
\q2 sǝ ko à twal kǝ gǝna-lwa mala bolo-azǝrfa ɗang. 
\q1  
\v 20 Anlero munǝ nǝ kuli. 
\q1 Aɓalǝ anjar-gya malea ka, 
\q2 à munǝ arǝ Sǝsera. 
\q1  
\v 21 Mùrɓangŋa mala Kishon yi pwania, 
\q2 mǝno yì mùrɓangŋa mala anza ɓara-ɓara, 
\q2 yì mùrɓangŋa mala Nggeasala Kishon. 
\q1 Yilǝmem, fa, kya aɓa rǝcandǝa! 
\q1  
\v 22 Pǝlǝa apǝr [mala Sǝsera] yiu nǝ tswaki, 
\q2 nkaulakusǝia kǝ tǝmgi nzali, 
\q2 nǝ tswaki mala apǝr-lwa male. 
\q1  
\v 23 Mǝturonjar mala Yahweh bang ama, <<Sú [Là] Meroz.>> 
\q1 <<Suban, suban amur aɓwana mǝnana à ndanǝdo kam ngga, 
\q2 acemǝnana à ginǝ puro ace yiua bwali Yahweh, 
\q2 ace yiua bwali wi munǝo arǝ akanggǝrang amǝ'lwa.>> 
\q1  
\v 24 Atà amamǝna ka, Jayel mālá Heba ɓwa Ken, 
\q2 ɓǝ̀ kum tsǝkbu mǝnana kutibani ka. 
\q1 Atà amamǝna amǝ'do aɓalǝ agumli ka, 
\q2 ɓǝ̀ kum tsǝkbu mǝnana kutibani ka. 
\q1  
\v 25 Sǝsera zǝmbi wi mùr, sǝ pe wi kiura; 
\q2 yinǝi wi nǝ kiura mǝbwale aɓa kwar mala amǝgulo. 
\q1  
\v 26 Pǝlǝa lǝmdǝ buì, twal nkpako gumli, 
\q2 sǝ buì-mǝlì bwal ndolo mala amǝ'túrô. 
\q1 Pǝlǝa gballì Sǝsera, ar mú ɓamuri; 
\q2 zuɓi, tusǝ nshekiri. 
\q1  
\v 27 Sǝsera yauwi; kpa a nzali, nong piu; 
\q2 solǝo kpa a nzali a kusǝi; 
\q1 a ban mǝnana kpa kam ngga, 
\q2 akàm sǝ nongŋo, wuna. 
\q1  
\v 28 Nggea Sǝsera soa mǝsǝi aban sǝnban a mǝsǝkurǝm; 
\q2 cam a nzǝm aferang sǝ keban ama, 
\q1 <<Palang sǝ waru-pǝr male dǝndi arǝ nyare? 
\q1 Palang sǝ gǝshi akusǝ apǝr mala waru-pǝr male dǝndi?>> 
\q1  
\v 29 Pǝlǝa amā-gulo male amǝkware pe wi eare; 
\q1 sǝ yale yì nǝ nggearǝì ka earî ɓamúrì ama, 
\q1  
\v 30 <<À malaká kum gǝna-lwa sǝ à mal gake re? 
\q2 Ɓwama mwashat ko ɓari ace koya mǝ'lwa, 
\q2 anggubyau mǝɓoarsǝne atà agǝna-lwa ace Sǝsera, 
\q2 anggubyau mǝɓoarsǝne mǝnana à teanǝta ka, 
\q2 nggubyau-koarǝu mwashat ko ɓari, 
\q2 amǝɓoarsǝne mǝnana à teanǝta ka, 
\q2 aɓalǝ agǝna-lwa, acem mǝ kô a myalam?>> 
\q1  
\v 31 Acemani ka, aɓio-mǝbura ɓǝà ueɓà, Yahweh, 
\q2 sǝ aɓwana mana à earceo ka, ɓǝà tǎ 
\q2 kǝla pwari mana kǝ eauwe aɓa rǝcandǝa male ka. 
\m Anggo sǝ à kum usǝlǝo aɓa nzalinì apǝlǝa lumi-ine. 
\c 6  
\s1 Amǝ'Midiyan pè amǝ'Isǝrayila tanni 
\p  
\v 1 Ɗǝm ngga amǝ Isǝrayila pàk gìr mǝnana mǝɓike na a mǝsǝ Yahweh ka, sǝ Yahweh tasǝia a ɓabu amǝ'Midiyan ba apǝlǝa tongno-nong-ɓari.  
\v 2 Rǝcandǝa mala amǝ'Midiyan ɓākì mala amǝ'Isǝrayila, sǝ atàcau mala amǝ'Midiyan ngga, amǝ'Isǝrayila alita ɓamuria abân sǝmbǝrǝa aɓalǝ ampu amur ankono, andǝ agumi-ɓa-tali andǝ akanggǝrang-ban.  
\v 3 A koya bàkú mana amǝ Isǝrayila ɓealkina agirɓaban malea ka, amǝ'Midiyan, andǝ amǝ'Amalek, andǝ aɓwana mala takuli nǝ̀ yiu arǝia.  
\v 4 À nǝ̀ tsǝki akattì malea ace ká arǝia, sǝ à nǝ̀ kiɗiki agirɓaban aban ká ɗār a Gaza. À pà nǝ̀ nyinggi amǝ Isǝrayila kǝ gìr mǝnana à nǝ̀ lì ka ɗàng; à nying kǝ nzur ko mbul, ko ndǎ, ko mǝdambǝriso ɗàng.  
\v 5 Pàk ka à nǝ̀ yiu nǝ agirkusǝu malea andǝ agumli malea. À kǝ yiu kǝla làkkì mala doshi. Yià andǝ akalakadambi malea ka, à pà nǝ̀ gandǝ ɓallia ɗàng. À nǝ̀ yiu aɓa nzalinì ace kiɗikè.  
\v 6 Amǝ'Midiyan pàk amǝ Isǝrayila ɓàɓá, sǝ amǝ Isǝrayila ɓua aban Yahweh. 
\p  
\v 7 Lang amǝ Isǝrayila ɓua aban Yahweh atàcau mala parban mala amǝ'Midiyan ngga,  
\v 8 Yahweh túr mǝɓangnǝa aban amǝ Isǝrayila. Sǝ banggia wia ama, <<Mǝnia ka nda cau mǝnana Yahweh, Ɓakuli mala amǝ Isǝrayila bang ngga: Ən pusǝ wun, wu pùrî ɓá nzali Masar, sǝ ǝn pusǝ wun, wu pùrî ɓá ɓala guro.  
\v 9 Sǝ ǝn amsǝ wun a ɓabu amǝ'Masar, sǝ a ɓabu aɓwana mǝnana à par wun ngga. Ən pǝria à pùrî ɓadǝm wun, sǝ ǝn pa wun nzali malea.  
\v 10 Ən na wun nǝma, <Mǝ nda Yahweh, Ɓakuli ma'wun; wu kǝa ɓanggi\f + \fr 6:10 \fq ɓanggi \ft ko kpata\f* aɓakuli mala amǝ'Amor, mǝnana wu do a nzali malea ka ɗàng.> Sǝ wun ngga, wu kwakikir wun arǝàm ɗàng.>> 
\s1 Ɓakuli tunǝ Gidiyon 
\p  
\v 11 Mǝturonjar mala Yahweh yiu sǝ do a tǝrtà nggea-nggun mala Johash, ɓwa nggurkwar mala Abiyeza, mǝnana a Ofǝra ka. Muna-ɓwabura male Gidiyon ngga nda aban nya mǝssa a ban mǝnana à kǝ kamggi mùr-anap kàm ngga, ace sǝmbǝrǝì amǝ'Midiyan.  
\v 12 Mǝturonjar mala Yahweh pusǝrǝi a baní sǝ banggi wi ama, <<Yahweh na atò, we kanggǝrang mǝ'lwa.>>  
\v 13 Sǝ Gidiyon banggi wi ama, <<Ida, ɓwamǝgule, ɓǝ̀ Yahweh na atà sǝm ngga, mana tsǝa sǝ amǝnia yì agir ka à kǝ kum sǝm? Agir-ndǝlǝki mǝnana kat aká sǝm na sǝm ceǎ ka, à ndake? À bang ama, <Nggeari ka, Yahweh pusǝ sǝm, sǝm pùrî ɓá nzali Masar re?> Sǝ ado ka, Yahweh vwakinabuì arǝ sǝm, sǝ pànà sǝm a ɓabu amǝ'Midiyan.>> 
\p  
\v 14 Sǝ Yahweh pǝlǝ a baní sǝ banggi wi ama, <<Kyane aɓa rǝcandǝa mò mǝnia ka, sǝ wu amsǝ Isǝrayila a bù amǝ'Midiyan. Ən túrǒ re?>>  
\v 15 Sǝ Gidiyon banggi wi ama, <<Ida ɓwamǝgule, lang sǝ mǝ nǝ amsǝ Isǝrayila? Sǝni, nggurkwar mem nda mǝtankwang a tàu mala Manasa, sǝ mǝ nda rítǎu a ɓala mala tárrám.>>  
\v 16 Sǝ Yahweh banggi wi ama, <<Mbak-kàngkàng mǝ nǝ pà atò, sǝ awu nǝ gandǝ amǝ'Midiyan kǝla ɓwa mwashat na.>>  
\v 17 Sǝ Gidiyon eari wi ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ ǝn kumǝna earmúrú a mǝsǝo ado ka, lǝmdǝam gir'lǝmdǝa mǝnana nǝ̀ lǝmdǝam ama a nda mǝnana a nakiyiam cau ka.  
\v 18 Ida, cè a nying ban mǝnia ka ɗàng she ɓǝn nyarǝna a bano, sǝ ǝn yinǝno nǝ ɓoro mem, ǝn yi nongsǝno wi a ɓadǝmbǝo ka.>> Sǝ Yahweh banggi wi ama, <<Mǝ nǝ kúndǝô sheɓǝ̀ a nyarǝna ka.>> 
\p  
\v 19 Nda Gidiyon wario sǝ kya lam muna mbul, sǝ pàk agbatali bǝredi mǝnana burè pà arǝì raka nǝ muku lita lumi-ɓari nǝ mǝsǝi ɓari. Tsǝk nyame aɓa zace, sǝ mutui ka soe aɓa nkwaring, sǝ yinǝì wi nǝi a tǝrta nggea-nggun, sǝ pe wi.  
\v 20 Mǝturonjar mala Ɓakuli banggi wi ama, <<Twal nyame andǝ bǝredi mana burè pà arǝì raka, nongsǝia amur tali mǝnia ka, sǝ wu solǝ mutui amúrià.>> Sǝ Gidiyon pè anggo.  
\v 21 Pǝlǝa mǝturonjar mala Yahweh lǝmdǝ kún gara mǝnana a bui ka, sǝ je nyame andǝ bǝredi mǝnana burè pà arǝì raka. Kara bǝsa pur nǝ ɓá tali, sǝ pisǝ nyame andǝ bǝredi mǝnana burè pà arǝì raka. Pǝlǝa mǝturonjar mala Yahweh ndǝrmi. 
\p  
\v 22 Lang yi kpani Gidiyon ama mǝturonjar mala Yahweh na ka, Gidiyon bang ama, <<Oi, we Yahweh Ɓakuli! Ado ka ǝn sǝnǝna mǝturonjar mala Yahweh ɓamǝsǝu andǝ ɓamǝsǝu!>> 
\p  
\v 23 Sǝama Yahweh banggi wi ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ rǝo pwalo! Cè ɓangciu pakko ɗàng. A pà wu nǝ wù ɗàng.>>  
\v 24 Pǝlǝa Gidiyon ɓakkî Yahweh gyangŋan abanì, sǝ pe wi lullǝu ama, Yahweh ka dorǝpwala na. Ba yalung, gyangŋanì nakam piu a Ofǝra mala amǝ'kà Abiyeza. 
\s1 Gidiyon arki gyangŋan mala Ba'al 
\p  
\v 25 Aɓa du mǝno ka, Yahweh banggi wi ama, <<Twal jamnda mǝnana a domwan mala tárró ka, nggearǝ ɓaria jamnda, mǝnana mbule tongno-nong-ɓari ka. Sǝ wu arki gyangŋan mala Ba'al mǝnana mala tárró na ka, sǝ wu kasǝki tondong mala Ashera\f + \fr 6:25 \fq tondong mala Ashera \ft Mǝno ka, ɓǝ̀nzál na, gir'lǝmdǝa mala Ashera, ɓakuli mǝɓwame; ɓalli gbal a mǝsǝi 26, 28, 30\ft . \f* mǝnana a nkanggari ka.  
\v 26 Pǝlǝa wu ɓakkì Yahweh Ɓakuli mô gyangŋan amur mǝnia yì kanggǝrang-ban ngga, a kǝkarì. Twal ɓaria jamnda mǝno sǝ wu pa gir'nkila mala pisǝe kǝring nǝi, nǝ tondong mala Ashera mǝnana awu nǝ kasǝki ka.>> 
\p  
\v 27 Nda Gidiyon pwan aɓwana lum atà amǝtúró male sǝ kya pak gìr mǝnana Yahweh banggi wi ama ɓǝ̀ pè ka. Sǝ acemǝnana kǝ ɓanggi amǝɓala mala tárrí andǝ aburana mala là ka, pè nǝ pwari ɗang, nǝ du sǝ kya pê. 
\p  
\v 28 Lang aburana mala là lo nǝ bari ɗiɗyal ka, kara à sǝn gyangŋan mala Ba'al ka à arkini, sǝ tondong mala Ashera mǝnana a nkanggari ka, à kasǝkini, sǝ ɓaria jamnda ka, à pana gir'nkila nǝi amur bǝsa gyangŋan mǝnana à ɓè ka.  
\v 29 À ɗì rǝia ama, <<Yana pàk mǝnia yì gìr ka?>> Sǝ lang à altaban sǝ à ɗikiban ngga, à banggia wia ama, <<Gidiyon muna-ɓwabura mala Johash na pàk mǝnia yì gìr ka.>> 
\p  
\v 30 Pǝlǝa aburana mala lě ne Johash ama, <<Yinǝ muna-ɓwabura mô a nza ace mana ɓǝ̀ wǔ, acemǝnana arkina gyangŋan mala Ba'al sǝ kasǝkina tondong mala Ashera mǝnana a nkanggari ka.>> 
\p  
\v 31 Sǝ Johash ne aɓwana mana kat à lo arǝì ka ama, <<Wun nǝ̀ munǝo ace Ba'al le? Ko ana raka wun nǝ̀ amsǝi le? Ɓwa mǝnana kat nǝ̀ munǝo aceì ka, kaniama ban nǝ̀ kwar ka, à nǝ̀ wal-lui! Ɓǝ̀ yì ka, ɓakuli na ka, ɓǝ̀ munǝo ace ɓamurì, acemǝnana ɓeɓwa arkina gyangŋan male ka.>>  
\v 32 Acemani, a pwari mǝno ka, à tunǝ Gidiyon ama <<Jerub-ba'al,>> ɓalǝi nda, <<Wu nying Ba'al ɓǝ̀ munǝo ace ɓamurì,>> acemǝnana Gidiyon arki wi gyangŋan male ka. 
\s1 Gidiyon ɗice gir'lǝmdǝa 
\p  
\v 33 Amǝ'Midiyan kat, andǝ amǝ'Amalek andǝ aɓwana mana a takuli ka, à ram rǝia abanɓwáná; sǝ à yàl a nkaring Nggeasala Jodan, sǝ à yi bwal kàttì a dulum mala Jezǝril.  
\v 34 Sǝ bangŋo mala Yahweh sulǝ amur Gidiyon, sǝ twang njawe, tunǝ amǝ'Abiyeza ɓǝà kpate.  
\v 35 Tasǝ amǝ'na-túrbân a bù-nzali Manasa, tunǝia ɓǝà yiu atè gbal. Sǝ tasǝ amǝ'na-túrbân arǝ abu-nzali Asha, andǝ Zebulu, andǝ Naftali, sǝ à yiu à yi kumia. 
\p  
\v 36 Gidiyon ne Ɓakuli ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ awu nǝ amsǝ Isǝrayila nǝ buam, kǝla mǝnana a bang ngga,  
\v 37 sǝni mǝ ndo mǝ nǝ tsǝk nggū-nzur a katǝra. Ɓǝ̀ ncimna nǝ̀ kpa amur nggū-nzur nǝmurǝi, sǝ nzali kat nǝ̀ ìm ngga, mǝ nǝ sǝlǝ ama awu nǝ amsǝ Isǝrayila nǝ buam, kǝla mǝnana a bang ngga.>>  
\v 38 Anggo sǝ pǎ. Lang lo ɗiɗyal nǝ dǝmbari ka, yi par nggū-nzur, sǝ pūrǝí; ncimna mana pur arǝì ka lùmsǝ kwar-numur.  
\v 39 Gidiyon ne Ɓakuli ama, <<Cè bumlulla mò earke amuram ɗàng. Mǝ nǝ zǝmbô kusǝ mwashat ɗǝm; ida, nyem ɓǝn mwam cê kusǝ mwashat ɗǝm nǝ nggū-nzur. Ado ka ɓǝ̀ nggū-nzur ime, sǝ ncimna ɓǝ̀ aki nzali kat.>>  
\v 40 A mǝno yì du ka, Ɓakuli pê anggo; nggū-nzurni na ìm nǝmurǝi ka, sǝ ncimna aki nzali kat. 
\c 7  
\s1 Gidiyon gandǝ amǝ'Midiyan 
\p  
\v 1 Nǝ ban'mbul-mbul ka, Jerub-ba'al (yì Gidiyon) andǝ aɓwana mǝnana atè ka, à lo sǝ à yi tsǝk kàttì a nkanggari mgbeaɗe-mùr Harot. Sǝ kàttì mala amǝ'Midiyan ngga, nda a njar-nza nǝ banià aɓa ɓangŋaban, tù a ban Nkono More. 
\p  
\v 2 Yahweh banggi Gidiyon ama, <<Aɓwana mǝnana atò ka, à ɓiki lakkì mǝnana mǝ nǝ pà amǝ'Midiyan a ɓabuia ka, cè Isǝrayila nggoriam ama, <Rǝcandǝa mem nǝ̀ amsǝam.>  
\v 3 Ado ka hambî aɓwana ama, <Ɓwa mǝnana kat rǝì kǝ ɓǝl nǝ ɓangciu ka, ɓǝ̀ wulio ɓǝ̀ nying Nkono Gilǝyat.> >> Nda aɓwana á-lumi-ɓari-nong-ɓari (22,000) nyare à o a là, sǝ aɓwana á-lum (10,000) ue ka. 
\p  
\v 4 Yahweh banggi Gidiyon ama, <<Ɓwapǝndǝa ɓiki lakkì piu. Kyan nǝia a kún mur, sǝ mǝ nǝ mwambo wia kàm. Ɓǝ̀ ǝn nô nǝma, <Ɓwa man, nǝ̀ ká atò ka,> nǝ̀ ká atò; sǝ ɓǝ̀ ǝn nô nǝma, <Mǝnia ka pà nǝ̀ ká atò raka,> pà nǝ̀ ká ɗàng.>>  
\v 5 Pǝlǝa Gidiyon warinǝ aɓwe a kún mur. Sǝ Yahweh banggi wi ama, <<Koyan mǝnana tàkki mur nǝ bui a lasǝi kǝla nvwa ka, tàrrì a buì man; anggo gbal ɓwa mǝnana kūndǝ nǝ nkūnǝi sǝ nu mùr ka, tàrrì a ɓè buì.>>  
\v 6 Aɓwana gbǝman-tàrú (300) na mǝnana à tàkki mur nǝ buia a kunia ka; acilia kat ka à kūndǝo amur ankūnǝia sǝ à nu mùr.  
\v 7 Yahweh banggi Gidiyon ama, <<Nǝ aɓwana mǝnia gbǝman-tàrú (300) mǝnana à tàkki mur nǝ buia ka sǝ mǝ nǝ amsǝo, sǝ mǝ nǝ pà amǝ'Midiyan aɓa buo. Nying acili aɓwana ɓǝà o, koyan ngga a là male.>>  
\v 8 Nda Gidiyon ak agirlina andǝ anjawe gam arǝ acili amǝ'lwa mǝnia sǝ tasǝia ɓǝà o, koyan ngga a gumli male. Sǝ aburana man gbǝman-tàrú (300) ka, banggia wia ɓǝà ueo atè. 
\p Kàttì mala amǝ'Midiyan ngga nda a ɓangŋaban ɓǝ̀ ɓwa sulǝì ban kàttì mala Gidiyon ngga.  
\v 9 Aɓa du mǝno ka, Yahweh banggi Gidiyon ama, <<Lo, sulǝo kyan nǝ munǝo arǝ kàttì mala amǝ'Midiyan acemǝnana ǝn pano wi aɓa buo.  
\v 10 Sǝama ɓǝ̀ ɓangciu kǝ pakko arǝ sulǝ aban ká ka, wu sulǝ wunǝ muna-ɓala mò Pura.  
\v 11 Kwakikiro arǝ cau mǝnana à banggiyi ka, sǝ awu nǝ kum mǝsǝkang-kangŋa mala sulǝo aban ká arǝ kàttì malea.>> Pǝlǝa yì andǝ Pura muna-ɓala male ka, à sulǝ a ban agumli mala aburana mǝnana à tamsǝia a kúnban ace yál amǝ'lwa mana à nda aɓa kùrrǝu aɓa kàttì ka.  
\v 12 Amǝ'Midiyan andǝ amǝ'Amalek andǝ aɓwana mala takuli sulǝna a ɓangŋaban mbǝl-mbǝl kǝla adoshi. Akalakadambi malea làkkì kǝla mǝsǝsala a kun-nggeamur, ɓwa pà nǝ̀ gandǝ ɓallia ɗàng.  
\v 13 Lang Gidiyon yi bingŋǝna ka, kara ok ɓeɓwa na aban ne ɓì lorǝo ama, <<Sǝni! Ən lorǝ ama ɗurǝo bǝredi mǝnana à pe nǝ muku mǝssa-bálì ka, ɗǝnggǝliki aɓa kàttì mala amǝ'Midiyan. Yiu aban ɓè gumli sǝ tùllì nǝ rǝcandǝa, ndǝlì nǝtakwari, sǝ gumlinì kpa a nzali mgbángtâng.>>  
\v 14 Sǝ ɓi earî wi ama, <<Mǝnia ka kǝgir na ɗang, nggeabyau mala Gidiyon muna-ɓwabura mala Johash, ɓwa Isǝrayila na. Ɓakuli pani wi amǝ'Midiyan andǝ kàttì aɓa buì kat.>> 
\p  
\v 15 Lang Gidiyon ok lorǝê andǝ mǝngi ɓalǝi ka, peri aban Ɓakuli. Pǝlǝa nyar a kàttì mala amǝ Isǝrayila sǝ sa'arǝia ama, <<Wu lo! Yahweh pana kàttì mala amǝ'Midiyan aɓa bù wun.>> 
\p  
\v 16 Gau aburana mǝno gbǝman-tàrú ka arǝ anggǝsan tàrú, sǝ pè koyan ngga njawe-gam andǝ muna-bàng mana kùmsǝ ɓukan-bǝsa ka.  
\v 17 Nea wia ama, <<Wu tsǝk mǝsǝ wun arǝàm, sǝ wu pa kǝla mǝnana ǝn pak ka. Lang ǝn warina a kún kàttì malea ka, kǝ gìr mǝnana ǝn pak ka, nda wun nǝ̀ pè ka.  
\v 18 Lang mim sǝnǝ aɓwana mǝnana kat atàm sǝm twangŋǝna anjawe-gam ma'sǝm ngga, pǝlǝa wun a koya buì mala kàttì ka, wun nǝ̀ twang anjawe-gam ma'wun gbal. Sǝ wun nǝ̀ na nǝ gi wun a kuli ama, <Ace Yahweh sǝ ace Gidiyon!> >> 
\p  
\v 19 Nda Gidiyon andǝ aburana gbǝman mana atè ka, à yiu a nkanggariban kàttì mala amǝ'Midiyan tù nǝ ɓadu, anzǝm mana à nggaɗina amǝ'yalban ngga. Pǝlǝa à twang anjawe-gam malea, sǝ à arki amuna-bàng mǝnana a buia ka.  
\v 20 Pǝlǝa anggǝsan mǝno tàrú ka, à twang anjawe-gam malea, sǝ à arki amuna-bàng malea. À bwal aɓukan a buia mǝnggare sǝ anjawe-gam mana à twang ngga a buia mǝlì, sǝ à na bangbang ama, <<Nggeabyau ace Yahweh, sǝ ace Gidiyon!>>  
\v 21 Pǝlǝa koyan ngga cam a bancame male, à gumbǝli kàttì; sǝ amǝ'lwa mala amǝ'Midiyan puppup lo nǝ mire. À ɓangŋa nǝ zwalo a kunia.  
\v 22 Lang aburana mala Gidiyon twang anjawe-gam gbǝman-tàrú ka, Yahweh tsǝk aburana aɓa kàttì à pǝlǝ arǝarǝia nǝ anggeabyau malea. Amǝ'lwa ɓang aban ká ɗār a Bet-Shita; à dǝshi Zerera aban ká ɗār a nzong-nzali mala Abel-Mehola, tù a ban Tabbat.  
\v 23 Aburana mala amǝ Isǝrayila a tàu mala Naftali, andǝ Asha, andǝ Manasa kat ka, à tunǝia sǝ à pyangnǝata amǝ'Midiyan.  
\v 24 Pǝlǝa Gidiyon tasǝ amǝ'na-túrbân arǝ abân aɓa nzali múr-ankono mala Ifǝrem nǝ cau ama, <<Wu sulǝ arǝ amǝ'Midiyan, sǝ wu tsǝk amǝ'yálban a koya mgbeaɗe-mùr, andǝ myalmúr, andǝ tūli-mùr, aban ká ɗār a Bet-Bara. \f + \fr 7:24 \fq wu yál Nggeasala Jodan \ft ko <<wu yál abân yálì nkaring mùr mala Jodan.>> \f*Sǝ wu yál Nggeasala Jodan.>> 
\p Anggo sǝ à tunǝ aburana mala tàu mala Ifǝrem kat, sǝ à yi ak amgbeaɗe-mùr, andǝ amyalmúr, andǝ atūli-mùr, aban ká ɗār a Bet-Bara. Sǝ à yál Nggeasala Jodan.  
\v 25 À bwalki ayálu ɓari mala amǝ'Midiyan, Orep andǝ Zip. À wal-lú Orep amur tali mala Orep, sǝ Zip ka à wal-luí a ban kam mùr-anap mala Zip. À pǝrta amǝ'Midiyan sǝ à yinǝ aɓamur Orep andǝ Zip aban Gidiyon, a nkaring Jodan. 
\c 8  
\p  
\v 1 Pǝlǝa aburana mala tàu mala Ifǝrem ɗì Gidiyon ama, <<Palang sǝ a pakka sǝm anggo? Ace mana sǝ awu nǝ o a munǝo arǝ amǝ'Midiyan ngga a ginǝ tunǝ sǝm?>> À munǝki arǝì kǝ̀rkǝ́r.  
\v 2 Sǝ yì ka banggia wia ama, <<Mana ǝn pa ado mǝnana à nǝ̀ kārǝi arǝ wun ngga? Ɓakurikuri mala aɓǝla-anap mala Ifǝrem kútì pwan-gìrɓaban mala Abiyeza re?  
\v 3 Ɓakuli pana ayálu mala amǝ'Midiyan, yià Orep andǝ Zip a ɓabu wun; sǝ mana ǝn gandǝ pa mǝnana à nǝ̀ kārǝi arǝ wun ngga?>> Pǝlǝa bumlulla malea arǝì sulǝo lang bang cau mǝnia ka. 
\s1 Gidiyon masǝlǝ limurǝm amur amǝ'Midiyan 
\p  
\v 4 Pǝlǝa Gidiyon andǝ aburana male mǝno gbǝman-tàrú ka, à yiu a Nggeasala Jodan sǝ à yàl a nkaring; sǝ kat andǝ aulǝa malea ka, à lidǝmba nǝ pǝrtau.  
\v 5 Lang à yiu a Sukkot ka, Gidiyon banggi amǝ Sukkot ama, <<Ida, wu pè amǝ'lwa mem girlina; à gandǝna, sǝ mim ngga mǝ ndarǝ pǝrta Zeba andǝ Zalmuna, amurǝma mala amǝ'Midiyan piu.>> 
\p  
\v 6 Sǝ aɓwana-mǝgule mala Sukkot bang ama, <<A gbamina Zeba andǝ Zalmuna a ɓabuo sǝ sǝm nǝ̀ pè amǝ'lwa mô girlina le?>>  
\v 7 Gidiyon bang ama, <<Anzǝm mana Yahweh pana Zeba andǝ Zalmuna a ɓabuam ngga, mǝ nǝ yia koàkì wun nǝ zwe ɓabondo andǝ galamba.>>  
\v 8 Gidiyon lo kano ka wari a Penǝwel sǝ zǝmbia wia kǝla mǝno ka; sǝ aburana mala Penǝwel nyesǝi wi kǝ cau mala amǝ Sukkot.  
\v 9 Sǝ ne amǝ Penǝwel ama, <<Lang ǝn linamurǝm sǝ ǝn nyarna ka, mǝ nǝ yia arki mǝnia yì nda-mǝ'dāhre ka.>> 
\p  
\v 10 Anggo ka, Zeba andǝ Zalmuna na a Karkor nǝ amǝ'lwa malea, aburana kǝla á-lum-bwamdǝ-tongno (15,000). À nda kǝ aburana mǝnana à ueo aɓalǝ amǝ'lwa mala aɓwana mana à yiu nǝ takuli ka; aɓwana á-gbǝman-mwashat nǝ á-lumi-ɓari (120,000) mala amǝ'lwa malea mǝnana à bwal nggeabyau ka, à walna-luia.  
\v 11 Gidiyon eau nǝ njargula mala amǝ'do aɓalǝ agumli, nǝ takuli mala Noba andǝ Jogbeha, sǝ yasǝlǝ amǝ'Midiyan a kàttì malea nǝ munǝo lang à nda aɓa do ɗwanyi-tsǝk'mǝsǝu ka.  
\v 12 Amurǝma mala amǝ'Midiyan ɓari, Zeba andǝ Zalmuna, tǝlli nǝ mire, sǝ yì ka pǝrtea yi bwalia, sǝ zurìmúr amǝ'lwa malea kat.  
\v 13 Anzǝm mǝno ka, Gidiyon muna-ɓwabura mala Johash nyarî kun-munǝo nǝ njar eauwe mala Heres.  
\v 14 Yi bwal ɓè mǝlagga a Sukkot sǝ ɗìkí, sǝ mǝlaggè gilǝî wi alullǝ amǝbuno andǝ aɓwana-mǝgule mala Sukkot, aburana lumi-tongno-nong-ɓari nǝ mǝsǝi tongno-nong-ɓari (77).  
\v 15 Pǝlǝa Gidiyon yiu aban aburana mala Sukkot sǝ banggia wia ama, <<Wu sǝni, Zeba andǝ Zalmuna nya ka; yià mǝnana wu \f + \fr 8:15 \fq nam nggaro cau \ft ko <<kyauwikiam>>\f*nam nggaro cau amúrià ama, <A gbamina Zeba andǝ Zalmuna a ɓabuo, sǝ sǝm nǝ̀ pè amǝ'lwa mô girlina le ka?> >>  
\v 16 Pǝlǝa Gidiyon bwalki aɓwana-mǝgule mala lê, sǝ kasǝ zwe ɓabondo andǝ galamba sǝ koàkia nǝi, ace kania amǝ Sukkot gìrkànì.  
\v 17 Sǝ yi arki nda-mǝ'dāhre mala Penǝwel sǝ wal-lú aburana mala lê. 
\p  
\v 18 Sǝ pǝlǝa ɗì Zeba andǝ Zalmuna ama, <<Aburana mǝnana wu wal-luia a Tabo ka, aya ulang aburana na?>> Sǝ à pa eare ama, <<Aburana na kǝla we, à pur amuna murǝm.>>  
\v 19 Gidiyon pǝlǝia wia ama, <<Amǝ'eambam, amuna mala nggem na. Mbak-kàngkàng Yahweh nakam ngga, ɓǝ̀ wu nyingŋǝnia nǝyilǝmu ka, ɓǝ́ pà mǝ nǝ wal-lú wun ɗàng.>>  
\v 20 Sǝ pǝlǝa aban muna-dǝmba male, yì Jeta, sǝ ne wi ama, <<Lo wal-luia!>> Sǝama mǝlagge ka, kwetǝ nggeabyau male ɗàng, acemǝnana yì ka muna na piu, ɓangciu kǝ pakkì wi. 
\p  
\v 21 Pǝlǝa Zeba andǝ Zalmuna banggi Gidiyon ama, <<Lo wàl sǝm nǝ nggearǝo; kǝla mǝnana ɓwabura pak ka, anggo sǝ rǝcandǝa male pǎ.>> Nda Gidiyon lo wal-lú Zeba andǝ Zalmuna, sǝ pusǝki anjengǝlan mǝnana a myal akalakadambi malea ka. 
\s1 Gidiyon pak ɓǝ̀nzál mala efot 
\p  
\v 22 Anzǝm mǝno ka, amǝ Isǝrayila banggi Gidiyon ama, <<Duk murǝm amur sǝm, we wunǝ munio, andǝ mǝkeo gbal, acemǝnana a amsǝna sǝm a ɓabu amǝ'Midiyan.>>  
\v 23 Sǝ Gidiyon banggia wia ama, <<Pà mǝ nǝ duk murǝm amur wun ɗàng, sǝ munem pà nǝ̀ duk murǝm amur wun ɗàng. Yahweh na nǝ̀ duk murǝm amur wun ngga.>>  
\v 24 Sǝama banggia wia ama, <<Mǝ ndanǝ zǝmba aban wun; nǝma koya ɓwa atà wun ngga, ɓǝ̀ pam gìrkiru aɓalǝ agǝna-lwa mǝnana wu ea arǝ aɓiwun amǝbura ka.>> (Aɓia-mǝbura ka amǝ'Ishmayel na, sǝ à kǝ oasǝ agirkiru mala bolo-njengǝlan.) 
\p  
\v 25 À pa eare ama, <<Sǝm nǝ po wia nǝ banɓoarnado.>> Pǝlǝa à sárǝ́ lagir, sǝ koya ɓwanani ka, túr agirkiru mala gǝna-lwa male aɓalǝi.  
\v 26 Sǝ dǝmbǝrya mala agirkiru bolo-njengǝlan mǝnana zǝm ngga nda, shekel á-mwashat nǝ gbǝman-tongno-nong-ɓari (1,700), tsǝa-amur anjengǝlan andǝ agirɓamyalu andǝ alagir mala amurǝma mǝnana amurǝma mala amǝ'Midiyan oasǝ arǝia ka, andǝ anlang-bolo mǝnana a myal akalakadambi malea ka.  
\v 27 Gidiyon pàk efot nǝi sǝ tsǝì aɓa Ofǝra nggea-là male. Sǝ Isǝrayila kat ka, à kùti a gyatàrǝia nǝ ká peri a baní kǝla nkúl, sǝ yi dupi Gidiyon andǝ amǝɓala male gbǝli. 
\p  
\v 28 Anggo sǝ amǝ Isǝrayila ɓùn amǝ'Midiyan aɓatea sǝ à loasǝ múrià ɗǝm ɗang. Sǝ nzali dum nǝ rǝpwala ba pǝlǝa lumi-ine a do-yilǝmu mala Gidiyon. 
\s1 Isǝrayila purî-njar a nzǝm lú mala Gidiyon 
\p  
\v 29 Jerub-ba'al muna-ɓwabura mala Johash nyar a là male kya dukam.  
\v 30 Gidiyon ngga, ndanǝ amuna-burana lumi-tongno-nong-ɓari (70) mǝnana à ɓǝli wi ka, acemǝnana ndanǝ amamǝna pas.  
\v 31 Mā-twala male mǝnana nda a Shekem ngga ɓǝli wi muna-ɓwabura gbal, mǝnana pe wi lullǝu ama, Abimale ka.  
\v 32 Sǝ Gidiyon muna-ɓwabura mala Johash ka, è kutsuk sǝ pàk-lú, sǝ à tsǝì a ɓembe-ɓa-tali mala tárrí Johash a Ofǝra, là mala nggurkwar mala Abiyeza. 
\p  
\v 33 Lú mala Gidiyon nda mǝkwane, amǝ Isǝrayila pǝlǝ ɗǝm à kùti a gyatarǝu atà aBa'al. À tsǝk Ba'al-berit duk ɓakuli malea.  
\v 34 À ɗenyinǝ Yahweh Ɓakuli malea, mǝnana amsǝia a bù ka aɓia-mǝbura a koya buì ka ɗàng.  
\v 35 Sǝ à lǝmdǝì ɓala mala Jerub-ba'al (yì Gidiyon) pěmǝɓoarne ace agir mǝɓoarne mǝnana pakkî Isǝrayila ka ɗàng. 
\c 9  
\s1 Abimale wal-lú amǝ'eambi 
\p  
\v 1 Abimale muna-ɓwabura mala \f + \fr 9:1 \fq Jerub-ba'al \ft ka nda Gidiyon.\f*Jerub-ba'al wari a Shekem a ɓè pwari ace sǝn akíne, sǝ nacau nǝia andǝ ɓala-kau mala nggè puppup, ama,  
\v 2 <<Ida, wu banggi aɓwana-mǝgule mala Shekem kat mǝnia yì cau ka ama, <Mǝye nani na ɓoara wun: amuna-burana lumi-tongno-nong-ɓari mala Jerub-ba'al kat ɓǝà yálmúr wun le, ko ɓwa mwashat ɓǝ̀ yálmúr wun?> Wu ɗenyi ama, mǝ nda nkila wun andǝ nyam wun.>>  
\v 3 Akína Abimale banggi aɓwana-mǝgule mala Shekem kat acau mǝnana kat Abimale nea wia ka. Ɓabum aɓwana-mǝgule man o arǝ Abimale; acemǝnana à bang ama, <<Yì ka ɓǝla ma'sǝm na ka.>>  
\v 4 À pe wi agbatali bolo-azǝrfa shekel lumi-tongno-nong-ɓari mǝnana à twal aɓa ndà mala Ba'al-berit ka. Pǝlǝa Abimale pàktúró nǝ boale, sǝ kya kúrna aɓwana-mǝɓane andǝ amǝ'yàl-nzongcau nǝi, ɓǝà duk amǝkpate.  
\v 5 Wari a ɓala mala tárrí a Ofǝra, sǝ wal-lú amǝ'eambi, yià amuna-burana lumi-tongno-nong-ɓari mala Jerub-ba'al, amúr tali mwashat. Kǝ Jotam, muna-ɓwabura mǝtankwang mala Jerub-ba'al, nda mǝnana ueo nǝmurǝi à wal-lui raka, acemǝnana ɓangŋa sǝmbǝrǝa.  
\v 6 Aɓwana-mǝgule mala Shekem kat andǝ Bet-Millo kat ramba abanɓwáná, sǝ à pè Abimale murǝm, tù aban nggun-mǝgule mǝnana cam a Shekem ngga. 
\s1 Kanicau mala Jotam 
\m  
\v 7 Lang Jotam ok man yì cau ka, wario kya cam a ɓong \f + \fr 9:7 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Nggur 11:29; 27:12; Jes 8:33; Yoh 4:20\ft .\f*Nkono Gerizim, sǝ loasǝ gi kpǝm nea wia ama: 
\q1 Wu kwakikir wun arǝàm, 
\q1 wun aɓwana-mǝgule mala Shekem, 
\q2 ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ Ɓakuli kwakikiri arǝ wun ngga. 
\q1  
\v 8 Ɓè pwari nakam mǝnana anggun ram rǝia, 
\q1 à nǝ̀ twalî ɓamúrià murǝm. 
\q1 À banggi nggun-olif ama, 
\q1 <<Duk murǝm ma'sǝm.>> 
\q1  
\v 9 Sǝama nggun-olif nyesǝia wia cau ama, 
\q1 <<Mǝ nying pusǝ mùrú mem, 
\q1 mǝnana à kǝ pángŋǝ̀nà-túró nǝi 
\q1 ace gusǝlǝ Ɓakuli andǝ aɓwapǝndǝa ka, 
\q2 ace wuliki amúr anggun le?>> 
\q1  
\v 10 Pǝlǝa anggun banggi nggun-vwari ama, 
\q1 <<Yiu duk murǝm ma'sǝm.>> 
\q1  
\v 11 Sǝ nggun-vwari nyesǝia wia cau ama, 
\q1 <<Mǝ nying pusǝ ɓǝlanggun mem mǝ'pǝlpǝlni, 
\q1 andǝ ɓǝlanggun mem mǝɓoarne, 
\q2 ace wuliki amúr anggun le?>> 
\q1  
\v 12 Pǝlǝa anggun banggi nggun-anap ama, 
\q1 <<Yiu duk murǝm ma'sǝm.>> 
\q1  
\v 13 Sǝ nggun-anap nyesǝia wia cau ama, 
\q1 <<Mǝ nying pusǝ mùr-anap mem, 
\q1 mǝnana kǝ pwasǝbum Ɓakuli andǝ aɓwapǝndǝa ka, 
\q2 ace wuliki amúr anggun le?>> 
\q1  
\v 14 Nda anggun kat banggi zwe ama, 
\q1 <<Yiu duk murǝm ma'sǝm.>> 
\q1  
\v 15 Zwe eari anggun ama, 
\q1 <<Ɓǝ̀ wu kǝ earce ama wun nǝ̀ twalam nǝ mǝsǝcau, 
\q1 mǝ duk murǝm ma'wun ngga, 
\q1 she wun nǝ̀ yiu aɓata yilǝm mem ace kum-àwá! 
\q1 Sǝ ɓǝ̀ pà anggo raka, ɓǝ̀ bǝsa pur aɓa zwe, 
\q1 sǝ ɓǝ̀ pisǝ \f + \fr 9:15 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 1Amur 4:33; 2Amur 14:9; 19:23; Ang 104:16; Isha 2:13; 37:24\ft .\f*anggun-seda mala Lebano.>> 
\m  
\v 16 <<Ado ka, wun nǝ̀ gandǝ na mbak-kàngkàng ama wu lǝmdǝna domǝsǝcau andǝ ɗwanyicau-arǝǔ nǝ pe Abimale murǝm le? Wu pàngŋǝ́nì Jerub-ba'al andǝ ɓala male gìr mǝnana nda pepè ka le? Sǝ wu mbwenì kǝla mǝnana karǝa arǝ atúró male ka le?  
\v 17 Wu ɗenyi ama tárrám twal yilǝmi a kún bui ace amsǝ wun a ɓabù amǝ'Midiyan.  
\v 18 Sǝ yalung ngga, ndya wu longŋǝ́nà arǝ ɓala mala tárrám. Wu walna-lú amuna-burana male lumi-tongno-nong-ɓari amúr tali mwashat, sǝ wu tsǝ̀ngŋǝ̀nà Abimale muna-ɓwabura mala mā-twala male, ɓǝ̀ duk murǝm amúr aɓwana-mǝgule mala Shekem, acemǝnana yì ka ɓǝla ma'wun na ka.  
\v 19 Adyan ngga, ɓǝ̀ gìr mǝnana wu pàkkî Jerub-ba'al andǝ ɓala male yalung ngga, gìr mǝɓoarne na, sǝ mǝ'mǝsǝcaunì na ka, ɓǝ̀ bum wun pwasǝ arǝ Abimale, sǝ yì gbal ka ɓǝ̀ bumi pwasǝ arǝ wun.  
\v 20 Sǝ ɓǝ̀ pà anggo raka, ɓǝ̀ bǝsa pùr nǝban Abimale ɓǝ̀ pisǝ aɓwana-mǝgule mala Shekem andǝ Bet-Millo! Sǝ ɓǝ̀ bǝsa pùr gbal nǝban aɓwana-mǝgule mala Shekem andǝ Bet-Millo ɓǝ̀ pisǝ Abimale.>> 
\p  
\v 21 Pǝlǝa Jotam ɓangŋa o a Biya, sǝ kya do abanì \f + \fr 9:21 \fq atàcau mala \ft ko <<ace upì ɓadǝm>>\f*atàcau mala mǝ'eambi Abimale. 
\s1 Ɓakuli lumsǝ suban mala Jotam 
\p  
\v 22 Abimale yálmúr amǝ Isǝrayila apǝlǝa tàrú.  
\v 23 Pǝlǝa Ɓakuli tasǝ ɓè bangŋo mǝɓike ɓǝ̀ loasǝ ɓibura anre Abimale andǝ aɓwana-mǝgule mala Shekem; sǝ aɓwana-mǝgule mala Shekem lǝmdǝ ɗwanyi-domǝsǝcau arǝ Abimale.  
\v 24 Ɓakuli pàk mǝnia ka ace mǝnana caukpaka mala ɓealɓikea mǝnana à pàkkî amuna-burana lumi-tongno-nong-ɓari mala Jerub-ba'al, andǝ bafe mala nkilia mana à sukkì ka, ɓǝ̀ sulǝ amur Abimale mǝ'eambia, sǝ amur aɓwana-mǝgule mala Shekem mǝnana à bwali wi wal-lú amǝ'eambi ka.  
\v 25 Aɓwana-mǝgule mala Shekem mgbicau arǝ Abimale, sǝ à tasǝ aburana ɓǝà kya kùmsǝî wi amúr ankono, sǝ à ɓǝmbǝri koyan kat mǝnana gya pǝlǝ nǝbania amur njargula mǝno ka. Pǝlǝa cê yi kpa a kir Abimale. 
\p  
\v 26 Pǝlǝa Ga'al muna-ɓwabura mala Ebet, yiu andǝ amǝ'eambi sǝ à yi do a Shekem. Aɓwana-mǝgule mala Shekem tsǝkɓalǝia arǝ Ga'al.  
\v 27 Amǝ Shekem wari arǝ aɓaban-anap malea. À ram ɓǝla-anap sǝ à kàmgi mùrì ace pàkkiɗire. Pǝlǝa à kùtí a ndà mala ɓakuli malea sǝ à lìli, à nu, sǝ à sú Abimale.  
\v 28 Sǝ Ga'al muna-ɓwabura mala Ebet nacau ama, <<Yana nda Abimale, sǝ palang sǝ sǝm amǝ Shekem ngga, sǝm nǝ̀ nyesǝ ɓamur rǝ sǝm aɓate? Yì ka nda muna-ɓwabura mala Jerub-ba'al re? Sǝ Zebul ka nda mǝkwaɗitè mǝnana twal ka re? Wu kpata amǝɓala mala \f + \fr 9:28 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Tite 34:2,6\ft .\f*Hamo, tár Shekem! Palang sǝ sǝm nǝ̀ kpata Abimale?  
\v 29 Ɓǝ̀ duk mǝni'ama, aɓwana man ngga, à nda aɓata rǝcandǝa mem ngga, ɓǝ́ mǝ nǝ pusǝ Abimale!>> Mǝ nǝ ne Abimale ama, <<Kyane kya hatǝki amǝ'lwa mô sǝ wu pur atàm ɓǝ̀ sǝm munǝo!>>  
\v 30 Lang Zebul mǝ'yálmúr nggea-lê ok acau mala Ga'al muna-ɓwabura mala Ebet ka, bumi lul kǝ̀rkǝ́r.  
\v 31 Pǝlǝa Zebul tasǝ amǝ'na-túrbân aban Abimale a Aruma,\f + \fr 9:31 \fq Aruma \ft ko <<aɓa sǝmbǝrǝa>>\f* nǝ cau ama, <<Sǝni, Ga'al muna-ɓwabura mala Ebet andǝ amǝ'eambi yina a Shekem, sǝ à ndaban soakita aɓwana mala nggea-là ɓǝà mgbicau arǝò.  
\v 32 Ado ka, lo wunǝa aburana mǝnana atò ka nǝ du, wu yi kumsǝ a ɓabondo anzǝm nggea-là.  
\v 33 Nǝ dǝmbari, a eauwe mala pwari ka, wu ndashi amur nggea-là nǝ munǝo. Sǝ lang Ga'al nǝ̀ pur andǝ aburana mǝnana atè ace yiu a munǝo arǝò ka, pàkkia wia gìr mǝnana buo kumi nǝ̀ pàk ka.>> 
\p  
\v 34 Nda Abimale andǝ aburana mǝnana atè kat ka, à lo nǝ du sǝ à kya kumsǝ anzǝm Shekem; à gau rǝia arǝ abanì ine.  
\v 35 Lang Ga'al muna-ɓwabura mala Ebet puro yi cam a bankutio mala kún nggea-là ka, Abimale andǝ aburana mǝnana atè ka à loapi ban mǝnana à kùmsǝ kam ngga.  
\v 36 Sǝ lang Ga'al sǝn aburane ka, ne Zebul ama, <<Sǝni, aburana naban sulǝì múr ankono aban yiu.>> Sǝ Zebul ne wi ama, <<Yilǝmi ankono na a kǝ̀ sǝnia kǝla aɓwapǝndǝa na ka.>>  
\v 37 Ga'al nacau ɗǝm ama, <<Sǝni! Aɓwana no à kǝ sulǝî tsùrú mala nzali man ngga. Sǝ ɓè nggǝsan no kǝ yiu nǝban njar mala Nggun-mǝgule mala Mǝ'nggár ka.>>  
\v 38 Pǝlǝa Zebul ne wi ama, <<Acau gusǝlǝ-múrû mô na ke? We mǝnana a bang ama, <Yana nda Abimale mana sǝm nǝ̀ kpate ka?> Aburana mǝnia na a ɓǝsǝkia ka re? Pur ado kya munǝ arǝia!>>  
\v 39 Nda Ga'al puro sǝ dupi aɓwana-mǝgule mala Shekem a dǝmba, sǝ à munǝ arǝ Abimale.  
\v 40 Abimale pǝrta Ga'al sǝ ɓang a ɓadǝmbi. Amǝ Shekem pas kpakia, à kum penye a bankutio mala kún nggea-lê.  
\v 41 Abimale nyar a Aruma, sǝ Zebul pǝr Ga'al andǝ amǝ'eambi à purî ɓá Shekem. 
\p  
\v 42 Lang bankwarna ka, amǝ Shekem puro, à o a njenza. Lang Abimale ok cê ka,  
\v 43 twal aburana male sǝ gauwia arǝ abanì tàrú, sǝ à kumsǝ a ɓabondo. Lang sǝn aɓwana kǝ purì ɓá nggea-là aban yiu ka, lo sǝ soa-munǝo arǝia, wal-luia.  
\v 44 Pǝlǝa Abimale andǝ nggǝsan aɓwana mana atè ka à ɓangŋa à kya cam a bankutio mala kún nggea-là. Sǝ anggǝsan ɓari mala aɓwana mala Abimale ka à soa-munǝo sǝ wal-lú aɓwana mǝnana kat a njenza ka.  
\v 45 A pwari mǝno kat ka, Abimale munǝ-munǝo arǝ nggea-là. Ak nggea-lê sǝ wal-lú aɓwana mǝnana kat aɓa nggea-lê ka. Pǝlǝa bǝbbǝriki nggea-lê sǝ mesǝki tuɓamur amurí. 
\p  
\v 46 Lang aɓwana-mǝgule mala ndà-kulí mǝ'dāhre mala Shekem ok cê ka, à kùtí aɓa kanggǝrang-ban mala ndà mala El-berit.\f + \fr 9:46 \fq El-berit \ft ɓè lullǝu mala Ba'al-berit\f* 
\v 47 Cau yi bik ban Abimale ama, aɓwana-mǝgule mala ndà-kulí mǝ'dāhre mala Shekem ramǝna abanɓwáná.  
\v 48 Nda Abimale andǝ aburana mǝnana kat atè ka à eau amúr Nkono \f + \fr 9:48 \fq Zalmon \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Ang 68:14\ft .\f*Zalmon. Sǝ Abimale twal bero a bui sǝ kasǝ bu-nggun, loasǝi tsǝì a kwàrì. Sǝ banggi aburana mǝnana atè ka ama, <<Gìr mǝnana wu sǝni ǝn pê ka, wu fà rǝ wun, wu pè kǝla mǝnana ǝn pàk ka.>>  
\v 49 Nda koyan ateà ka kasǝ bu-nggun gbal, sǝ à kpata Abimale. À tsǝk abu-nggunì arǝ kanggǝrang-ban mala ndà mala El-berit, sǝ à soaki wi bǝsa. Aɓwana mǝnana kat aɓa ndà-kulí mǝ'dāhre mala Shekem ngga à wù kat, aɓwana kǝla á-mwashat (1,000), aburana andǝ amamǝna. 
\p  
\v 50 Pǝlǝa Abimale wari a Tebez, tsǝk kàttì kàm, soa-munǝo arǝì sǝ é.  
\v 51 Kanggǝrang ndà-kulí mǝ'dāhre nakam a tsùrú mala nggea-lê, nda aburana andǝ amamǝna andǝ aɓwana-mǝgule mala nggea-lê ɓangŋa, à kutiki aɓalǝi sǝ à gìrkún ɓamuria aɓalǝi. Pǝlǝa à eauwe à bik múr-kurǝm.  
\v 52 Abimale yiu sǝ soa-munǝo arǝ ndà-kulí mǝ'dāhrenì. Sǝama lang gbashì kún ndà-kulí mǝ'dāhrenì nǝ̀ soaki wi bǝsa ka,  
\v 53 kara ɓè ɓwama a múr-kurǝm, túr muna-taligo amur Abimale, ar nkpoula-ɓamuri.  
\v 54 Pǝlǝa Abimale tunǝ lagga mǝ-bwali-wi agirmunǝo male akaurǝa, sǝ banggi wi ama, <<Kwetǝ nggeabyau mô, wal-luem, ace mǝnana ɓǝà kǝa na amuram ama, <Ɓwama na mǝnana wal-luí ka> ɗàng.>>  
\v 55 Lang amǝ Isǝrayila sǝni Abimale wuna ka, koyanale ka nyar a là male. 
\p  
\v 56 Ɓakuli nyesǝì Abimale mǝɓike mǝnana pàkkî tárrí, nǝ wal-lú amǝ'eambi lumi-tongno-nong-ɓari ka.  
\v 57 Ɗǝm ngga Ɓakuli tsǝk mǝɓike mǝnana aburana mala Shekem pè ka ɓǝ̀ nyar amúrià, sǝ suban mǝnana Jotam muna-ɓwabura mala Jerub-ba'al ne ka, yi sulǝ amúrià. 
\c 10  
\s1 Tola andǝ Jayir 
\p  
\v 1 Anzǝm lú mala Abimale ka, Tola muna-ɓwabura mala Puwa, mǝ'kà Dodo, a tàu mala Isaka, lo ace amsǝ amǝ Isǝrayila. Yì Tola ka, do a Shamir aɓa nzali múr-ankono mala Ifǝrem.  
\v 2 Yì ka, duk kasǝla amúr amǝ Isǝrayila apǝlǝa lumi-ɓari-nong-tàrú, sǝ yi wú. À tsǝì a Shamir. 
\p  
\v 3 Anzǝm Tola ka, Jayir ɓwa Gilǝyat lo, sǝ duk kasǝla amúr amǝ Isǝrayila apǝlǝa lumi-ɓari-nong-ɓari.  
\v 4 Jayir ndanǝ amuna-burana lumi-tàrú mǝnana à kǝ gya a nzǝm amǝdambǝriso lumi-tàrú ka, sǝ à yálmúr alá lumi-tàrú a Gilǝyat. À kǝ tunǝ amǝno yì alá ka ama Havot-Jayir\f + \fr 10:4 \fq Havot-Jayir \ft ko alá aɓata yálmúrû mala Jayir\f* bà yalung.  
\v 5 Jayir paklú sǝ à tsǝkbani a Kamon. 
\s1 Amǝ'Amon andǝ amǝ'Filisti par amǝ'Isǝrayila 
\p  
\v 6 Amǝ Isǝrayila pàk gìr mǝɓike ɗǝm, a sǝne mala Yahweh.\f + \fr 10:6 \ft Sǝni gbal aɓa: \xt Akas 2:11-13\ft .\f* À peri aban aBa'al andǝ Ashtarot, aɓakuli mala amǝ'Suriya, andǝ aɓakuli mala amǝ'Sidon, andǝ aɓakuli mala amǝ'Mowap, andǝ aɓakuli mala amǝ'Amon, andǝ aɓakuli mala amǝ'Filisti. \f + \fr 10:6 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Nggur 31:16\ft .\f*À vwakibuia arǝ Yahweh, sǝ à nying peri abani.  
\v 7 Nda bumlulla mala Yahweh earke amúr amǝ Isǝrayila, sǝ tasǝia a ɓabù amǝ'Filisti andǝ amǝ'Amon\f + \fr 10:7 \ft Sǝni gbal aɓa: \xt Akas 2:14\ft .\f* ngga.  
\v 8 Amǝ'Filisti andǝ amǝ'Amon par amǝ Isǝrayila sǝ à betia aɓa pǝlǝa mǝno. À par amǝ Isǝrayila ba apǝlǝa lum-bwamdǝ-tongno-nong-tàrú, yià amǝ Isǝrayila mǝnana kat à ndanǝdo a takuli mala Jodan, a nzali mala amǝ'Amor, mǝnana nda aɓa Gilǝyat ka.  
\v 9 Pǝlǝa amǝ'Amon gbal ka à yàlî Nggeasala Jodan ace kánǝ munǝo arǝ amǝ'tàu mala Yahuda, andǝ amǝ'tàu mala Benjami, sǝ arǝ ɓala-kàu mala Ifǝrem. Amǝ Isǝrayila tanni kǝ̀rkǝ́r. 
\p  
\v 10 Nda amǝ Isǝrayila ɓua aban Yahweh ama: <<Sǝm pàngŋǝ́nò cauɓikea. Sǝm pǝlǝna nzǝm sǝm arǝò, we Ɓakuli ma'sǝm, sǝ sǝm kpanata aBa'al.>>  
\v 11 Sǝ Yahweh earî amǝ Isǝrayila ama, <<Ən amsǝ wun a ɓabù amǝ'Masar, andǝ amǝ'Amor, andǝ amǝ'Amon, andǝ amǝ'Filisti re?  
\v 12 Ɗǝm ngga lang amǝ'Sidon, andǝ amǝ'Amalek, andǝ amǝ'Mawon\f + \fr 10:12 \fq amǝ'Mawon \ft ko <<amǝ'Midiyan>>\f* par wun aɓata tanni, sǝ wu ɓua abanam ngga, ǝn amsǝ wun a ɓabuia.  
\v 13 Sǝ kat andǝ mǝno ka, wu pǝlǝ nzǝm wun arǝàm, wu kpata aɓea aɓakuli. Acemani ka, pà Mǝ nǝ amsǝ wun ɗǝm ɗàng.  
\v 14 Wu kyane, wu kya ɓua aban aɓakuli mǝnana wu twal ka; ɓǝà amsǝ wun a pwari mǝnana wu kùtí aɓa tanni ka.>> 
\p  
\v 15 Sǝ amǝ Isǝrayila zǝmbî Yahweh ama, <<Sǝm pàngŋǝ̀nà cauɓikea. Pàk gìr mǝnana kat a kǝ sǝni nda pepè awu nǝ pangnǝ sǝm ngga, sǝama, ida amsǝ sǝm yalung.>>  
\v 16 Nda amǝ Isǝrayila pusǝki abǝri ɓakuli mǝnana aɓalǝia ka, à sukkia, sǝ à peri aban Yahweh ka. A masǝlǝate ka, \f + \fr 10:16 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Akas 2:18; Isha 63:9\ft .\f*Yahweh yi aulǝ nǝ sǝn tanni mǝɓike mǝnana amǝ Isǝrayila kǝ nu ka. 
\p  
\v 17 Amǝ'lwa mala amǝ'Amon ram rǝia abanɓwáná, sǝ à kya tsǝk kàttì malea aɓa Gilǝyat; amǝ Isǝrayila gbal ka, à ram rǝia abanɓwáná sǝ à kya tsǝk kàttì malea a Mizpa aɓa Gilǝyat.  
\v 18 Aɓwana-mǝgule amur Gilǝyat\f + \fr 10:18 \fq Gilǝyat \ft ko <<amǝ Isǝrayila mǝnana a bù-nzali Gilǝyat ka>>\f* ne arǝarǝia ama, <<Ɓwa mana nǝ̀ tita kánǝ munǝo arǝ amǝ'Amon ngga, ɓwê na nǝ̀ duk múrû amúr aɓwana puppup mǝnana ndanǝdo a Gilǝyat ka.>>\f + \fr 10:18 \ft Sǝni gbal aɓa: \xt Akas 11:5-6,8,11\ft .\f* 
\c 11  
\s1 Jefta duk Kasǝla mala Isǝrayila 
\p  
\v 1 A bàkú mǝno ka, Jefta\f + \fr 11:1 \fq Jefta \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 1Sam 12:11; Ib 11:32\ft .\f* ɓwa Gilǝyat ka, nggea kanggǝrang mǝ'lwa na, sǝama yi ka, muna mala mā-gyatarǝu na. Gilǝyat nda tár Jefta.  
\v 2 Mālá Gilǝyat ɓǝlî Gilǝyat amuna-burana. Sǝ lang amuna-burana mala māmí gulkina ka, à pǝ̀r Jefta, sǝ à banggi wi ama, <<A pà nǝ kum liɓala aɓa ɓala mala tár sǝm ɗàng, acemǝnana a nda muna mala ɓè ɓwama ɗàng.>>  
\v 3 Pǝlǝa Jefta ɓanggi amǝ'eambi, sǝ kya do a nzali Top,\f + \fr 11:3 \fq Top \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 2Sam 10:6,8\ft .\f* sǝ aɓwana-mǝɓane na mǝnana à ram rǝia à kǝ pur gya andǝi ka. 
\p  
\v 4 Ɓè pwari yiu mǝnana amǝ'Amon yinǝ munǝo arǝ Isǝrayila ka.  
\v 5 Sǝ lang amǝ'Amon soa munǝo arǝ Isǝrayila ka, aɓwana-mǝgule mala Gilǝyat wari a nzali Top ace yinǝ Jefta.  
\v 6 À banggi Jefta ama, <<Yiu yi duk múr sǝm, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ sǝm munǝ arǝ amǝ'Amon ngga.>>  
\v 7 Sǝ Jefta ne aɓwana-mǝgule mala Gilǝyat ama, <<Wun nda mǝnana wu lǝmdǝam ɓinǝmǝsǝu, sǝ wu pǝram ǝn purì ɓala mala tárrám ngga re? Palang sǝ wu yiu abanam ado mǝnana wu kutina aɓa tanni ka?>> 
\p  
\v 8 Pǝlǝa aɓwana-mǝgule mala Gilǝyat earî Jefta ama, <<Nda gìr mǝnana tsǝa sǝ sǝm nyar a bano ado ka. Yiu atà sǝm ace munǝo arǝ amǝ'Amon, sǝ awu nǝ duk múr sǝm, sǝm kat a Gilǝyat.>> 
\p  
\v 9 Pǝlǝa Jefta banggi aɓwana-mǝgule mala Gilǝyat ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ wu nyesǝam ace munǝo arǝ amǝ'Amon, sǝ Yahweh tsǝa à kpa a ɓabuam ngga, mǝ nǝ duk múr wun.>> 
\p  
\v 10 Sǝ aɓwana-mǝgule mala Gilǝyat earî Jefta ama, <<Yahweh ɓǝ̀ duk mǝ'nakún anre sǝm, ɓǝ̀ sǝm pak kǝla mǝnana a na raka.>>  
\v 11 Anggo sǝ Jefta o andǝ aɓwana-mǝgule mala Gilǝyat, sǝ à kya tsǝi duk múrû, sǝ mǝ'sàrǝ̀ban amúrià. Sǝ Jefta ɓǝsǝlǝ bang acau male kat\f + \fr 11:11 \fq acau male kat \ft mala eare mǝnia ka\f* aɓadǝm Yahweh a Mizpa. 
\p  
\v 12 Pǝlǝa Jefta tasǝ amǝ'na-túrbân aban murǝm mala amǝ'Amon nǝ cau ama, <<Mana ǝn pakko, sǝ a yiu ama a nǝ munǝ arǝ nzali mem?>> 
\p  
\v 13 Sǝ murǝm mala amǝ'Amon earî amǝ'na-túrbân mala Jefta ama, <<Nda acemǝnana lang Isǝrayila purî Masar aban yiu ka, ak nzali mem, twal a Nggeasala Arnon, kya bik Nggeasala Jabok, sǝ sárǝ́ aban ká a Nggeasala Jodan; acemani ka, nyesǝi aɓa do-jam.>> 
\p  
\v 14 Jefta pǝlǝa tasǝ amǝ'na-túrbân ɗǝm aban murǝm mala amǝ'Amon,  
\v 15 sǝ à kya ne wi ama, <<Jefta bang ama: Isǝrayila ak nzali mala amǝ'Mowap ko nzali mala amǝ'Amon ɗàng.  
\v 16 Lang Isǝrayila purî Masar ka, kúti nǝɓa pǝɗanban, aban ká a Nggeamùr Nzuno, sǝ yiu a Kadesh.  
\v 17 Isǝrayila pǝlǝa tasǝ amǝ'na-túrbân aban murǝm mala amǝ'Edom, ama <Ida, eara sǝm ɓǝ̀ sǝm kùtí nǝɓa nzali mô.> Sǝ murǝm Edom ngga kwakikiri ɗàng. Ɗǝm ngga, à tasǝ cau aban murǝm mala amǝ'Mowap, sǝ yi gbal ka wakí cê. Nda Isǝrayila ueo a Kadesh ka.\f + \fr 11:17 \fq Kadesh \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Ɓal 20:14-21\ft .\f* 
\v 18 Pǝlǝa à twal gya nǝɓa pǝɗanban, sǝ à kàrìban arǝ nkanggari nzong-nzali mala amǝ'Edom andǝ mala amǝ'Mowap. À kya bik bù takuli mala nzali mala amǝ'Mowap, sǝ à yi duk kàttì a nkaring Nggeasala Arnon; à kùtí aɓa bu-nzali mala amǝ'Mowap ɗàng, acemǝnana myalmur Arnon ngga, nda nzong-nzali mala amǝ'Mowap.  
\v 19 Isǝrayila pǝlǝa tasǝ amǝ'na-túrbân aban Sihon, murǝm mala amǝ'Amor, murǝm mala Heshbon, nǝ cau ɓǝà banggi wi ama, <Ida, eara sǝm ɓǝ̀ sǝm kùtí nǝɓa nzali mô aban ká a là ma'sǝm.>  
\v 20 Sǝ Sihon ngga, earnǝ Isǝrayila ama ɓǝ̀ kùtí nǝɓa nzong-nzali male ɗàng; nda Sihon ramba aɓwana male kat abanɓwáná, à yi tsǝk kàttì a Jahaz, sǝ warinǝ munǝo arǝ Isǝrayila ka. 
\p  
\v 21 <<Pǝlǝa Yahweh, Ɓakuli mala Isǝrayila pà Sihon andǝ amǝ'lwa male puppup a ɓabu Isǝrayila, sǝ Isǝrayila gandǝia. Anggo sǝ Isǝrayila ak nzali Amor kat, arǝ aɓwana mǝnana à dukam ɗiɗyal ka.  
\v 22 Isǝrayila ak nzalinì twal a Nggeasala Arnon kya bik Nggeasala Jabok, sǝ twal aɓa Pǝɗanban, kya bik Nggeasala Jodan. 
\p  
\v 23 <<Ado mǝnana Yahweh, Ɓakuli mala Isǝrayila angŋǝna nzali arǝ amǝ'Amor sǝ pǝrnia à purni ɓadǝmba amǝ Isǝrayila, aɓwana male ka, a ndarǝ ɓariki awu nǝ ak nzalinì arǝia le?  
\v 24 Ɓǝ̀ Kemosh ɓakuli ma'wun, pà wun gìr ka, pà nǝ̀ duk girkuma ma'wun re? Anggo gbal gìr mǝnana kat Yahweh, Ɓakuli ma'sǝm pǝr aɓwana sǝ pà sǝmi ka, dumǝna ma'sǝm.  
\v 25 Nggeari ka, a kútì \f + \fr 11:25 \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt Ɓal 22:2; Jes 24:9; Mik 6:5\f*Balak muna-ɓwabura mala Zippor, murǝm mala amǝ'Mowap le? Yi ka, kutia ɓekǝ makgir andǝ Isǝrayila a kǝ fara le? Sǝ wari nǝ lwa arǝia a kǝ fara le?  
\v 26 Twalna Isǝrayila apǝlǝa gbǝman tàrú (300) nda ban do a Heshbon andǝ amuna-là male, sǝ a Aruwa andǝ amuna-là male, sǝ arǝ anggea-là mǝnana kat à nda a kún Nggeasala Arnon ngga. Ɓǝ̀ mbak-kàngkàng nzalinì ka ma'wun na, wun amǝ'Amon ngga, palang sǝ wu ak anggea-lê aɓalǝ apǝlǝkia mǝno ka ɗàng?  
\v 27 Acemani ka, mim ngga, ǝn pakko cauɓikea ɗàng; a nda mǝnana a kǝ pàkkam mǝɓane nǝ yiu mô arǝàm nǝ munǝo ka. Ado ka, ɓǝ̀ Yahweh, mǝɓashi,\f + \fr 11:27 \fq mǝɓashi \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Tite 18:25; Ayu 9:15; 23:7; Ang 7:11; 50:6; 75:7; Isha 33:2\ft .\f* kasǝ-ɓashi yalung anre ka amǝ Isǝrayila andǝ amǝ'Amon.>> 
\m  
\v 28 Kat andǝ mani anggo ka, murǝm mala amǝ'Amon tsǝkiri arǝ acau mǝnana Jefta túrìbani ka ɗàng. 
\s1 Pàcau mala Jefta mǝnana yinǝì wi nǝ bumkiɗikea ka 
\p  
\v 29 A bàkú mǝno ka, Bangŋo mala Yahweh yiu amur Jefta, sǝ twal gya kúti nǝɓa Gilǝyat andǝ Manasa, sǝ kya kúti aban ká a Mizpa mala Gilǝyat, sǝ purî Mizpa mala Gilǝyat ka, kúti aban ká aban amǝ'Amon.  
\v 30 Pǝlǝa Jefta pàcau nǝ-shambum\f + \fr 11:30 \fq pàcau nǝ-shambum \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Tite 28:20; Ɓal 30:2; 1Sam 1:11\ft .\f* aban Yahweh, bang ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ mbak-kàngkàng awu nǝ pà amǝ'Amon a ɓabuam ngga,  
\v 31 ɓǝ̀-mana pur a kún ɓala mem aban yiu a kulliǎm, lang ǝn nyarǝnì ban amǝ'Amon aɓa limurǝm ngga, nǝ̀ duk mala Yahweh, sǝ mǝ nǝ pana gir'nkila mala pisǝe kǝring nǝi.>> 
\p  
\v 32 Nda Jefta yàl a nkaring aban o a munǝo arǝ amǝ'Amon ngga, sǝ Yahweh tsǝa à kpa a ɓabui.  
\v 33 Sǝ kiɗiki anggea-là lumi-ɓari nǝ kiɗikiban mǝgule, twal a Aruwa aban ká ɗār arǝ abân mǝnana à kàrì nggea-là Minit, sǝ kya bwal ɗār a ban nggea-là Abel-keramim ngga. Anggo sǝ amǝ Isǝrayila ɓùn\f + \fr 11:33 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Akas 3:30; 8:28; 1Sam 7:13; 1Kpa 20:4; 2Kpa 13:18; Ang 106:42\ft .\f* amǝ'Amon aɓatea. 
\p  
\v 34 Pǝlǝa Jefta nyar a ɓala male, a Mizpa, sǝ mǝnia ka nda gìr mǝnana sǝn ngga: ɓoarnsarile puro aban ká a kúllè nǝ wal karata-bu andǝ ta'nggwam. Yì nda kǝ muni ɓǝ̀rɓǝ̀r; ɓǝ̀ yì na raka, panǝ ɓekǝ muna-ɓwabura, ko muna-ɓwama ɗàng.  
\v 35 Sǝ lang sǝni ka, kara bwal daura male sannì\f + \fr 11:35 \fq kara bwal daura male sannì \ft ko <<kara bumkiɗikea bwali kǝ̀rkǝ́r>>\f*, sǝ bang ama, <<Oi ɓoarnsarilem! A ɓunǝnam a nzali amúr ankūnǝam, sǝ a dumǝna tǝ́r bumkiɗikea mǝgule abanam. Acemǝnana ǝn panacau aban Yahweh, sǝ pà mǝ nǝ nggaɗi kunam ɗàng.>>  
\v 36 Sǝ earî wi ama, <<Dâ, ɓǝ̀ a angŋa-dǝmba a panacau aban Yahweh, sǝ ado mǝnana Yahweh pano limurǝm amur aɓio-amǝbura, amǝ'Amon ngga, pàngnǝ mim kǝla mǝnana a pacau ka.>>  
\v 37 Pǝlǝa banggi tárrí ama, <<Pakkam mǝnia yì gìr ka: ɗekiam ace mǝnana mǝ o a ɓua do-nsari mem sǝnǝ aɓiam, amur ankono, ba azongŋo ɓari.>> 
\p  
\v 38 Sǝ tarrí earî wi ama, <<Kyane.>>Pǝlǝa tasǝi ɓǝ̀ o, yì andǝ aɓî, sǝ à kya ɓua do-nsari male amur ankono ba azongŋo ɓari.  
\v 39 Sǝ a masǝlǝata azongŋo ɓari ka, nyar aban tárrí, sǝ tárrí pàngnǝi kǝla mana pàcau nǝ-shambum ngga; sǝ yì muna-ɓwame ka súrǝ̀ kǝ ɓwabura ɗang. Pǝlǝa cê duk kuncau a Isǝrayila  
\v 40 ama koya pǝlǝa ka amuna-mamǝna mala amǝ Isǝrayila nǝ̀ twal anonggio ine ace o a ɓua ace muna-ɓwama mala Jefta, ɓwa Gilǝyat. 
\c 12  
\s1 Amǝ Ifǝrem munǝo arǝ aburana mala Jefta 
\p  
\v 1 Amǝ Ifǝrem tunǝ amǝ'lwa malea abanɓwáná, sǝ à yàlî nkaring. À wari a Zafon ace je andǝ Jefta. À ɗì Jefta ama, <<Palang sǝ a wari a lwa arǝ amǝ'Amon, sǝ a tunǝ sǝm, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ sǝm kyan sǝnǝa wun ngga ɗàng? Ado ka, sǝm ndo sǝm nǝ̀ pisǝo wunǝ ɓala mò kat.>> 
\p  
\v 2 Pǝlǝa Jefta pa eare ama, <<Mim sǝnǝ aɓwana mem ngga, sǝm kùtí aɓa makgir mǝgule sǝnǝ amǝ'Amon. Ən tunǝ wun ɓǝ̀ wu yiu ace amsǝam a ɓabuia, sǝ wu yiu ɗang.  
\v 3 Sǝ lang ǝn sǝni ama, pà wu nǝ̀ pàkkam gbasha raka, ǝn twal yilǝmem a kún buam, sǝ ǝn yàl nkaring aban ká arǝ amǝ'Amon, sǝ Yahweh túrmuria a ɓabuam. Sǝ mana tsǝa ado, sǝ wu yiu yalung nǝ munǝo arǝàm?>> 
\p  
\v 4 Sǝ amǝ Ifǝrem bang ama, <<Wun amǝ Gilǝyat aɓa Ifǝrem ngga, wun nda ka yan? Wun nda ka kǝ aɓwana mana wu ɓangŋa, sǝ wu yiu ace kum-àwá aɓa bù-nzali Ifǝrem andǝ Manasa ka!>> Nda Jefta ramba aburana mala amǝ Gilǝyat, sǝ à soa munǝo arǝ amǝ Ifǝrem. Sǝ aburana mala Gilǝyat gandǝ amǝ Ifǝrem. 
\p  
\v 5 Aburana mala Gilǝyat ak ban yálì nkaring mùr mala Nggeasala Jodan arǝ amǝ Ifǝrem. Sǝ lang ɓwa Ifǝrem mana auna, sǝ yi bang ama, <<Wu ɗekiam, ɓǝn yàl a nkaring ngga,>> aburana mala amǝ Gilǝyat nǝ̀ ɗì ama, <<A nda ɓwa Ifǝrem le?>> Sǝ ɓǝ̀ pa eare ama, <<Awo ka,>>  
\v 6 pǝlǝa à nǝ̀ bang ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ nda anggo ka, ida, bang ama, <Shibbolet.> >> Sǝ yì ka nǝ̀ bang ama, <<Sibbolet,>> acemǝnana pà nǝ̀ gandǝ pusǝ cau mǝno ka pepè ɗàng. Pǝlǝa à nǝ̀ gbami, à nǝ̀ wal-luí a mǝno yì ban yálì nkaring mùr Jodan ngga. Anggo, sǝ à wal-lú ka amǝ Ifǝrem, á-lumi-ine-nong-ɓari (42,000), a mǝno yì pwari ka. 
\p  
\v 7 Jefta ka duk kasǝla mala amǝ Isǝrayila, mala apǝlǝa tongno-nong-mwashat. Pǝlǝa Jefta, ɓwa Gilǝyat paklú sǝ à tsǝì a ɓembe, a la male aɓa Gilǝyat. 
\s1 Ibzan, andǝ Elon, andǝ Abdon duk akasǝla mala amǝ Isǝrayila 
\p  
\v 8 Anzǝm Jefta ka, Ibzan, ɓwa Betalami, duk kasǝla mala Isǝrayila.  
\v 9 Yi ka, ndanǝ amuna-burana lumi-tàrú, andǝ amuna-mamǝna lumi-tàrú. Yi pǎ amuna-mamǝna male à alki aburana mǝnana à pa a tàu male raka. Sǝ amuna-burana male ka, alkia wia amamǝna mǝnana à pà a tàu male raka. Ibzan duk kasǝla amúr Isǝrayila apǝlǝa tongno-nong-ɓari.  
\v 10 Pǝlǝa Ibzan paklú, sǝ à tsǝì a ɓembe a Betalami. 
\p  
\v 11 Anzǝm Ibzan ngga, Elon a tàu mala Zebulu, duk kasǝla amur Isǝrayila apǝlǝa lum.  
\v 12 Pǝlǝa Elon ɓwa tàu Zebulu paklú, sǝ à tsǝì a ɓembe a Aijalon, a bù-nzali Zebulu. 
\p  
\v 13 Anzǝmi ka, Abdon muna-ɓwabura mala Hilel, ɓwa Piraton, duk kasǝla a Isǝrayila.  
\v 14 Ndanǝ amuna-burana lumi-ine, andǝ amǝkau-amuna-burana lumi-tàrú, mana à kǝ kok amǝdambǝriso lumi-tongno-nong-ɓari ka. Abdon duk kasǝla a Isǝrayila apǝlǝa tongno-nong-tàrú.  
\v 15 Pǝlǝa Abdon, muna-ɓwabura mala Hilel ɓwa Piraton paklú, sǝ à tsǝì a ɓembe a Piraton, a bù-nzali Ifǝrem, aɓa nzali múr-ankono mala amǝ'Amalek. 
\c 13  
\s1 Ɓǝlban mala Samsǝn 
\p  
\v 1 Ɗǝm ngga, amǝ Isǝrayila pàk gìr mǝnana mǝɓike na a mǝsǝ Yahweh ka, nda Yahweh tasǝia a ɓabù amǝ'Filisti apǝlǝa lumi-ine ka. 
\p  
\v 2 A bàkú mǝno ka, ɓè ɓwabura nakam lùllǝì ama Manuwa, ɓwa Zora a tàu mala Dan. Māmí ka ɓǝl muna ɗàng, acemǝnana nkombi na.  
\v 3 Mǝturonjar mala Yahweh pusǝrǝi aban ɓwame, sǝ banggi wi ama, <<Sǝni, a nda nkombi, sǝ a ɓǝl kǝ muna ɗang, sǝama awu nǝ kum muna a bumo, awu nǝ ɓǝl muna-ɓwabura.  
\v 4 Adyan ngga, tsǝkiro! A pà wunǝ nu mùr-anap ko mba ɗàng, sǝ a pà wunǝ lì kǝ gìr'ɓeami ɗàng.\f + \fr 13:4 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Ɓal 6:2-5; Luk 1:15\ft .\f* 
\v 5 Sǝni, awu nǝ kum muna a bumo sǝ awu nǝ ɓǝl muna-ɓwabura. \f + \fr 13:5 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Akas 16:17; 1Sam 1:11\ft .\f*Kǝ nkembu pa nǝ̀ je múrí ɗàng, acemǝnana twal a bum ngga, mune nǝ̀ duk ɓwa-Nazir aban Ɓakuli. Sǝ mune ka nǝ̀ tita amsǝ amǝ Isǝrayila a ɓabù amǝ'Filisti.>> 
\p  
\v 6 Pǝlǝa mālá Manuwa wario kya ne burí ama, <<Ɓè ɓwa mala Ɓakuli yiu abanam, sǝ ɓamǝsǝi ka ndanǝ ɓoarɓwa kǝ̀rkǝ́r kǝla ɓamǝsǝ mǝturonjar mala Ɓakuli. Ən ɗî ban mǝnana pur kàm ngga ɗàng, sǝ banggam lùllǝì ɗàng.  
\v 7 Banggam ama, <Sǝni, awu nǝ̀ kum muna a bumo, sǝ awu nǝ̀ ɓǝl muna-ɓwabura. Adyan ngga, a pà wunǝ nu mùr-anap ko mba ɗàng, sǝ a pà wunǝ li ɓekǝ gìr'ɓeami ɗàng, acemǝnana twal a bum ngga, mune nǝ̀ duk ɓwa-Nazir ba lú male.> >> 
\p  
\v 8 Pǝlǝa Manuwa pakhiwi aban Yahweh ama, <<Ida, Mǝtalem, nying ɓwa mala Ɓakuli mana a tasǝi ka ɓǝ̀ nyare ɓǝ̀ yiu ɗǝm aban sǝm, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ yi kania sǝm lang sǝ sǝm nǝ̀ lǝsǝ muna mana à nǝ̀ ɓǝli ka.>> 
\p  
\v 9 Sǝ Ɓakuli ok hiwi mala Manuwa; mǝturonjar mala Ɓakuli nyare yiu aban mālá Manuwa lang ndaban do a patal ka. Sǝama burí Manuwa ka pa a baní ɗàng.  
\v 10 Pǝlǝa ɓang akaurǝa kya ne burí ama, <<Yiu akaurǝa! Ɓwabura mana yiu abanam a ɓè pwari ka, yi pusǝnarǝi ɗǝm abanam!>>  
\v 11 Manuwa lo, sǝ o atà māmí. Lang yi kum ɓwabure ka ɗì ama, <<A nda ɓwabura mana a nacau nǝ māmám ngga le?>> Pǝlǝa ɓwabure eari wi ama, <<È, mǝ nda.>>  
\v 12 Manuwa ne wi ama, <<Adyan ngga, ɓǝ̀ cau mò yi lúmsǝ̀nà ka, lang sǝ sǝm nǝ̀ lǝsǝ mune, sǝ ya túró na mune nǝ̀ yia pa?>>  
\v 13 Mǝturonjar mala Yahweh ne Manuwa ama, <<Māmó ɓǝ̀ tsǝkiri arǝ agir mǝnana kat ǝn banggi wi ka.  
\v 14 Māmó pà nǝ̀ li kǝgir mana pur arǝ nggun-anap ka ɗàng. Pà nǝ̀ nu mùr-anap ko mba ɗàng, sǝ pà nǝ̀ li kǝ gìr'ɓeami ɗàng.\f + \fr 13:14 \ft Sǝni gbal a mǝsǝi 4 andǝ 7 mala kùré mǝnia.\f* Yì ka, ɓǝ̀ kpata agir mǝnana kat ǝn banggi wi ɓǝ̀ pàk ka.>> 
\p  
\v 15 Manuwa ne mǝturonjar mala Yahweh ama, <<Ida, kundǝ bǝti, ace mana ɓǝ̀ sǝm lambo muna-mbul ka.>>  
\v 16 Mǝturonjar mala Yahweh banggi wi ama, <<Ko ɓǝ̀ a tsǝem ǝn kúndǝ ka, pà mǝ nǝ lì girlina mô ɗàng. Sǝama ɓǝ̀ a ndanǝ gìr mǝnana awu nǝ pana ɓoro mala pisǝe kǝring nǝi ka, pà aban Yahweh.>> (Manuwa ka sǝlǝ ama mǝturonjar mala Yahweh na ɗàng.)  
\v 17 Sǝ Manuwa ɗì mǝturonjar mala Yahweh ama, <<Mana nda lullǝo, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ sǝm gusǝlǝo lang cau mò yi lúmsǝ̀nà ka?>>  
\v 18 Mǝturonjar mala Yahweh banggi wi ama, <<Palang sǝ a ɗiem lullǝam? Lullǝam ngga gìr'ndali na, a pà wu nǝ̀ bwalte ɗàng.>> 
\p  
\v 19 Nda Manuwa twal muna-mbul sǝ ɗàrǝ́ mǝsǝsa ace pàgir mala mǝsǝsa, sǝ pana ɓoro nǝia amúr tali aban Yahweh. Mǝturonjar mala Yahweh pàk gìr'ndali, lang Manuwa andǝ māmí na ban sǝnban ngga.  
\v 20 Lang lasǝ-bǝsa lo amúr gyangŋan aban o a kuli ka, kara à sǝn mǝturonjar mala Yahweh mǝno eau aban o a kuli aɓa lasǝ-bǝshe. Lang Manuwa andǝ māmí sǝni anggo ka, à sarǝa a nzali nǝ ɓamǝsǝia.  
\v 21 Mǝturonjar mala Yahweh pusǝrǝi aban Manuwa andǝ māmí ɗǝm ɗàng. Nda Manuwa yi sǝlǝ ama ɓwê ka, mǝturonjar mala Yahweh na.  
\v 22 Manuwa ne māmí ama, <<Ɓafo, sǝm nda sǝm nǝ̀ wù ka, acemǝnana sǝm sǝnǝna Ɓakuli.>>  
\v 23 Sǝama māmí banggi wi ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh earce ama nǝ̀ wal-lú sǝm ngga, pà nǝ̀ ak pàgir mala pisǝe kǝring, andǝ pagìr mala mǝsǝsa a bù sǝm ɗàng. Ɗǝm ngga, pà nǝ̀ lǝmdǝa sǝm amǝnia yì agir kat, ko nǝ̀ hamba sǝm agir kǝla amǝnia ka ɗàng.>> 
\p  
\v 24 Mālá Manuwa ɓǝl muna-ɓwabura, sǝ tsǝki wi lullǝu ama Samsǝn. Mune gulo sǝ Yahweh tsǝki wi bù.  
\v 25 Bangŋo mala Yahweh tita pàktúró nǝ Samsǝn a Mahane-Dan, anre \f + \fr 13:25 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Akas 18:11; Jes 15:33\ft .\f*Zora andǝ Eshtawol. 
\c 14  
\s1 Doɓala mala Samsǝn 
\p  
\v 1 Samsǝn wari a Timna,\f + \fr 14:1 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Tite 38:12-13; Jes 15:10; 19:43\ft .\f* sǝ kya sǝn ɓè muna-ɓwama mala amǝ'Filisti a ban mǝno.  
\v 2 Lang nyar a là ka, yi ne tárrí andǝ nggè ama, <<Ən sǝn ɓè muna-ɓwama mala amǝ'Filisti a Timna. Ən nggǝ earce nǝma wu alami ɓǝ̀ duk māmám.>>  
\v 3 Sǝ tárrí andǝ nggè banggi wi ama, <<Kǝ muna-ɓwama pà kàm atà amuna-mamǝna mala amǝ'eambo, ko aɓalǝ aɓwana ma'sǝm kat re, mǝnana nǝ̀ tsǝa sǝ awu nǝ nggá al ɓwama aɓalǝ amǝ'Filisti, yià amǝ ɗwanyi kasǝ-ɓatau ka?>> Sǝama Samsǝn ngga banggi tárrí ama, <<Alami, acemǝnana nda ɓwama mǝnana ǝn sǝni ɓoaram a mǝsǝàm ngga.>>  
\v 4 (Tárrí andǝ nggè ka, à sǝlǝ ama Yahweh na mǝnana kǝ pàk mǝnia yì gìr ka ɗàng, acemǝnana Yahweh naban alta njar mala munǝo arǝ amǝ'Filisti. A bàkú mǝno ka, amǝ'Filisti na mǝnana à kǝ yálmúr amǝ Isǝrayila ka.) 
\p  
\v 5 Samsǝn wari a Timna atarǝia andǝ tárrí andǝ nggè. Pǝlǝa wari a ban aɓaban mala anggun-anap mala amǝ Timna, kara ɓè muna-im lo arkwar aban yiu arǝì.  
\v 6 \f + \fr 14:6 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Akas 14:19; 15:14\f*Bangŋo mala Yahweh sulǝ amurí nǝ rǝcandǝa, sǝ kat andǝ amani ama pànǝ kǝ girbura a buì raka, bwal muna-imnì sàngi, kǝla mǝnana ɓwa nǝ̀ sàngi muna-mbul ka. Sǝama ne tárrí andǝ nggè gìr mǝnana pàk ka ɗàng. 
\p  
\v 7 Pǝlǝa wario kya nacau nǝ muna-ɓwame, sǝ ceɓoarî Samsǝn.  
\v 8 Anzǝm anonggio bǝti ka, Samsǝn nyare wario nǝ̀ nggá al muna-ɓwame. Amur njar ka, kyangye ace sǝn lú muna-im mana wal-luí ka; sǝ sǝni ka, mǝsǝnyi ramǝna arǝì mbǝl-mbǝl sǝ mur-nyi na kam aɓa lú imnì.  
\v 9 Samsǝn pǝlǝa ɗàrǝ́ mur-nyi a ɓabui, sǝ kǝ nui aban o. Lang yina aban tárrí andǝ nggè ka, pea wia aɓa mur-nyinî, sǝ à nu. Sǝama banggia wia ama ɗàrǝ́ mǝno yì mur-nyi ka aɓa lú imnì ɗang. 
\p  
\v 10 Pǝlǝa tárrí wari a Timna a ɓala mala muna-ɓwame. Samsǝn pàk girlina ace lìli-isǝban, kǝla mǝnana abura-māfela pàkkiyi ka.  
\v 11 Lang amǝ'Filisti sǝni Samsǝn panǝ aɓwana atè raka, pǝlǝa à yinǝ alaggana lumi-tàrú ace mǝnana ɓǝà pà kǝla aɓimǝdo ka.  
\v 12 Samsǝn banggia wia ama, <<Mǝ nǝ na wun ɓekǝ cauɓaɓe. Ɓǝ̀ wun nǝ̀ gandǝ súrǝ̀ mǝnia yì cauɓaɓe aɓa nongŋo tongno-nong-ɓari mala lìli-isǝban man, sǝ wun nǝ̀ banggam ɓalǝi ka, mǝ nǝ pà wun adaura linǝn lumi-tàrú andǝ anggea-daura lumi-tàrú.  
\v 13 Sǝama ɓǝ̀ wu gandǝnǝ nam raka, wun nǝ̀ pam adaura linǝn lumi-tàrú andǝ anggea-daura lumi-tàrú.>> 
\p Amǝ'Filisti ne wi ama, <<Na sǝm cauɓaɓenî ɓǝ̀ sǝm oè.>> 
\p  
\v 14 Pǝlǝa nea wia ama, 
\q1 <<Aɓa mǝligìr, girlina puro; 
\q2 Aɓa mǝ'rǝcandǝa, gìr pǝlpǝl puro.>> 
\m Nongŋo tàrú yi kutio, à gandǝnǝ na ɓá cauɓaɓe man ɗang. 
\p  
\v 15 A inea nongŋo ka, à banggi mālá Samsǝn ama, <<Ɓorikitakun burio ɓǝ̀ na sǝm ɓá cauɓaɓenî, ɓǝ̀ ana raka, sǝm nǝ̀ pisǝo wunǝ ɓala mala tárró. Wu tunǝ sǝm kani, ace mǝnana wun nǝ̀ tsǝk sǝm ɓǝ̀ sǝm pǝlǝ amǝ'tǝ̀r ka le?>> 
\p  
\v 16 Nda mālá Samsǝn ɓua a ɓadǝmbi, sǝ ne wi ama, <<A kǝ ɓinǝmǝsǝàm; a earcem ɗàng. A nongsǝì alaggana mala aɓwana mem cauɓaɓe, sǝ a nam ɓalǝi ɗàng.>> 
\p Samsǝn ne wi ama, <<Sǝni, nggearǝ tárrám andǝ nggem ngga, ǝn malaká nea wia ɗàng, sǝ palang sǝ a kǝ earce ama mǝ banggo?>> 
\p  
\v 17 Mālá Samsǝn ɓua aɓadǝm Samsǝn aɓalǝ anongŋo tongno-nong-ɓari mala lìli-isǝban mǝnia ka, sǝ a tongno-nong-ɓaria pwari ka, Samsǝn ne wi ɓá cauɓaɓenî acemǝnana kùrrî mwacang ngga. Mālá Samsǝn pǝlǝa wario kya ne aɓwana male ɓá cauɓaɓenî. 
\p  
\v 18 A tongno-nong-ɓaria pwari, kaniama pwari nǝ̀ kpa ka, aburana mala nggea-lê ne Samsǝn ama, 
\q1 Mana pàk-pǝlpǝl kútì mur-nyi? 
\q1 Mana pàk-rǝcandǝa kútì im? 
\m Pǝlǝa Samsǝn nea wia ama, 
\q1 Ɓǝ̀ wu rikma-rya nǝ mamǝna muna-ndǎ mem raka, 
\q2 wun pà wun nǝ̀ súrǝ̀ ɓá cauɓaɓe mem ɗàng. 
\p  
\v 19 Bangŋo mala Yahweh sulǝ amúr Samsǝn nǝ rǝcandǝa, pǝlǝa wari a Ashkelon kya wal-lú aburana lumi-tàrú, swárki agir-nggūrǝu malea, sǝ pè aburana mana à na ɓá cauɓaɓe male ka. Bumilul kǝ̀rkǝ́r, sǝ nyare o a ɓala aban tarrí.  
\v 20 Nda à twal mālá Samsǝn à pè mwashat atà aɓimǝdo, mǝnana pàk murǝm-gyajam male. a ban lìli-isǝban ngga.\f + \fr 14:20 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Akas 15:2,6\ft .\f* 
\c 15  
\s1 Mbweban-akúnì mala Samsǝn amur amǝ'Filisti 
\p  
\v 1 Anzǝm anonggio bǝti, a kúnì mala pwan-mǝssa alkama ka, Samsǝn warinǝ muna-mbul a buì nǝ̀ nggá sǝn māmí. Ne nkili-mǝɓwabure ama, <<Ən nggǝ earce mǝ nǝ kúti atà māmám aɓa kurǝm male.>> Sǝ nkili-mǝɓwabure ka eari wi ɓǝ̀ kùtí ɗang. 
\p  
\v 2 Nkili-mǝɓwabure ne wi ama, <<Ən twali nǝma a ɓǝsǝki, a ɓinǝmǝsǝi, nda ǝn twali ǝn pê murǝm-gyajam mô ka. Mǝ'kyauwa māmó ka ɓoarnsari kútì māmó re?\f + \fr 15:2 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Akas 14:20\ft .\f* Ida, twali ɓǝ̀ duk māmó a kúnì.>>  
\v 3 Samsǝn bang ama, <<Man yalung ngga, mǝ nǝ duk mǝ'ɗwanyicau-arǝu, ɓǝ̀ ǝn pakki amǝ'Filisti gìr mǝɓane ka.>>  
\v 4 Nda Samsǝn wario kya bwal amǝ'nzǝgban gbǝman-tàrú, sǝ kurkia ɓari-ɓari arǝ anggilatea, sǝ ɗúrkia wia ɓukan, a tsùrú mala nggilatea mana kurkia ɓari-ɓari ka.  
\v 5 Pǝlǝa tsǝk bǝsa arǝ aɓukanì, sǝ nying amǝ'nzǝgbanî à kutiki aɓa mǝssa mǝnana nda ban came aɓalǝ aɓaban mala amǝ'Filisti ka. Sǝ kutio soa bǝsa, pisǝ akūno mǝssa mala amǝ'Filisti mǝnana à rambi ka, andǝ mǝssa mǝnana à malaká cani raka. Ɗǝm ngga pisǝ aɓaban-anap andǝ aɓaban mala anggun-olif malea.  
\v 6 Pǝlǝa amǝ'Filisti ɗiban ama, <<Yana ɓwê pàk mǝnia yì gìr ka?>> À banggia wia ama, <<Samsǝn, nkil ɓwa'Timna na. Samsǝn pàk mǝno acemǝnana nkili-mǝɓwabure twal māfela mala Samsǝn, sǝ pè murǝm-gyajam mala Samsǝn.>> Nda amǝ'Filisti wario à kya pisǝ ɓwame andǝ tárrí nǝ bǝsa ka.  
\v 7 Samsǝn nea wia ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ anggo sǝ wu kǝ pak ka, ǝn kána mǝ nǝ mbwe wun akúnì, anzǝm mǝno ka, sǝ mǝ nǝ came.>>  
\v 8 Nda wal-luia pas, sǝn mǝsǝswatǝr pà kàm ɗàng, nǝ kaɓa walban. Pǝlǝa wario kya do aɓa sà-tali mala Etam. 
\p  
\v 9 Pǝlǝa amǝ'lwa mala amǝ'Filisti yiu nǝ rǝcandǝa mala lwa aɓa bù-nzali Yahuda, à bwal-kàttì anzǝm la mǝnana à tunǝi ama Lehi ka, sǝ à warinǝ munǝo arǝì.  
\v 10 Aburana mala tàu mala Yahuda ɗia ama, <<Palang sǝ wu yiua munǝo arǝ sǝm?>> Amǝ'Filisti earia wia ama, <<Sǝm yiu ace bwal Samsǝn, ace mǝnana sǝm nǝ̀ pàkki wi kǝla mǝnana pàkka sǝm ngga.>>  
\v 11 Aburana á-tàrú (3,000) mala Yahuda wari a sà-tali mala Etam, sǝ à ne Samsǝn ama, <<A sǝlǝ mbak ama amǝ'Filisti na à yálkiyimúr sǝm ngga? Palang sǝ a pàkka sǝm mǝnia yì gìr ka?>> Samsǝn pǝlǝa earia wia ama, <<Kǝ gìr mǝnana à pàkkam ngga, nda gbal ǝn pàkkia wia ka.>>  
\v 12 À banggi wi ama, <<Sǝm yiu a kùrro, sǝm nǝ̀ túrrǒ a ɓabù amǝ'Filisti.>> Samsǝn bang ama, <<Wu kánbàm ama pà wun nǝ̀ wal-luem nǝnggearǝ wun ɗàng.>>  
\v 13 À banggi wi ama, <<Awo, kǝ kùrban na nǝmurǝi sǝm nǝ̀ kùrro, sǝ sǝm nǝ̀ túrrǒ a ɓabuia ka.>> Nda à kùrrì nǝ aɓǝsa anggur ɓari, sǝ à pur nǝi aɓa tali mǝno ka, à umnǝi. 
\p  
\v 14 Lang Samsǝn yi bingŋǝna Lehi ka, amǝ'Filisti lo aban yiu a baní nǝ gāwàn. Sǝ Bangŋo mala Yahweh sulǝ amurí nǝ rǝcandǝa. Anggur mana à kùrkina agarabui nǝia ka, à pǝlǝ kǝla záng mana à pisǝì a bǝsa ka, à panzǝkya à nying abui.  
\v 15 Kum mu-garakún mǝdambǝriso mǝnana malaká ìm raka, pǝlǝa lǝmdǝ buì twali sǝ wal-lú aburana á-mwashat nǝi.  
\v 16 Samsǝn pǝlǝa bang ama, 
\q1 <<Nǝ́ mu-garakún mǝdambǝriso, 
\q2 ǝn ramgia amur rǝarǝia gum-gum. 
\q1 Nǝ́ mu-garakún mǝdambǝriso, 
\q2 \f + \fr 15:16 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pǝris 26:8\ft .\f*ǝn wal-lú aburana á-mwashat.>> 
\p  
\v 17 Lang malna nacau ka, pǝlǝa nyesǝ mu-garakún mǝdambǝrisonî mǝnana a buì ka túrí, sǝ tsǝkî banì lullǝu ama Ramat Lehi.\f + \fr 15:17 \fq Ramat Lehi \ft ka ɓālǝi nda <<mgbang-ban mala mu-garakún.>>\f* 
\p  
\v 18 Mǝsamùr wali kǝ̀rkǝ́r, nda ɓua aban Yahweh ama, <<A pana mǝnia yì kaɓa amsǝban ngga nǝ bu guro mò. Sǝ adyan ngga, mǝ nǝ wù ace mǝsamùr, mǝ nǝ kpa a ɓabù amǝ'Filisti, amǝ ɗwanyi kasǝ-ɓatau le?>>  
\v 19 Pǝlǝa Ɓakuli mǝn ɓè tūliban a nzali a Lehi, sǝ mùr pur kàm aɓalǝi. Lang nuna ka, kara nyare kum bǝsa rǝcandǝa, sǝ yilǝmi nyar arǝì. Ace mǝno ka, Samsǝn tsǝkî tūli-mùrnî lullǝu ama En Hakkore.\f + \fr 15:19 \fq En Hakkore\ft ka ɓālǝi nda <<tūli-mùr mala ɓwa mǝnana ɓua ka.>>\f* Mǝno yì tūli-mùr ka, ndakam a Lehi bà yalung. 
\p  
\v 20 Samsǝn duk kasǝla amúr amǝ Isǝrayila ba apǝlǝa lumi-ɓari, a bàkú mǝnana amǝ'Filisti kǝ yálmúr amǝ Isǝrayila ka. 
\c 16  
\s1 Samsǝn andǝ Delila 
\p  
\v 1 Samsǝn wari a Gaza, sǝ kya sǝn ɓè mā-gung abanì, pǝlǝa kúti a baní.  
\v 2 Cau mesǝ aban amǝ Gaza ama, <<Samsǝn yina kani!>> Nda à kàrì banì, sǝ à kùmsǝi wi, à nǝ̀ kundǝi aɓa dù kat, a kún nggea-là. Sǝama nǝ du ka à nea rǝia ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ sǝm ɗeki sheɓǝ̀ bankwarna nǝ dǝmbari ka; pǝlǝa sǝm nǝ̀ wal-lui.>> Nda à duk ɗǝong aɓa dù kat.  
\v 3 Sǝ Samsǝn ngga nongŋo ba gakkya mala ɓadu. Sǝ lang ɓadu gakkina ka, pǝlǝa lo sǝ kya gbami agirkún bankutio mala nggea-lê, atarǝia andǝ anggunkúni ɓari, sǝ uia, kat andǝ nggun-gangndea mala múr bankutionì andǝ koman kat, sǝ imsǝia a kwàrì, pǝlǝa umnǝia a ɓong mgbang-ban mana a dǝm Hebǝron ngga. 
\p  
\v 4 Anzǝm mǝno ka, Samsǝn yi earce ɓè ɓwama a Ɓangŋaban Sorek. Lullǝ ɓwame ama Delila.  
\v 5 Aɓwana-mǝgule mala amǝ'Filisti wari aban Delila sǝ à ne wi ama, <<Swárí ɓǝ̀ lǝmdǝo ban mǝnana kaɓa rǝcandǝa male pàk kàm ngga, sǝ lang sǝ sǝm nǝ̀ gandǝì, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ sǝm kùrrì, sǝ sǝm nǝ̀ ɓunni ka; sǝ koyana atà sǝm ngga nǝ̀ po mǝsǝ bolo-azǝrfa á-mwashat nǝ gbǝman-mwashat [1,100.]>> 
\p  
\v 6 Nda Delila ne Samsǝn ama, <<Ida, banggam ban mǝnana kaɓa rǝcandǝa mò pàk kàm, sǝ lang sǝ ɓwa nǝ̀ gandǝ kurkio ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ ɓùn rǝcandǝa mô ka.>>  
\v 7 Samsǝn ne wi ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ ɓwa kùrram nǝ bǝsa amazo tongno-nong-ɓari mǝnana à malaká ìm raka, mǝ nǝ yauwiki, mǝ nǝ pa kǝla koya ɓwa ka.>>  
\v 8 Pǝlǝa aɓwana-mǝgule mala amǝ'Filisti yinǝì Delila bǝsa amazo tongno-nong-ɓari, mǝnana à malaká ìm raka, sǝ kùrki Samsǝn nǝia.  
\v 9 Delila ka angŋa-dǝmba yinanǝ aɓea aburana à ndaban kùmsǝó aɓa ɓè kurǝm-ɓaɓalǝu. Pǝlǝa Delila loasǝ gì na ama, <<Samsǝn! Amǝ'Filisti na amuro!>> Samsǝn kasǝki amazo mǝno kǝla kasǝa mala nkonggúr lang bǝsa je ka. Acemani ka, fe mala rǝcandǝa male ka à súrǝì ɗàng. 
\p  
\v 10 Pǝlǝa Delila ne Samsǝn ama, <<Sǝni, a swarkiam sǝ a nam nyir. Ida, nam lang sǝ ɓwa nǝ̀ gandǝ kùrro.>> 
\p  
\v 11 Samsǝn banggi wi ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ ɓwa kùrram nǝ bǝsa anggur mana à malaká pàktúró nǝia raka, mǝ nǝ yauwiki, mǝ nǝ pa kǝla koya ɓwa ka.>>  
\v 12 Aburana mǝno yina à ndaban kùmsǝó aɓa kurǝm-ɓaɓalǝu. Pǝlǝa Delila twal bǝsa anggur, kùrki Samsǝn nǝia, sǝ loasǝ gì na ama, <<Samsǝn! Amǝ'Filisti na amuro!>> Sǝ Samsǝn kara kasǝki anggur mana à kùrki nǝia arǝ agarabui ka kǝla mǝsǝ'nkonggúr. 
\p  
\v 13 Pǝlǝa Delila ne Samsǝn ama, <<Bà adyan a camarǝ swarkiam, andǝ nam nyir. Banggam lang sǝ ɓwa nǝ̀ gandǝ kùrro.>> Pǝlǝa Samsǝn banggi wi ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ a tâ nyang-muram mǝnana à bwalki arǝ abanì tongno-nong-ɓari aɓalǝarǝia andǝ nkonggúr-tàgìr mana nda arǝ nggun-tà'nggubyau, sǝ a kifi nǝ gara-tàgìr ka, mǝ nǝ yauwiki, mǝ nǝ pa kǝla koya ɓwa.>>  
\v 14 Sǝ lang Samsǝn na a ntulo ka, Delila tà nyang-múr Samsǝn mǝnana à bwalki arǝ abanì tongno-nong-ɓari ka aɓalǝarǝia andǝ nkonggúr-tàgìr mana nda arǝ nggun-tà'nggubyau ka, sǝ kifi nǝ gara-tàgìr. Pǝlǝa loasǝ gì na ama, <<Samsǝn! Amǝ'Filisti na amuro!>> Sǝ Samsǝn loapi ntulo, gwachi nyang-múrí arǝ gara-tàgìr, andǝ nggun-tà'nggubyau, andǝ nkonggúr-tàgìr. 
\p  
\v 15 Pǝlǝa Delila ne Samsǝn ama, <<Lang sǝ awu nǝ na ama, <Ən nggǝ earceo,> sǝ ɓabumo pà arǝàm ɗàng? A ɓangginanǝ mim kusǝ tàrú ado, sǝ a nam ban mǝnana kaɓa rǝcandǝa mò pàk kàm ngga ɗàng.>>  
\v 16 Delila camarǝ pisǝta Samsǝn tùtù koya pwari nǝ acau male andǝ ɓuakiarǝu, gandǝa lulbum Samsǝn kǝla nǝ wǔ. 
\p  
\v 17 A masǝlǝate ka, Samsǝn ne wi ɓabumi kat. Banggi wi ama, <<Twal a pwari mǝnana à ɓǝlam ngga, nkembu je muram a kǝ pwari ɗàng, acemǝnana mǝ nda ɓwa-nazir\f + \fr 16:17 \fq ɓwa-nazir \ft ko <<ɓwa mǝnana à tàrrì aban Ɓakuli ka.>>\f* aban Ɓakuli twal a bum nggem. Ɓǝ̀ ɓwa mwa nyang ɓamuram ngga, rǝcandǝa mem nǝ̀ nyem, sǝ mǝ nǝ yauwiki, mǝ nǝ pa kǝla koya ɓwa ka.>> 
\p  
\v 18 Lang Delila sǝni ama Samsǝn nani wi ɓabumi kat ka, túrban ɓǝà tunǝ aɓwana-mǝgule mala amǝ'Filisti, nǝ cau ama, <<Wu yiu ɗǝm, acemǝnana bangŋǝnam ɓabumi kat.>> Nda aɓwana-mǝgule mala amǝ'Filisti yiu abani nǝ boalo a buia.  
\v 19 Delila pǝlǝa tsǝk Samsǝn koa ntulo a byali, sǝ tunǝ ɓè ɓwabura yi mwa nyang-múr Samsǝn mǝnana à bwalki wi arǝ abanì tongno-nong-ɓari ka. Anggo sǝ Delila tita kyauwiki Samsǝn, sǝ rǝcandǝa male nying rǝì.  
\v 20 Pǝlǝa loasǝ gì na ama, <<Samsǝn! Amǝ'Filisti na amuro!>> Sǝ Samsǝn loapi ntulo male, ne ɓamurǝi ama, <<Mǝ nǝ puro kǝla mǝnana ǝn pakkiyi ɗiɗyal ka, sǝ mǝ nǝ dǝurǝ rǝàm ace panzǝ ɓamuràm.>> Sǝ yi ka sǝlǝ ama Yahweh nyingŋǝni ɗàng.  
\v 21 Amǝ'Filisti gbami, sǝ à ukki amǝsǝi à pusǝkia. À yinǝi a Gaza, sǝ à kùrri nǝ ansolo bolo-bángŋá. À tsǝi pǝlǝ mǝgogô a ndàkurban.  
\v 22 Sǝama nyang-múrí tita to ɗǝm anzǝm mana à mwani ka. 
\s1 Lú andǝ tsǝkban mala Samsǝn 
\p  
\v 23 Aɓwana-mǝgule mala amǝ'Filisti ramba abanɓwáná ace pa gìr'nkila mǝgule aban \f + \fr 16:23 \ft Ɓalli amurí aɓa: \xt 1Kpa 10:10; 1Sam 5:1-7\ft .\f*Dagon, ɓakuli malea, sǝ ace pàkkiɗire. À na ama, <<ɓakuli ma'sǝm pàna Samsǝn ɓisǝm mǝbura a ɓabù sǝm.>> 
\p  
\v 24 Lang aɓwe sǝn Samsǝn ngga, à ɓwangsǝ ɓakuli malea. À kǝ na ama, 
\q1 <<ɓakuli ma'sǝm pàna ɓisǝm mǝbura 
\q2 a ɓabù sǝm, 
\q1 yì ɓwa mana kiɗiki nzali ma'sǝm sǝ wal-lú sǝm pas ka.>> 
\p  
\v 25 Lang à nda aɓa banɓoarnado ka, à bang ama, <<Wu yinǝa sǝm nǝ Samsǝn ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ yi pakgìr ace pa sǝm oalo ka.>> Pǝlǝa à pusǝ Samsǝn a ndàkurban, sǝ pàkkia wia gìr pà oalo. À tamsǝì a nre ka anggun-gbasha.  
\v 26 Samsǝn ne mǝlagga mǝnana bwalkiyi wi gara ka ama, <<Kyan nǝ mim a ban mǝnana mǝ nǝ gandǝ je anggun-gbasha mana à tamsǝ ndàmǝgule man ngga, ace mǝnana mǝ eangnǝ arǝia ka.>>  
\v 27 Ndàmǝgule mǝno lumsǝ nǝ aburana andǝ amamǝna, andǝ aɓwana-mǝgule mala amǝ'Filisti. Sǝ a múr-kurǝm ngga aburana andǝ amamǝna nakam á-tàrú aban sǝn Samsǝn kǝ pàk gìr pà'oalo.  
\v 28 Pǝlǝa Samsǝn pakhiwi aban Yahweh ama, <<We Mǝtalem, Yahweh, ida ɗenyinǝ mim! Ida, pam rǝcandǝa ɗǝm kusǝ mwashat ɓǝ̀rɓǝ̀r, We Ɓakuli, ace mǝnana mǝ mbweka amǝ'Filisti akúnì amǝsǝam ɓari mǝnana à pusǝkia ka.>>  
\v 29 Pǝlǝa Samsǝn tsǝk abui arǝ anggun-gbasha ɓari mǝnana a tsùrú, mana à tamsǝ ndàmǝgulenì ka, sǝ eangnǝ arǝia nǝ buì-mǝlì arǝ man mwashat ka, sǝ buì-mǝ'nggare arǝ ɓè.  
\v 30 Sǝ Samsǝn bang ama, <<Ɓǝ̀n wú sǝnǝ amǝ'Filisti!>> Pǝlǝa mǝn rǝì [ramta anggun-gbasha] nǝ rǝcandǝa male kat, kara ndàmǝgulenì bǝbbǝriki amúr aɓwana-mǝgule sǝ amur aɓwe kat mǝnana aɓalǝi ka. Aɓwana mana Samsǝn wal-luia a lú male ka, à kútì mana wal-luia a do-yilǝmu male ka. 
\p  
\v 31 Amǝ'eam Samsǝn andǝ aɓǝla male yi twal luí, à umnǝi à kya tsǝì anre \f + \fr 16:31 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Akas 13:25\ft .\f*Zora andǝ Eshtawol, a ɓembe-ɓa-tali mala tárrí Manuwa. Samsǝn duk kasǝla amúr amǝ Isǝrayila mala apǝlǝa lumi-ɓari. 
\c 17  
\s1 Mika pàk ankúl sǝ twal pǝris 
\p  
\v 1 Ɓè ɓwabura nakam, ɓwa nzali múr-ankono mala Ifǝrem na, lùllǝì ama Mika.  
\v 2 Banggi nggè ama, <<Mǝsǝ bolo-azǝrfa á-mwashat-nǝ-gbǝman-mwashat (1,100) mana à twalì arǝò, mǝnana ǝn oeo a sú ɓwa mana iu mǝsǝ boale ka, sǝni, mǝsǝ bolo-azǝrfe ka nda a buam; mǝ nda ǝn twali ka.>> Sǝ nggè ne wi ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh tsǝko bù, munem!>>  
\v 3 Pǝlǝa nyesǝî nggè mǝsǝ bolo-azǝrfa á-mwashat-nǝ-gbǝman-mwashat mǝno. Sǝ nggè bang ama, <<Mǝ ndya ǝn nggǝ tàr mǝnia yì mǝsǝ bolo-azǝrfa ka nǝ buam aban Yahweh ace munem, ace pàk \f + \fr 17:3 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pur 20:4\ft .\f* nkúl mǝnana à shàrrì andǝ \f + \fr 17:3 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pǝris 19:4\ft .\f* ɓǝ̀nzál mana à ɓè nǝ bolo-azǝrfa ka.>>  
\v 4 Lang nyesǝni nggè mǝsǝ bolo-azǝrfa ka, pǝlǝa nggè twal mǝsǝ bolo-azǝrfa gbǝman-ɓari (200), sǝ pè mǝ'ntùl. Sǝ mǝ'ntùl pàktúró nǝ mǝsǝ bolo-azǝrfa man sǝ pàk ɓǝ̀nzál mǝnana à shàrrì, andǝ ɓǝ̀nzál mala bolo-ntùl. Pǝlǝa à tsǝì a ɓala mala Mika.  
\v 5 Ɓwabura man, yì Mika ka ndanǝ ndà-ankúl. Pàk \f + \fr 17:5 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Akas 8:14; 17; Pur 28:6-35\ft .\f*efot andǝ ankúl ace amǝɓala, sǝ tàr mwashat atà amuna-burana male ɓǝ̀ duk pǝris male.  
\v 6 A bàkú mǝno ka, amǝ'Isǝrayila pànǝ murǝm ɗàng. Koyana le ka pàk gìr mǝnana ɓoari wi a mǝsǝi ka. 
\p  
\v 7 Ɓè lagga nakam mǝnana ndanǝdo a Betalami, a bu-nzali Yahuda ka. Yì ka, ɓwa'Lawi na sǝ yi do kǝla bǝri aɓalǝ amǝ'tàu mala Yahuda.  
\v 8 Mǝnia yì ɓwabura ka, nying Betalami a bu-nzali Yahuda, sǝ o ace alta ɓè ban mana nǝ̀ duk kam ngga. Aɓa gya male ka, yiu a nzali múr-ankono mala Ifǝrem, a ɓala mala Mika.  
\v 9 Mika ɗì ama, <<A pùr nǝ kǝshe?>> Pǝlǝa eari wi ama, <<Mǝ nda ɓwa'Lawi, sǝ ǝn pùr a Betalami a bu-nzali Yahuda. Mǝ nda aban alta ban mǝnana mǝ nǝ duk kam ngga.>>  
\v 10 Mika ne wi ama, <<Do atàm. Duk tárrû andǝ pǝris abanam. Mǝ nǝ nggǝ mbweo mǝsǝ bolo-azǝrfa lum koya pǝlǝa ka, andǝ agir-nggūrǝu sǝ girlina.>>  
\v 11 Nda ɓwa'Lawi man eare do atà Mika, sǝ yì laggè ka pǝlǝì Mika kǝla mwashat atà amuna-burana male.  
\v 12 Pǝlǝa Mika kùrî ɓwa'Lawi man pǝris, sǝ yì laggè ka pǝlǝ pǝris male, sǝ do a ɓala mala Mika.  
\v 13 Sǝ Mika bang ama, <<Adyan ngga, ǝn sǝlǝna ama Yahweh nǝ̀ pàkkam mǝɓoarne, atàcau mala ɓwa'Lawi mǝnia mǝnana duk pǝris mem ngga.>> 
\c 18  
\s1 Amǝ'tàu mala Dan alta nzali liɓala 
\p  
\v 1 A bàkú mǝno ka, amǝ'Isǝrayila pànǝ murǝm ɗàng. Sǝ a kǝ bákuì ka, \f + \fr 18:1 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Akas 1:34; Jes 19:47-48\ft .\f*amǝ'tàu mala Dan naban alta nzali liɓala mǝnana à nǝ̀ duk kam ngga, acemǝnana yi pur a bàkú mǝno ka, à malaká kum nzali liɓala malea aɓalǝ atau mala amǝ'Isǝrayila ɗàng.  
\v 2 Nda amǝ'tàu mala Dan tàrki akanggǝrang aburana tongno, aɓa tàu malea puppup a Zora andǝ Eshtawol, sǝ à tasǝia ace shenzǝ nzali mǝnana à nǝ̀ duk kam ngga, ɓǝà gya aɓalǝi ace súrǝè pepè. À banggi aburane ama, <<Wu kyane, wu gya aɓa nzali pacauni wu pelǝki pepè.>> 
\p Sǝ à yiu a nzali múr-ankono mala Ifǝrem, a ɓala mala Mika, sǝ à sulǝ kam.  
\v 3 Lang à yi bik ban ɓala mala Mika ka, à súrǝ̀ gi mǝlagga ɓwa'Lawi mǝno. Nda à wari abani sǝ à ɗì ama, <<Yana yinǝ we kani? Mana a pakkiyi a ban mǝnia? Mana yinǝ we kani?>>  
\v 4 Pǝlǝa banggia wia gìr mǝnana Mika pàkki wi ka, ama, <<Mika twalama-túró, sǝ ǝn duk pǝris male.>>\f + \fr 18:4 \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt Akas 17:10\ft .\f* 
\v 5 Pǝlǝa à ne wi ama, <<Ida, ɗìbancau aban Ɓakuli, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ sǝm sǝlǝa ko gya ma'sǝm mǝnia ka, sǝm nǝ̀ kum puro aɓalǝi ko pà sǝm nǝ̀ kum ɗang.>>  
\v 6 Pǝris banggia wia ama, <<Wu kyane aɓa rǝpwala. Yahweh na atà wun aɓa gya ma'wun mǝnia.>> 
\p  
\v 7 Pǝlǝa aburana man tongno ka à lo, sǝ à yiu a Layish. À sǝn aɓwana mǝnana à ndanǝdo kano ka, à nda aɓa do-jam kǝla do mala amǝ'Sidon, aɓa rǝpwala andǝ ɗwanyi-tsǝk'mǝsǝu; yià ɗǝm ngga amǝ'kume na acemǝnana à ɗwanyi kǝgìr aɓa nzali malea ɗàng.\f + \fr 18:7 \fq yià ɗǝm ngga amǝ'kume na acemǝnana à ɗwanyi kǝgìr aɓa nzali malea ɗàng \ft ko <<à pà aɓata kǝɓwa mana limurǝm-nǝ-lwa ko duk-murǝm amúrià sǝ kǝ paria aɓa kyauwikiban nǝ rǝcandǝa ka ɗàng.>>\f* À nda kuko nǝ amǝ'Sidon, sǝ à pà aɓa kpapimúrû andǝ ɓekǝ nzali ace kum gbasha ɗàng. 
\p  
\v 8 Sǝ lang aburana man nyarna aban amǝ'eambia, a Zora andǝ Eshtawol ka, amǝ'eambia ɗia ama, <<Mana nda kún-bǝri ma'wun?>>  
\v 9 À banggia wia ama, <<Wu lo, ɓǝ̀ sǝm kya arǝia nǝ munǝo, acemǝnana sǝm pelǝna ɓá nzalinì, sǝ sǝm sǝni ka, ndanǝ ɓoaro kǝ̀rkǝ́r. Sǝ pà wun nǝ̀ pàk kǝgir re? Wu kǝa dǝndi arǝ ká ak nzalinì ɓǝ̀ pǝlǝ ma'wun ɗàng.  
\v 10 Lang wu bingŋǝna nzalinì ka, wun nǝ̀ kum aɓwana mana à nda ɓá do ɗwanyi-tsǝk'mǝsǝu; andǝ nzali mǝtangŋe mǝnana Ɓakuli pana wuni a ɓabù wun ngga; nzali mǝnana ɗwanyi kǝgir mana nda a ɓanza ka ɗàng!>> 
\p  
\v 11 Aburana gbǝman-tongno-nong-mwashat a tàu mala Dan kùr rǝia nǝ agirbura mala lwa, sǝ à pur a Zora andǝ Eshtawol.  
\v 12 Pǝlǝa à eauwe à kya tsǝk kàttì malea a Kiriat-Jarim a bu-nzali Yahuda. Nda gìr mǝnana tsǝa sǝ ban mǝno a njar-nzali mala Kiriat-Jarim ngga, à tunǝi ama Mahane Dan\f + \fr 18:12 \fq Mahane Dan \ft ngga nda <<Kàttì mala Dan.>>\f* bà yalung ngga.  
\v 13 À lo kano ka, à gya aɓa nzali múr-ankono mala Ifǝrem, sǝ à yiu a ɓala mala Mika. 
\p  
\v 14 Pǝlǝa aburana tongno mana à wari a shenzǝ nzali Layish ka, à banggi amǝ'eambǝia ama, <<Wu sǝlǝ ama atà \f + \fr 18:14 \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt Akas 17:4,5\ft .\f*aɓala mǝnia ka, efot, andǝ ankúl ace ɓala, andǝ ɓǝ̀nzál mǝnana à shàrrì, andǝ ɓǝ̀nzál mala bolo-ntul ka à ndakam? Wu ɓalkiɓabum wun amúr mana ɓoaro ɓǝ̀ wu pa.>>  
\v 15 Pǝlǝa à kàr kano, sǝ à wari a bando mala mǝlagga ɓwa'Lawi mǝno a ɓala mala Mika ka, sǝ à makki-wi-kûn.  
\v 16 Aɓa mǝno anggo ka, aburana mala amǝ'tàu mala Dan mǝno à kùrna rǝia nǝ agirbura ace lwa ka, à cam a bankutio a kúnɓala.  
\v 17 Pǝlǝa aburana tongno mǝnana à yina atadǝmbe à shenzǝna nzalinì ka, à wario sǝ à kutio sǝ à twal ɓǝ̀nzál mǝnana à shàrrì ka, andǝ efot, andǝ ankúl mala ɓala, andǝ ɓǝ̀nzál mala bolo-ntul, sǝ pǝris ka ndaban came a bankutio a kúnɓala atà aburana gbǝman-tongno-nong-mwashat mana à kùrna rǝia nǝ agirbura ace lwa ka.  
\v 18 Lang aburana man kúti a ɓala mala Mika sǝ à twal ɓǝ̀nzál mǝnana à shàrrì, andǝ efot, andǝ ankúl mala ɓala, andǝ ɓǝ̀nzál mala bolo-ntul ka, pǝris ɗia ama, <<Mana mǝna wu pàkkiyi ka?>>  
\v 19 À earî wi ama, <<Duk kúnó piu! Kǝa na kǝ cau ɗàng. We ka, yiu atà sǝm, sǝ wu duk tárrû andǝ pǝris amur sǝm. Pà nǝ̀ ɓoaribani wu duk pǝris amur ɓè nggurkwar, andǝ pǝris amur ɓè tàu mala Isǝrayila puppup, amúr-mana wu duk pǝris amúr ɓala mala ɓwa mwashat ka re?>>  
\v 20 Kara banɓoari pǝris mǝno. Nda twal ɓǝ̀nzál mǝnana à shàrrì, andǝ efot, andǝ ankúl mala ɓala, andǝ ɓǝ̀nzál mala bolo-ntul, sǝ o ateà. 
\p  
\v 21 Pǝlǝa à wulio, sǝ à bwal njar aban o, sǝama à tsǝk amuna-mǝkeke, andǝ agirkusǝu, andǝ agirkuma malea a dǝmba sǝ à kǝ gya anzǝmia.  
\v 22 Lang à umǝna ɗār nǝ ɓala mala Mika ka, amǝ'murkala mala Mika ramba abanɓwáná, sǝ à o pǝrta aɓwana mala Dan.  
\v 23 Lang à loasǝ gia à tunǝia ka, aɓwana mala Dan pǝlǝ ɓamǝsǝia sǝ à ɗì Mika ama, <<Marǝò sǝ wu ram rǝ wun anggo?>>  
\v 24 Mika earia wia ama, <<Wu twalna aɓakuli mem mǝnana ǝn pea ka, andǝ pǝris, sǝ wu umǝna nǝia. Mana uekàm ɗǝm? Palang sǝ wun nǝ̀ ɗiem ama, <Marǝò?> >>  
\v 25 Aɓwana mala Dan banggi wi ama, <<Kǝa eare ɓǝà ok gio aɓalǝ sǝm ɗàng, ɓǝ̀ ana raka, aɓea aburana mǝ'lulle aɓalǝ sǝm nǝ̀ kpa amuro, sǝ awu nǝ ɗwanyi yilǝmo andǝ ayilǝmi amǝ'ɓala mò.>>  
\v 26 Pǝlǝa aɓwana mala Dan ukia'o malea. Sǝ lang Mika sǝni ama à kútì nǝ rǝcandǝa ka, kara nyare o a ɓala male. 
\p  
\v 27 Aɓwana mala Dan twal agir mǝnana Mika pea ka, andǝ pǝris male, sǝ à yiu a Layish, aban aɓwana mana à nda ɓá do rǝpwala andǝ ɗwanyi-tsǝk'mǝsǝu ka. À wal-luia nǝ kún nggeabyau, sǝ à soaki nggea-lê bǝsa.  
\v 28 Sǝ kǝɓwa yiu ace amsǝia ɗàng, acemǝnana nggea-lê ka nda kuko nǝ Sidon, sǝ ɗǝm ngga, à pà aɓa kpapimúrû andǝ ɓekǝ nzali ace kum gbasha ɗang. Nggea-lê ka, nda aɓa ɓangŋaban mala Bet-Rehop. Pǝlǝa aɓwana mala Dan ɓǝsǝlǝ-ɓak nggea-lê, sǝ à duk kam.  
\v 29 À tsǝkî nggea-lê lullǝu ama Dan, mǝnana nda lullǝu keâ, yì Dan mana à ɓǝlî Isǝrayila ka; sǝama ɗiɗyal ka, lullǝu nggea-lê nda Layish.  
\v 30 Sǝ tàu mala Dan tamsǝî ɓamuria mǝno yì ɓǝ̀nzál mana à shàrrì ka; sǝ Jonatan, muna-ɓwabura mala Gashom, \f + \fr 18:30 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Pur 2:22; 18:3\ft .\f*muna-ɓwabura mala \f + \fr 18:30 \fq Musa \ft ko Manasa\f*Musa andǝ amǝ'ke ka, à nda ka apǝris mala tàu mala Dan bà bàkú mala bwalban-aguro andǝ umnǝia a bǝri-nzali.  
\v 31 Nda tàu mala Dan tamsǝî ɓamuria ɓǝ̀nzál mala Mika mana à shàrrì, mǝnana pè ka, sǝ uekam arǝ abákú mǝnana kat Taragula mala Ɓakuli nakam a Shilo ka. 
\c 19  
\s1 Ɓwa'Lawi andǝ mā-twala male 
\p  
\v 1 A bàkú mǝno mǝnana murǝm pà kàm a Isǝrayila raka,\f + \fr 19:1 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Akas 17:6; 18:1; 21:25\ft .\f* ɓè ɓwa'Lawi nakam mǝnana ndanǝdo kuko a nkanggariban mala nzali múr-ankono mala Ifǝrem ngga. Yì ka twalî ɓamurì mā-twala a Betalami, a bu-nzali Yahuda.  
\v 2 Sǝ mā-twala mǝnia ka bumi-lullo arǝ burí, pǝlǝa nyì sǝ o a ɓala mala tárrí a Betalami, a bu-nzali Yahuda. Lang pàngŋǝ́nà azongŋo ine a ɓala mala tárrí ka,  
\v 3 pǝlǝa burí lo wari ace bǝ́lè; nǝ̀ nggá bangcau nǝi, nǝ tsǝkɓalǝu ama nǝ̀ nun ɓabumi nǝ̀ nyesǝi. Wari andǝ guro male atè andǝ amǝdambǝriso ɓari. Lang bingŋǝ́nà ka, mā-twala male kútí nǝi a ɓala mala tárrí, sǝ lang nkili sǝni ka, gingsǝi nǝ banɓoarnado.  
\v 4 Sǝ nkili, yì tár mā-twala male ka, tsǝì duk kano, sǝ ue kano atè anonggio tàrú. Aɓalǝ anonggio mǝno ka, à lìli, sǝ à nǔ, sǝ nong kano atè. 
\p  
\v 5 A inea nongŋo ka, à lo nǝ dǝmbari nǝ ban'mbul-mbul, sǝ ɓwa'Lawi gilǝrǝi nǝ̀ o. Sǝama nkili ne wi ama, <<Kundǝ bǝti, wu lî girlina ace mǝnana wu kum rǝcandǝa ka, sǝ wu o.>>  
\v 6 Nda à do yià kǝm, sǝ à lì girlina sǝ à nǔ atārǝia; pǝlǝa tár muna-ɓwame banggi ɓwabure, yì ɓwa'Lawi ama, <<Ida, eare nong ɗǝm, sǝ ɓǝ̀ banɓoaro.>>  
\v 7 Sǝ lang ɓwabure, yì ɓwa'Lawi lo nǝ̀ u ka, nkili ɓuakiarǝi gandǝa nong ɗǝm.  
\v 8 A tongnoia pwari, lo nǝ dǝmbari ɗiɗyal ace mǝnana nǝ̀ o, sǝ nkili ka ne wi ama, <<Ida, kúndǝô wu lî girlina ace kum rǝcandǝa, sheɓǝ̀ rǝ pwari wuna ka!>> Nda à lìli yià kǝm ngga.  
\v 9 Sǝ lang ɓwabure andǝ mā-twala male andǝ guro male longŋǝ́nà à nǝ̀ u ka, nkili, yì tár muna-ɓwame banggi wi ama, <<Sǝni! Pwari malanǝ̀ kpa! Ida, nongŋo. Ado mǝnana pwari wulina ka, nong kani sǝ ɓǝ̀ ɓabumo kum banɓoarnado. Lí ka, awu nǝ lo nǝ dǝmbari ɗiɗyal ace gya mô, sǝ wu oa là.>> 
\p  
\v 10 Sǝama ɓwabure ka, ear ama nǝ̀ nong ɗǝm ɗàng. Nda tsǝk agir-do a nzǝm amǝdambǝriso male ɓari. Sǝ yì andǝ mā-twala male andǝ guro male à bwal-njar, sǝ à gya à yi bik \f + \fr 19:10 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Jes 15:8; 15:63\ft .\f*Jebus (mǝnana yalung à tunǝi ama Urǝshalima ka). 
\p  
\v 11 Lang à gbàshìban Jebus ka, pwari umǝna ɗār. Sǝ guro ne mǝtala-ɓala male ama, <<Ida, ɓǝ̀ sǝm kàr a nggea-là mala amǝ'Jebus mǝnia ka, ɓǝ̀ sǝm nong kam.>>  
\v 12 Sǝama mǝtala-ɓala male banggi wi ama, <<Pà sǝm nǝ̀ kàr aɓa nggea-là mala amǝ'kúnɗàngna, mǝnana amǝ'Isǝrayila na raka ɗàng. Sǝm nǝ̀ lidǝmba nǝ gya aban ká Gibiya.>>  
\v 13 Pǝlǝa ne guro male ama, <<Fa, ɓǝ̀ sǝm ɓariki ɓǝ̀ sǝm bik Gibiya ko Rama, sǝ sǝm nǝ̀ nong aɓa mwashat atà abân mǝnia ka.>>  
\v 14 Nda à lidǝmba nǝ gya, sǝ pwari yi kpa lang à gbàshìban Gibiya a bu-nzali mala amǝ'tàu mala Benjami ka.  
\v 15 Pǝlǝa à kàr abanì ace mǝnana à nǝ̀ kúti ace nongŋo aɓa Gibiya ka. À yiu aɓa nggea-lê sǝ à do a patal mala nggea-lê, acemǝnana kǝɓwa ea a ɓala male ɓǝà kya nong kam ɗàng. 
\p  
\v 16 Zuku ka, ɓè jamgula nia loapi túró a ɓaban male sǝ kǝ yiu nǝ pwarikpǝra mǝno ka. Ɓwabure ka ɓwa nzali múr-ankono mala Ifǝrem na; sǝ yì ka ndanǝdo a Gibiya kǝla bǝri-ɓwa. (Aɓwana mǝnana à ndanǝdo a là mǝno ka, amǝ'tàu mala Benjami na.)  
\v 17 Lang jamgula man loasǝ mǝsǝi sǝ sǝn bǝri a patal mala nggea-lê ka, pǝlǝa ɗì ama, <<A pùr nǝ kǝshe? Sǝ aya ban awu nǝ̀ ká?>>  
\v 18 Ɓwa'Lawi eari wi ama, <<Sǝm pùr a Betalami a bu-nzali Yahuda; sǝm nggǝ umnǝ o kuko a nkanggariban mala nzali múr-ankono mala Ifǝrem, ban mǝnana ǝn pur kàm ngga. Ən wari a Betalami a bu-nzali Yahuda, sǝ adyan ngga mǝ ndaban nyare mǝ nǝ o a là mem, sǝ kǝɓwa pà kàm mǝnana nǝ̀ em a ɓala male ka ɗàng.  
\v 19 Sǝm ndanǝ mǝsǝkuri andǝ dǝmo ace amǝdambǝriso ma'sǝm, sǝ sǝm ndanǝ girlina andǝ mùr-anap ace ɓamur rǝ sǝm, sǝm aguro mò, mim, sǝ ɓwama man andǝ lagga mana atà sǝm ngga. Sǝm ɗwanyi kǝgir ɗàng.>>  
\v 20 Sǝ jamgule bang ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ rǝ wun pwalo! Mǝ nǝ pa wun gìr mǝnana kat wu earce ka. Sǝama wu kǝa nongŋo a patal ɗàng.>>  
\v 21 Nda yinǝia a ɓala male, sǝ pe amǝdambǝriso dǝmo. Sǝ à lakkia wia akusǝia, à lìli sǝ à nu. 
\p  
\v 22 Lang bân na rǝ ɓoaria wia ka, kara aɓea aburana amǝɓealɓike mala nggea-lê yi gumbǝli ɓalae, sǝ à camarǝ walki kúnɓala. À banggi jamgula, mǝtala ɓalae ama, <<Pusǝa sǝm ɓwabura mana yiu a ɓala mò ka, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ sǝm súrǝì.>>  
\v 23 Pǝlǝa mǝtala ɓalae puro abania a nza sǝ nea wia ama, <<Awo, wun amǝ'eambǝam! Wu kǝa pàk gìr ɓealɓikea man ɗàng.\f + \fr 19:23 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Tite 19:17\ft .\f* Acemǝnana mǝnia yì ɓwabura ka bǝri na a ɓala mem ngga, wu kǝa pàk gìr ɓeakǝno man ɗàng!  
\v 24 Wu sǝni, muna-ɓwama mem mǝnana nsari na ka, andǝ mā-twala mala ɓwabure ka, à ndya ka. Mǝ nǝ pusǝia ado; wu gbária sǝ wu pàk gìr mǝnana wu earkiyice pangnǝia ka. Sǝama wu kǝa pàk mǝnia yì gìr kǝsǝkya ka arǝ ɓwabura man ɗàng.>>\f + \fr 19:24 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Tite 34:2; Nggur 21:14\ft .\f* 
\v 25 Sǝ aburane ka à ɓinǝ kwakikiria arǝì. Nda ɓwa'Lawi gbami mā-twala male sǝ wari nǝi abania a nza. Sǝ à nongnǝi, à kìɗikì aɓa du kat bà kwaro mala bân. Sǝ lang bân tita pàk mbul-mbul ka, à ɗeki o.  
\v 26 Nǝ ban'mbul-mbul ka ɓwame yiu yi kpa a kún ɓala mala ɓwabura mǝnana mǝtala-ɓala male nakam ngga bà kwaro mala bân.  
\v 27 Lang mǝtala-ɓala male lo nǝ dǝmbari, mǝn kún ɓala sǝ pur a nza ace mǝnana nǝ̀ lidǝmba nǝ gya male ka, kara sǝn mā-twala male aban nongŋo a kún ɓala nǝ abui amur bankutio mala kún ɓala.  
\v 28 Pǝlǝa ne wi ama, <<Lo, ɓǝ̀ sǝm o!>> Sǝama okban ɗǝong. Nda twali, tsǝì a nzǝm mǝdambǝriso, sǝ bwal njar aban oa là ka.  
\v 29 Lang bingŋǝna là ka, twal byau sǝ kasǝki abare lú mā-twala male arǝ abanì lum-nong-ɓari, sǝ túrban nǝ koya bare mwashat ka arǝ abu-nzali kat mala amǝ Isǝrayila.  
\v 30 \f + \fr 19:30 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Hos 9:9; 10:9\ft .\f*Sǝ koyan mǝnana sǝni ka, bang ama, <<Gìr kǝla mǝnia ka kumban, ko à sǝni a kǝ fara ɗàng, twal a pwari mǝnana amǝ Isǝrayila purî ɓá nzali Masar ka, she yalung! Wu pàk ɗenyicau amurí, wu sǝngi, sǝ wu bang gìr mǝnana ɓoaro ɓǝà pàk ka.>> 
\c 20  
\s1 Lwa mala Isǝrayila arǝ tàu mala Benjami 
\p  
\v 1 Pǝlǝa amǝ Isǝrayila puppup puro, twal a bu-nzali Dan aban ká Biya-Sheba, kat andǝ \f + \fr 20:1 \fq nzali Gilǝyat \ft ka nda bu takuli mala Nggeasala Jodan.\f*nzali Gilǝyat. Ɓwabundǝa yi ramba kǝla ɓwa mwashat aban Yahweh a Mizpa.  
\v 2 Aɓwana-mǝgule mala aɓwe kat, andǝ atau mala Isǝrayila kat, à yi twal bancame malea a ban ramba mala aɓwana mala Ɓakuli, mǝnana làkkì malea ka amǝ'lwa á-gbǝman-ine (400,000) na, mǝnana à nda aɓa kùrrǝu nǝ anggeabyau ka.  
\v 3 Amǝ'tàu mala Benjami ok ama Isǝrayila umǝna a Mizpa. Sǝ amǝ'Isǝrayila bang ama, <<Wu bǝla sǝm lang sǝ gìr mǝɓike man kumban?>>  
\v 4 Pǝlǝa Ɓwa'Lawi, bura ɓwame mǝnana à wal-lui ka, ear ama, <<Mim sǝnǝ mā-twala mem sǝm yiu a Gibiya a bu-nzali Benjami, ace mǝnana sǝm nǝ̀ nongŋo abanì ka.  
\v 5 Aɓa bu-dù mǝno ka, aburana mala Gibiya lo arǝàm, à gumbǝli ɓala mana sǝm sulǝ kam ngga. À earce ama à nǝ̀ wal-luem, sǝama a kún mani ka, à gbárí mā-twala mem, gandǝa wǔ.  
\v 6 Ən twal lú mā-twala mem sǝ ǝn kasǝki arǝ abare mwashat-mwashat, sǝ ǝn túrban nǝ abare arǝ abân aɓa nzali liɓala kat mala Isǝrayila, acemǝnana à pàngŋǝ̀nà ɓealɓikea andǝ ɓwaɓana mala pa-kǝsǝkya a Isǝrayila.  
\v 7 Ado ka, wun amǝ Isǝrayila kat, wu na mana nda kwarkiru ma'wun andǝ gìr mǝnana ɓoaro ɓǝà pè amúr cau man ngga.>> 
\p  
\v 8 Pǝlǝa aɓwana kat lo gǝu kǝla ɓwa mwashat ama, <<Kǝɓwa atà sǝm pà nǝ̀ o a ɓala male ɗàng, sǝ kǝɓwa atà sǝm pà nǝ̀ nyar a là male ɗàng!  
\v 9-10 Mǝnia ka, nda gìr mǝnana sǝm nǝ̀ pàkkî Gibiya ka: aɓa koya tàu mala Isǝrayila ka, sǝm nǝ̀ twal aburana lum aɓa gbǝman, gbǝman-mwashat aɓa á-mwashat, sǝ á-mwashat aɓa á-gbǝman-mwashat, ɓǝà yinǝ girlina ace amǝ'lwa. Sǝ sǝm nǝ̀ bwal-shishar ace tàr aburana mǝnana à nǝ̀ ká arǝ Gibiya a bu-nzali Benjami nǝ lwa ka. Sǝ lang à warina ka, ɓǝà mbwe ka amǝ Gibiya a kúnì ɓwaɓana mala pa-kǝsǝkya mǝnana à pè a Isǝrayila ka.>>  
\v 11 Nda aburana mala Isǝrayila kat ram rǝia ace kánǝ lwa arǝ nggea-lê, sǝ à kpapimúrià kǝla ɓwa mwashat ka. 
\p  
\v 12 Atau mala Isǝrayila túr aburana arǝ abân aɓa bu-nzali mala tàu mala Benjami puppup nǝ cau ama, <<Mana nda man yì ɓealɓikea mǝnana kumban aɓalǝ wun ngga?\f + \fr 20:12 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Nggur 13:14-15\ft .\f* 
\v 13 Adyan ngga, wu pusǝki amǝ'ɓealɓana mǝnana aɓalǝ wun a Gibiya ka, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ sǝm wal-luia, sǝ ɓǝ̀ sǝm esǝki ɓealɓikea a Isǝrayila.>> Sǝama amǝ'tàu mala Benjami ɓinǝ kwakikiria arǝ gi ka amǝ'eambia, amǝ Isǝrayila.  
\v 14 Pǝlǝa amǝ'tàu mala Benjami purki arǝ anggea-là, sǝ à yi ram rǝia abanɓwáná a Gibiya ace oa munǝo arǝ amǝ Isǝrayila.  
\v 15-16 A pwari mǝno ka, amǝ'tàu mala Benjami ramba amǝ'lwa á-lumi-ɓari nǝ á-tongno-nong-mwashat (26,000) mǝnana à purki arǝ anggea-là malea, sǝ à kùrna rǝia nǝ anggeabyau ka. Tsǝa amur amǝnia ka, amǝ'do aɓa Gibiya tàrki aburana gbǝman-tongno-nong-ɓari (700) mana anggaro na ka; koyan atea ka nǝ̀ gandǝ túr tali nǝ ntamso arǝ mǝsǝ nyang mwashat sǝ pà nǝ̀ pǝ́tì ɗàng.  
\v 17 Pǝlǝa cili aburana mala Isǝrayila (mana tàu mala Benjami pà aɓalǝia raka) ram rǝia, amǝ'lwa á-gbǝman-ine (400,000) mǝnana à kùrna rǝia nǝ anggeabyau ka; yià kat ka akanggǝrang amǝ'lwa na. 
\p  
\v 18 Aburana mala Isǝrayila lo sǝ à wari a Betel, \f + \fr 20:18 \ft Sǝni gbal aɓa: \xt Ɓal 27:21; Akas 18:5; 1Sam 14:37; 1Kpa 14:10\f*sǝ à ɗì Ɓakuli ama, <<Ya tàu nani nǝ̀ aka sǝm dǝmba kánǝ munǝo arǝ amǝ'tàu mala Benjami?>> Sǝ Yahweh earia wia ama, <<Tàu mala Yahuda na nǝ̀ tita ká ka.>>\f + \fr 20:18 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Akas 1:1\ft .\f* 
\p  
\v 19 Pǝlǝa amǝ Isǝrayila lo nǝ dǝmbari sǝ à kya tsǝk kàttì malea a nkanggari Gibiya.  
\v 20 Sǝ à pur ace soa munǝo arǝ amǝ'tàu mala Benjami; à tsǝk amǝ'lwa malea à cam a nzong ban-je munǝo a Gibiya.  
\v 21 Amǝ'tàu mala Benjami purî ɓá Gibiya, sǝ à yi wal-lú aburana mala amǝ'Isǝrayila á-lumi-ɓari nǝ á-ɓari (22,000) a kun-munǝo a pwari mǝno. 
\p  
\v 22-23 Amǝ'Isǝrayila wario à kya ɓua aɓadǝm Yahweh bà pwarikpǝra. Pǝlǝa à ɗì Yahweh ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ sǝm kyan ɗǝm nǝ munǝo arǝ amǝ'eam sǝm amǝ'tàu mala Benjami le?>> Yahweh earia wia ama, <<Wu kya arǝia ɗǝm.>> 
\p Aburana, amǝ'lwa mala amǝ'Isǝrayila kum ɓabumcandǝa, sǝ à kya cam a nzong ban-je munǝo, a kǝ̀ ban mǝnana à cam kam a dǝmbe ka. 
\p  
\v 24 Anggo sǝ amǝ'Isǝrayila wari arǝ amǝ'tàu mala Benjami a ɓaria nongŋo.  
\v 25 Lang amǝ'lwa mala tàu mala Benjami purî ɓá Gibiya sǝ à soa munǝ arǝ amǝ'Isǝrayila, a ɓaria pwari ka, à wal-lú aburana á-lum-bwamdǝ-tongno-nong-tàrú (18,000) mala amǝ'Isǝrayila. Yia mǝno kat ka, aburana amǝ'lwa nǝ nggeabyau na. 
\p  
\v 26 Pǝlǝa amǝ'Isǝrayila kat, yì amǝ'lwa malea puppup, à eauwe sǝ à yiu a Betel, sǝ à ɓua. À do abanì aɓadǝm Yahweh, sǝ à gilmùr a pwari mǝno ka, bà pwarikpǝra. À pàgir mala pisǝe kǝring andǝ pàgir mala dotarǝu aɓadǝm Yahweh.  
\v 27-28 (A bàkú mǝno ka, Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli na kanó, sǝ Finehas muna-ɓwabura mala Eleaza, mǝ'kà Haruna ka, nda mǝnana pàkkiyi túró-pǝris aɓadǝmbi ka.) Amǝ Isǝrayila ɗì Yahweh ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ sǝm kyan nǝ munǝo ɗǝm arǝ amǝ'eam sǝm amǝ'tàu mala Benjami le, ko ɓǝ̀ sǝm tamsǝ munǝo?>> 
\p Yahweh nea wia ama, <<Wu kyane, acemǝnana liwi ka, Mǝ nǝ̀ pà wunia a ɓabù wun.>> 
\p  
\v 29 Nda Isǝrayila tsǝk aburana à kùmsǝó, à kàrì Gibiya.  
\v 30 Pǝlǝa Isǝrayila wari arǝ amǝ'tàu mala Benjami a tàruia pwari, sǝ à twal bancame malea ace soa munǝo kǝla mana à pè aɓalǝ anonggio mana à kutiki ka.  
\v 31 Pǝlǝa aburana mala tàu mala Benjami puro ace je-munǝo andǝia, sǝ Isǝrayila nunia à upi nggea-là. Sǝ kǝla mǝnana à pè arǝ aɓea apwari ka, amǝ'tàu mala Benjami tita walkia sǝ à wal-lú aɓea aɓwana ateà amur anjargula: mana umnǝ Betel ka andǝ mana umnǝ Gibiya ka, sǝ aɓa ɓawan. À wal-lú amǝ'Isǝrayila kǝla aɓwana lumi-tàrú.  
\v 32 Nda amǝ'tàu mala Benjami bang ama, <<Sǝm ndarǝ gandǝia kǝla mana atadǝmbe ka.>> Sǝ amǝ'Isǝrayila ka, à na ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ sǝm ɓangŋa sǝ ɓǝà pǝrta sǝm ɓǝ̀ sǝm nunia ɓǝà upi nggea-là ɗār amúr anjargula.>>  
\v 33 Sǝ koya ɓwabura mala Isǝrayila ka loapi ban male sǝ dǝshi Ba'al-Tamar, ban mǝnana à kya ram rǝia kàm ngga. Sǝ aburana mala Isǝrayila mana à kumsǝ ka, à purki pat arǝ abân kumsǝó malea a ɓawan mana kàrì Gibiya ka.  
\v 34 Nda amǝ'lwa á-lum, aburana mana à kwar aɓa lwa ka, purî ɓá Isǝrayila kat, sǝ à dǝshi Gibiya, sǝ munǝo yi candǝ kǝ̀rkǝ́r. Sǝ amǝ'tàu mala Benjami ka, à sǝlǝ ama gir'murmwana naban yiu amúrià ɗàng.  
\v 35 Sǝ Yahweh gandǝ amǝ'tàu mala Benjami aɓadǝm Isǝrayila, mǝnana tsǝa amǝ'Isǝrayila wal-lú amǝ'lwa mala tàu mala Benjami, aɓwana á-lumi-ɓari-bwamdǝ-tongno nǝ gbǝman-mwashat (25,100), a pwari mǝno, sǝ yià mǝno kat ka amǝ'lwa nǝ nggeabyau na. 
\p  
\v 36 Nda amǝ'tàu mala Benjami sǝni ka amǝ'Isǝrayila gandǝnia. 
\p Amǝ'Isǝrayila nyar nǝtea arǝ ká arǝ amǝ'tàu mala Benjami, acemǝnana à gūlì arǝ aburana malea mana à tsǝ̀ngŋǝ̀nia à kùmsǝ̀nà a nkanggari Gibiya ka.  
\v 37 Pǝlǝa aburana mana à kumsǝ ka, à latti arǝ nggea-là Gibiya, sǝ à mesǝ amurí; à pàktúró nǝ kún anggeabyau malea sǝ à wal-lú koyan mǝnana aɓalǝi ka.  
\v 38 Gir'lǝmdǝa mǝnana à earna amurí anre ka aburana mala Isǝrayila andǝ aburana mana à kumsǝ ka, nda mǝnana ama à nǝ̀ loasǝ nggea yele aɓa nggea-là aban o a kuli.  
\v 39 Sǝ lang mǝno pángŋǝ̀nà ka, aburana mala Isǝrayila nǝ̀ wulio arǝ amǝ'lwa mala tàu mala Benjami nǝ munǝo. 
\p Sǝama kaniama mǝno yi kumban ngga, amǝ'lwa mala tàu mala Benjami walna-lú atà aburana mala Isǝrayila kǝla lumi-tàrú. Sǝ à nani arǝarǝia ama, <<Ɓafo, sǝm ndarǝ gandǝia kǝla mana aɓa munǝo mǝdǝmbe ka.>>  
\v 40 Sǝ lang gupi mala yele tita lo aɓa nggea-là aban o a kuli ka, amǝ'lwa mala tàu mala Benjami pǝlǝ mǝsǝia anzǝmia sǝ à sǝni ka, yele angŋa nggea-lê puppup aban o a kuli.  
\v 41 Pǝlǝa aburana mala Isǝrayila wulio, sǝ amǝ'lwa mala tàu mala Benjami ka, ɓangciu bwalia sǝ à gǝggǝli kǝ̀rkǝ́r acemǝnana à sǝni ka, gir'murmwana sulǝna amúrià.  
\v 42 Acemani ka, à pǝlǝ nzǝmia arǝ aburana mala Isǝrayila sǝ à tsǝkmuria nǝ njargula ɓabondo, sǝ kat andǝ amani ka, à apî munǝo ɗang. Amǝ Isǝrayila mǝnana à purki aɓalǝ anggea-là ka, à kùtí a wal-luia aɓalǝia.  
\v 43 À gumbǝli amǝ'tàu mala Benjami aɓalǝu, sǝ à pǝrtea, twal a Noha\f + \fr 20:43 \fq twal a Noha \ft ko <<usǝlǝo pa kàm ɗàng>>\f* sǝ à yi ɓākia aban ká ɗār a nkāɓe Gibiya a bù takuli.  
\v 44 Amǝ'lwa á-lum-bwamdǝ-tongno-nong-tàrú (18,000) mala amǝ'tàu mala Benjami kpa, sǝ yià mǝno kat ka, akanggǝrang amǝ'lwa na.  
\v 45 Acilia wulio sǝ à ɓangŋa aban o nǝ ɓabondo, à tsǝkmuria aban ká tali mala Rimon. Sǝama amǝ'Isǝrayila wal-lú aɓwana atea á-tongno (5,000) amúr anjargula. À pìtea aban ká Gidom, sǝ à kya wal-lú aɓea aburana kàm á-ɓari.  
\v 46 A pwari mǝno ka, tàu mala Benjami ɗwanyi akanggǝrang amǝ'lwa á-lumi-ɓari-bwamdǝ-tongno (25,000) a munǝo; sǝ yià mǝno kat ka amǝ'lwa nǝ nggeabyau na.  
\v 47 Sǝama aburana gbǝman-tongno-nong-mwashat (600) auwa sǝ à ɓangŋa à umnǝ ɓabondo aban ká a tali mala Rimon, sǝ à ue kano a tali mala Rimon zongŋo ine.  
\v 48 Pǝlǝa aburana mala Isǝrayila nyar arǝ aɓwana mala tàu mala Benjami, sǝ à wal-lú koya ɓwa andǝ girkusǝu mǝnana à kumi nǝyilǝmu aɓa nggea-lê ka puppup. Sǝ koya là na à kumi ka, à soaki wi bǝsa. 
\c 21  
\s1 Amamǝna ace aburana mala tàu mala Benjami 
\p  
\v 1 Aburana mala Isǝrayila kánagìr a Mizpa ama, <<Kǝɓwa pà atà sǝm nǝ̀ pà muna-ɓwama male ɓǝ̀ al ɓwabura a tàu mala Benjami ɗàng.>>  
\v 2 Nda amǝ Isǝrayila yiu a Betel, sǝ à dumnǝdo abanì a ɓadǝm Ɓakuli bà kpa mala pwari, sǝ à loasǝ già à ɓua, ɓua mǝkwanbanì.  
\v 3 À bang ama, <<We Yahweh Ɓakuli mala Isǝrayila, palang sǝ mǝnia yì gìr ka kumban a Isǝrayila, ama yalung ngga à nǝ̀ ɗwanyi tàu mwashat a Isǝrayila?>> 
\p  
\v 4 Lang ban fana ka, à lo nǝ dǝmbari ɗiɗyal, sǝ à ɓak gyangŋan abanì. À pàgir mala pisǝe kǝring andǝ pàgir mala dotarǝu.  
\v 5 Sǝ à bang ama, <<Ya tàu na atà atau mala Isǝrayila yiu a ramba-banɓwáná aɓadǝm Yahweh ɗàng?>> Acemǝnana à kanǝna nggea kángìr amúr ɓwa mana yiu a ramba-banɓwáná aɓadǝm Yahweh a Mizpa raka, ama, <<Mbak-kàngkàng à nǝ̀ wal-lui.>>  
\v 6 Amǝ Isǝrayila pàk bumkiɗikea nǝ gìr mǝnana kum amǝ'tàu mala mǝ'eambia, Benjami ka, sǝ à bang ama, <<Yalung ngga sǝm ɗwanyini tàu mwashat aɓalǝ atau ma'sǝm.  
\v 7 Lang sǝ sǝm nǝ̀ kum amamǝna ace aburana mana à ueo nǝyilǝmu a tàu mala Benjami ngga? Sǝm kánagìr aɓa lullǝu Yahweh ama, pà sǝm nǝ̀ pea wia amuna-mamǝna ma'sǝm ɓǝà alia ɗàng.>>  
\v 8 Nda à ɗìban ama, <<Ya tàu na aɓalǝ atau mala Isǝrayila mǝnana yiu a ramba-banɓwáná aɓadǝm Yahweh a Mizpa raka?\f + \fr 21:8 \ft Sǝni a: \xt Akas 21:5\ft .\f* Sǝ à yi sǝni ka, kǝɓwa pà kàm a \f + \fr 21:8 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 1Sam 11:1; 31:11-13\ft .\f*Jabesh-Gilǝyat mǝnana yiu a kàttì mala ramba-banɓwáná ka ɗàng.>>  
\v 9 Lang à ɓalkiban ngga, à yi sǝni ka, kǝ ɓwa pà kàm atà amǝ'do a Jabesh-Gilǝyat a banì ɗàng.  
\v 10 Nda ɓwabundǝa tasǝ akanggǝrang amǝ'lwa malea á-lum-nong-ɓari (12,000) sǝ à sà'arǝia ama, <<Wu kyane wu wal-lú aɓwana mǝnana à ndanǝdo a Jabesh-Gilǝyat ka nǝ kún nggeabyau, kat andǝ amamǝna andǝ amuna-mǝkeke.  
\v 11 Wu pàk mǝnia ka: koya ɓwabura, andǝ koya ɓwama mana súrǝ́nà ɓwabura ka, wu twaltea kat-kat.>>  
\v 12 Sǝ à yi kum atà aɓwana mana à ndanǝdo a Jabesh-Gilǝyat ka, alo-ɓwa ansarina gbǝman-ine, mǝnana à malaká súrǝ̀ ɓwabura raka; sǝ à yinǝia a kàttì a Shilo, mǝnana nda aɓa nzali Kan'ana ka. 
\p  
\v 13 Pǝlǝa ɓwabundǝa puppup túrban nǝ cau aban amǝ'tàu mala Benjami mǝnana à nda a \f + \fr 21:13 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Akas 20:47\ft .\f*tali mala Rimon ngga, sǝ à hambia wia dorǝpwala.  
\v 14 Nda aburana mala tàu mala Benjami nyare a bákú mǝno, sǝ à pea wia amamǝna mǝnana à amsǝia nǝyilǝmu aɓalǝ amamǝna mala Jabesh-Gilǝyat ka. Sǝama amamǝne karǝa amúrià ɗàng. 
\p  
\v 15 Aɓwana mala Isǝrayila pàk bumkiɗikea ace gìr mǝnana kum amǝ'tàu mala Benjami ka; acemǝnana Yahweh gbakǝrina atau mala Isǝrayila.  
\v 16 Nda aɓwana-mǝgule amur ɓwabundǝa bang ama, <<Amamǝna mala tàu mala Benjami ka, à twalnatea. Mana ado sǝm nǝ̀ pa ace kum amamǝna ace acili aburana mana à ue ka?>>  
\v 17 À na ama, <<Dumǝna púp ama acili aɓwana mala Benjami mana à au ka, ɓǝà kum malea amǝ'liɓala, ace mana ɓekǝ tàu a Isǝrayila ɓǝ̀ kǝa ɓwar raka.  
\v 18 Sǝama pà sǝm nǝ̀ gandǝ pea wia amamǝna atà aɓoarnsarile sǝm ɗang, acemǝnana amǝ Isǝrayila kánagìr ama, <Ɓwa mǝnana kat pè ɓwa'Benjami ɓwama ka, ɓǝ̀ suban sulǝo amur ɓwe!> >>  
\v 19 Nda à bang ama, <<Wu sǝni, lamsan mala Yahweh mǝnana à kǝ pê koya pǝlǝa a Shilo ka malanǝ̀ yiu.>> (Shilo ka nda a njar-nza mala Betel, a njar-kunmur mala Lebona, sǝ a takuli mala njargula mǝnana anre Betel andǝ Shekem ngga.)  
\v 20 À ne amǝ'tàu mala Benjami ama, <<Wu kyane wu kùmsǝ aɓalǝ aɓaban-anap,  
\v 21 sǝ wun nǝ̀ tsǝk mǝsǝ wun. Ɓǝ̀ wu sǝni ansarina mala Shilo purna ace tàki-anggwam ngga, pǝlǝa wun nǝ̀ purî ɓalǝ aɓaban-anap, sǝ koya ɓwa atà wun ngga ɓǝ̀ gbami male yì ɓwama ace ɓamurì aɓalǝ ansarina mala Shilo, sǝ wu o a nzali Benjami.  
\v 22 Sǝ nǝ̀ ya do ama atárrià ko amǝ'eambǝia nǝ̀ yiu ace lǝmdǝ ɓua malea aban sǝm, sǝ sǝm nǝ̀ banggia wia ama, <Wu ɓwamur sǝm acea, acemǝnana sǝm gandǝnǝ kúmbi koyan atea ka male yì ɓwama a kun-munǝo ɗàng. Sǝ wun gbal ka, wu pea wia ɗàng, ɓǝ̀ ana raka ado ka wun nǝ̀ duk amǝ'kumcau.> >>  
\v 23 Aburana mala tàu mala Benjami pè kǝla mǝnana à banggia wia ka. À twalki amamǝna kǝla mana làkkì malea pàk ka, aɓalǝ amǝ'tà-nggwam sǝ à umnǝia. Pǝlǝa à nyare à o a nzali liɓala malea, sǝ à kya ɓǝsǝlǝ-ɓakki alá, sǝ à do aɓalǝia.  
\v 24 Nda amǝ'Isǝrayila mesǝì ban mǝno a pwari mǝno; à o arǝ atau andǝ anggurkwar malea, sǝ koya ɓwa ka nyar a nzali liɓala male. 
\p  
\v 25 A bàkú mǝno ka, murǝm pà kàm a Isǝrayila ɗàng. Koyan ngga pàk gìr mǝnana sǝni ɓoari wi a mǝsǝi ka.\f + \fr 21:25 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Akas 17:6; 18:1; 19:1\ft .\f*